INSERT INTO `news` VALUES (3,'BUNGWE LA DAPP LASANGALALA PA TSIKU LOKUMBUKIRA UFULU NDI ANTHU OSOWA','Bungwe la Development Aid from People to People (DAPP) lidasangalala ndi anthu ovutika pa tsiku lokumbukira kuti dziko lino lakwanitsa zaka 52 lili pa ufulu odzilamulira lachitatu sabata lino. Bungweli lidapereka zovala zosiyanasiyana za mu nyengo yozizila kwa odwala ku Dream Centre mu mzinda wa Blantyre komanso kwa anthu ozungulira koleji ya aphunzitsi ya bungweli yomwe ili m’dera la mfumu yayikulu Kuntaja m’bomali.\r\nAnthu oposa 1000 ndi omwe apindula ndi thandizoli lomwe ndi la ndalama zokwana 1 miliyoni Kwacha.\r\nMkulu wothandizila kyuyendetsa bungweli a Cedric Masikamu adati chaka chilichonse bungwe lawo limapereka thandizo kwa anthu poyamikira ubale wawo ndi anthuwo.\r\nKoma a Masikamu adati adachiona chabwino kuti afikire mwapadera anthu okalamba mu midzi komanso odwala a ku Dream Centre pomwe amakondwerela tsiku lolandira ufulu chaka chino.\r\nIwo ati anthu omwe alandira thandizo chaka chino ndi ovutika amene adalibe zovala zodzitetezera ku mphepo.\r\nM’mawu awo, mfumu yayikulu Kuntanja adathokoza bungwe la DAPP chifukwa chathandizo lomwe lidapereka. Iwo adati anthu okalamba atetezedwa ku mphepo komanso apewa matenda monga zibayo.\r\nA Maureen Lwanda yemwe ndi othandizira kuyendetsa ntchito za Dream Centre ku Blantyre adati anthu pafupifupi 5100 ndi omwe amalandira thandizo pa malowo ndipo ambiri mwa iwo ndi ovutika. Iwo adathokoza chifukwa cha zovala zomwe bungwe la DAPP lidapereka kwa odwala pa chipatala chawo.','local_news','2017-04-12','2017-04-12 17:21:49'),(4,'BUNGWE LA NICE LAYAMBITSA PULOJEKITI YOSAMALIRA MOYO WA AMAYI NDI ANA','Bungwe la National Initiative for Civic Education (NICE) mogwirizana ndi bungwe la WaterAid Malawi, layambitsa pulojekiti yotchedwa Deliver Life yomwe cholinga chake ndi kuthetsa imfa za ana aang’ono m’dziko muno.\r\nPoyankhula ku Kasungu dzulo, mkulu woyendetsa bungwe la NICE a Enock Chinkhuntha adatI cholinga cha pulojekitiyi ndi kulimbikitsa ntchito za umoyo pomwe amayi ali woyembekezera komanso akabereka ndinso kuonetsetsa kuti anthu ali ndi madzi akumwa aukhondo.\r\nIwo adati nkhani zokhudza pathupi zimakhudza kwambiri amayi ndipo akufuna kuti amayi akhale ndi liwu pa nkhani zomwe zimawakhudza.\r\nIwo adati akhazikitsa magulu a amayi omwe azitha kuyankhula limodzi pa nkhani zomwe zimawakhudza komanso zomwe zimakhudza ana omwe amabereka.\r\nIwo adawonjezerapo kuti pulojekitiyo ikhudzanso ulamuliro wabwino komanso kuti anthu omwe amapereka ntchito zosiyanasiyana monga za umoyo ndi zina azitha kufotokoza momwe ayendetsera ndalama zogwirira ntchitozo.\r\nIwo adatinso amanga malo olandirirako thandizo la zaumoyo komanso akumba zitsime mu maboma momwe pulojekitiyi ichitike.\r\nPulojekiti ya Deliver Life ichitika kwa zaka zitatu mu maboma a Kasungu, Nkhotakota ndi Machinga ndi thandizo la ndalama zochokera ku bungwe la United Kingdom Department for International Development (DfID).','local_news','2017-04-12','2017-04-12 17:23:00'),(5,'MPUNGWEPUNGWE CHIFUKWA CHOCHOTSA PAUDINDO MAFUMU 7','Kuli mpungwepungwe kwa mfumu Kalipula m’boma la Karonga kamba koti a TA Kalipula a m’deralo, a William Kalongolera Mwakikunga, akuganiziridwa kuti adachotsa pampando magulupu 7 omwe amakana kuti mfumuyi ikwezedwe pampando kuti ikhale TA.\r\nMafumu okhuzidwawo adayitanira a TA’wo kwa bwanamkubwa wa bomalo a Rosemary Moyo lachisanu ku msonkhano womwe kudali mafumu onse a mu ufumu wa a Kalipula.\r\nKulinso malipoti kuti anthu ena 16 a m’mudzi wa a Mwantende, omwe tsopano umatchedwa kuti Mwangosi, omwe amatsutsana ndi kukwezedwa kwa mfumuyo awathamangitsa m’deralo.\r\nPoyankhula pa msonkhanowo, m’modzi mwa mfumu yokhudzidwa a GVH Mwantende adati adali odabwa atadziwitsidwa kuti achotsedwa paudindo kawiri konse kuchokera kwa anthu omwe adatumidwa ndi a TA’wo.\r\nIwo adati kuyambira pomwepo, sakumaitanidwanso ku misonkhano ndipo anthu awo akumanidwa chitukuko.\r\nM’mawu mwawo, a Kilupula adakana kuti adachotsa pampando mafumuwo. Iwo adati palibe umboni wowonetsa izi.\r\nBwanamkumbwa wa bomali a Moyo adapempha mafumuwo kuti akambilane za nkhaniyi ku likulu lawo mwamsanga.\r\n','local_news','2017-04-12','2017-04-12 17:23:42'),(6,'NTCHITO YOSANKHA OSEWERA MU TIMU YA U-17 IKUYENDA BWINO','M’phunzitsi wa timu ya mpira wamiyendo ya anyamata ochepera zaka 17 ya dziko lino a DeKlerk Msakakuwona ati ntchito yosankha osewera ikuyenda bwino m’malo onse okhazikitsidwa anayi m’dziko muno.\r\nNtchito yosankha osewera ikuchitikira ku bwalo la Mpira ku Chiwembe m’boma la Blantyre, ku bwalo la Zomba m’boma a Zomba, ku Nankhaka m’boma la Lilongwe ndi ku bwalo la Mzuzu mu mzinda wa  Mzuzu.\r\nA Msakakuona ati osewera akhala akubwera m’malo onsewa ndipo ali ndi chikhulupiriro kuti apanga timu yamphamvu zedi.\r\nBungwe lowona za mpira wamiyendo wa achinyamata la National Youth Football Association (NYFA) ndi bungwe lowona za mpira wamiyendo m’masukulu la Malawi Schools Sports Association (MASSA) likugwira nawo ntchitoyi.\r\nTimuyi iyamba kukonzekera lamulungu likubwerali masewero a mpikisano wa achinyamata wa 2016 Cosafa Youth Championship omwe ukachikire m’dziko la Mauritius kumapeto a mwezi uno. \r\nMalingana ndi mlembi wa bungwe la FAM a Suzgo Nyirenda, mabungwe a MASSA ndi NYFA ali kale ndi osewera omwe adawasankha mu mipikisano ya Copa Coca-Cola, Airtel Money ndi FMB.\r\nKoma bungwe la FAM lidaganiza zopereka mpata kwa achinyamata ena omwe samasewera nawo mu mpikisano itatuyi.\r\nTimu ya dziko lino ili mu gulu B ndipo ikasewera ndi matimu a mu mayiko a Zambia, Madagascar ndi Mozambiki.\r\n','sports_news','2017-04-12','2017-04-12 17:24:30'),(7,'A YABWANYA SAPANGA APILU','Amene amapikisana nawo pa udindo wa pulezidenti wa bungwe la FAM a Willy Yabwanya Phiri ati sapanga apilu pa chilango chomwe komiti yowona za milandu ku bungwe la FAM idawapatsa. Iwo ati mlandu wawo sudayendetsedwe bwino.\r\nIwo amayankha pa zomwe mlembi wa bungwe la FAM a Suzgo Nyirenda adanena kuti kumvetsera apilu kuchitika sabata likubwerali.\r\nMwezi umodzi wapitawo, a Willy Yabwanya Phiri ndi a Wilkins Mijiga, omwe amafuna kupikisana nawo pa udindo wa pulezidenti wa bungwe la FAM, adawagamula kuti asatenge nawo mbali mu nkhani iliyonse yokhudza masewero kwa chaka chimodzi chifukwa adatenga chiletso kuletsa bungwe la FAM kuti lisapitirire ndi zisankho za bungweli m’mwezi wa Disembala chaka chatha. \r\nMu chigamulo chake, komiti yowona za milandu ku bungwe la FAM idati awiriwa adatsutsana ndi malamulo a bungwe la FIFA pomwe adakatenga chiletso kuletsa zisankho za bungweli.\r\nA Mijiga, kudzera mwa yemwe amawayimilira pa mlandu a David Kanyeda ndi omwe adapempha apilu masabata apitawo.\r\nA Nyirenda ati mlandu wa apiluwo upitirirabe ngakhale a Yabwanya Phiri sanapange apilu.\r\nA Nyirenda atinso akambilana ndi loya a Mijiga za tsiku lenileni lomwe akakambirane mlanduwo.\r\n','sports_news','2017-04-12','2017-04-12 17:25:19'),(8,'MTAWALI WASUMIRA BUNGWE LA FAM','M’phunzitsi wakale wa timu ya Flames a Ernest Mtawali asumira bungwe loyendetsa masewero a mpira wa miyendo mu dziko muno la FAM pamodzi ndi wachiwiri kwa pulezidenti wa bungweli yemwenso ndi wapampando wa komiti yowona za luso a James Mwenda. A Mtawali akusumira bungwe la FAM ndi a Mwenda mlandu owayipitsira mbiri.\r\nMalingana ndi chisamani chomwe chalemberedwa ku khoti yayikulu ya Blantyre, a Mtawali akufuna akuti bungwe la FAM liwapepese chifukwa chowayipitsira mbiri.\r\nChisamanicho chikunena kuti a Mwenda, mwa zina, adayankhula ndi kusindikiza mu nyuzi zosiyanasiyana kunena kuti bungwe la FAM lidaganiza zosawapatsa kontirakiti yatsopano a Mtawali chifukwa alibe luso loyendetsa timu komanso khalidwe labwino ndipo amabwereka ndalama kwa osewera.\r\nIwo ati nkhaniyi, komanso yomwe idalembedwa ndi wayilesi ya Zodiak komanso wayilesi ya BBC idawaonongera mbiri ngati m’phunzitsi wa mpira wamiyendo. \r\nA Mwenda ndi bungwe la FAM akuyembekezereka kukaziteteza ku khoti pasadathe masiku 28 chilandilireni samaniyo.\r\nA Mwenda ndi mlembi wa bungwe la FAM a Suzgo Nyirenda atsimikiza kuti alandira chisamani koma adakana kuyankhulapo.','sports_news','2017-04-13','2017-04-13 11:13:34'),(9,'BANKI YA FDH TSOPANO NDI SIPONSA WA FLAMES','Banki ya FDH dzulo idaulutsa za thandizo la ndalama zokwana 30 miliyoni kwacha lomwe bankiyi idzipereka ku timu ya mpira wa miyendo ya dziko lino ya Flames.\r\nMwambo wosayinira m’gwirizanowu, womwe ndi wa zaka zitatu, udachitikira ku maofesi a bungwe la FAM ku Mpira ku Chiwembe mu mzinda wa Blantyre.\r\nMkulu wa banki ya FDH a Eric Outtara adati banki yawo idaganiza zokhala mu m’gwirizano ndi timu ya Flames ndi cholinga chotukula masewero a mpira wa miyendo mu dziko muno.\r\nIwo adati anthu ambiri amakonda masewero a mpira wa miyendo m’dziko muno ndipo iwo ngati banki akufuna kutenga nawo mbali mu masewerowa.\r\nPulezidenti wa bungwe la FAM a Walter Nyamilandu adati thandizoli labwera mu nthawi yabwino pomwe timu ya dziko lino ikulandira ndalama zochepa kuchokera ku boma kutsatira ganizo la boma lochepetsa ndalama zomwe limapereka ku bungwe la FAM kuchokera pa 100 miliyoni kwacha kufika pa 32 miliyoni kwacha. \r\nChoncho iwo ati ndi okondwa ndi thandizo la banki ya FDH. Iwo adati sizophweka kupeza thandizo la ndalama zokwana 30 miliyoni kwacha kutengera mavuto a zachuma omwe ali mu dziko muno.\r\nTimu ya Flames tsopano ili ndi masiponsa awiri, banki ya FDH ndi kampani ya Calsberg Malawi Limited.','sports_news','2017-04-13','2017-04-13 11:13:57'),(11,'BOMA LAYIKA NDALAMA ZOKWANA 13.2 BILIYONI KWACHA ZOTHANDIZIRA ANTHUBOMA LAYIKA NDALAMA ZOKWANA 13.2 BILIYONI KWACHA ZOTHANDIZIRA ANTHU','Boma la Malawi lati lipereka ndalama zokwana 13.2 biliyoni kwacha ku makhonsolo a m’maboma a mu dziko muno. Ndalamazi zigwiritsidwa ntchito kudzera mu pulogilamu ya ntchito zothandiza anthu komanso pulogilamu yogawira ndalama anthu osauka ngati njira yoperekera ndalama kwa osauka kuti azitha kupeza chakudya.\r\nNduna yowona zachuma a Goodall Gondwe ndi omwe ayankhula izi dzulo kwa atolankhani ku Lilongwe.\r\nIwo adati kutsatira mavuto a zachuma komanso kusowa kwa chakudya omwe ali mu dziko muno, pulezidenti Mutharika wawonetsetsa kkuti ndalama zifikire anthu osauka kumudzi ndi mtawuni kudzera mu ntchito zothandiza anthu komanso ntchito yogawa ndalama kwa anthu osauka.\r\nA Gondwe ati ndalama zokwana 11 biliyoni kwacha ndi za pulogilamu ya ntchito zothandiza anthu pomwe ndalama zokwana 2.2 biliyoni kwacha ndi za ntchito yogawa ndalama kwa anthu osauka. Ndalamazi ziperekedwa ku makhonsolo kudzera ku unduna wowona za maboma aang’ono ndi chitukuko cha ku kumudzi.\r\nMalingana ndi nduna yowona za maboma aang’ono a Kondwani Nankhumwa, unduna wake waphunzitsa kale anthu mu makhonsolo ndi cholinga choti ndalamazi zikagwire bwino ntchito.\r\nAnthu okwana 3.4 miliyoni kapena kuti makomo 66 500 ndi omwe apindure ndi pulogilamu ya ntchito zothandiza anthu pomwe anthu okwana 589, 000 kapena kuti makomo 170, 150 ndi omwe apindure ndi ntchito yogawa ndalama.','local_news','2017-04-13','2017-04-13 11:15:07'),(12,'AKAYIDI AMATHAWA PAFUPIPAFUPI KU NDENDE YA MAULA','Mboni mu mlandu womwe alonda a ku ndende ya Maula akuwaganizira kuti adathandizira akayidi anayi kuthawa mu ndendeyo dzulo idauza khoti ku Lilongwe kuti akayidi amathawa ku ndende ya Maula pafupipafupi.\r\nSajenti Gabriel Chipala, yemwe adali mkulu wa alonda usiku wa pa 10 Julayi pomwe akayidi anayi adathawa adayitanidwa kubwalolo kuti apereke umboni opachika a Jonathan Themba a zaka 29 ndi a Steven Mwase a zaka 24 omwe amalondela mbali ya ku rimandi komwe akayidiwo adathyola ndikuthawa.\r\nMu umboni wawo, a Chipala adati usiku omwe akayidiwo adathawa, alonda awiriwa adachoka pa malo awo a ntchito ndipo adaonedwa akuthamanga kuchokera ku sukulu ya ku ndendeko lipenga litamveka kuti akayidi ena athawa.\r\nKoma loya oyimira awiriwo a Yasin Maoni adawafunsa a Chipala kuti anene kuti akayidi ku ndendeyo amathawa pafupipafupi bwanji. Apa ndi pomwe adaulula kuti akayidi ku ndendeyo amathawa pafupipafupi koma sizimanenedwa. \r\nIwo adati mu sabata yomwe akayidi anayiwo adathawa, mkayidi wina adathawanso pomwe amathirira ndiwo za masamba. Koma iwo adati aka ndi kadali koyamba kuti akayidi athawe pothyola ndende.\r\nA Chipala adatinso ku rimandi kuli babu limodzi lokha ndipo chipinda chomwe anayiwo adasungidwa chidali ndi loko m’modzi popeza loko wamkulu adali atawonongeka kalekale.\r\nMlanduwu awuyimitsa kaye.','local_news','2017-04-13','2017-04-13 11:15:33'),(13,'DZOMBE WAWONONGA MAHEKITA 30 A MBEWU YA CHIMANGA M’BOMA LA NSANJE','Akatswiri achenjeza kuti dzombe yemwe wagwa m’boma la Nsanje atha kufalikira mu maboma ena ngati sipakhala njira yomuthetsera.\r\nPakadali pano, dzombeyu wawononga kale mahekita 30 a mbewu ya chimanga ndipo wafalikira mu madera ena m’bomalo.\r\nPofika dzulo, dzombeyu adali atafika ku dera la Bangula lomwe lili pa mtunda wa makilomita 30 kuchokera ku sikimi ya ulimu wa m’thirira ya Nyamula komwe dzombeyu adayamba kugwa.\r\nAsadakatere ku Bangula komwe dzombeyu adafikako dzulo m’mawa, dzombeyu adali ataononga mbewu makamaka ya chimanga ku masikumu a ulimu wam’thirira a Ntolongo b ndi Nyapilulu.\r\nA Rodrick Mphamba yemwe ndi mlangizi wa zaulimi m’bomalo adati pofika dzulo, dzombe adali atawononga mahekita 5 a mbewu ya chimanga ku Nyamula ndi mahekita atatu a mbewu ya chimanga ku Nyapilulu.\r\nIwo ati alimi okwana 26 ndi omwe awonongeredwa mbewu zawo. A Mphamba atinso ali ndi nkhawa kuti dzombeyo atha kubwereranso chifukwa akumayendayenda.\r\nA Mphamba ati dzombeyo ndi wotalika pafupifupi makilomita awiri ndipo akumatenga pafupifupi mphindi 30 kuti amalize kudutsa pa malo.','local_news','2017-04-13','2017-04-13 11:16:04'),(14,'A ANIVA AKAWONEKERA KU KHOTI LERO','A Eric Aniva, yemwe ndi bambo wa m’boma la Nsanje yemwe adaulura kuti amagona ndi atsikana achichepere komanso azimayi ofedwa potsatira mwambo wa kusasa fumbi ndi kulowa kufa pomwe ali ndi kachilombo koyambitsa matenda a Edzi ka HIV, lero akawonekera ku khoti la majesitireti la m’boma la Nsanje.\r\nM’neneri wa apolisi m’dziko muno a Nicholas Gondwa komanso mkazi wachiwiri wa a Aniva a Fanny Eric atsimikizira za izi.\r\nA Gondwa ati Aniva akayankha mlandu wochita m’chitidwe woletsedwa womwe utha kuyika anthu ena pa chiopsezo.\r\nMkazi wawo wa Aniva, a Fanny Eric, omwe amaoneka othodwa ndi ankhawa adati akupemphelera kuti amuna awo akawatulutse. Iwo ati moyo wawo wakhala wovutika kwambiri chimangidwireni a Aniva.\r\nA Fanny Eric apemphanso pulezidenti Mutharika kuti akhululukire amuna awo womwe ati adasiya m’chitidwe wosasa fumbi komanso kulowa kufa asadakwatirane nawo zaka zinayi zapitazo.\r\nNkhani ya Aniva idatchuka kutsatira pomwe iwo adayankhula ndi ndi wayilesi ya BBC pa 21 Julayi chaka chino. A Aniva adauza wayilesiyi kuti iwo amachitidwa hayala kuti azikagonana ndi atsikana komanso amayi omwe amuna awo amwalira pa mwambo wosasa fumbi ndi kulowa kufa. \r\nKuwululika kwa m’chitidwewu kudachititsa kuti pulezidenti Mutharika alamule kumangidwa kwa a Aniva.','local_news','2017-04-13','2017-04-13 11:16:54'),(15,'PULEZIDENTI MUTHARIKA WALAMULA KUTI FIZI M’SUKULU ZA UKACHENJEDE ITSIKE KOMANSO KOLEJI YA CHANCELLOR ITSEKULIDWE','Pulezidenti wa dziko lino a Peter Mutharika walamula kuti koleji ya Chancellor itsekulidwe komanso kuti fizi za m’sukulu zonse za ukachenjede za boma zitsitsidwe ndi K50, 000.\r\nIzi ndi zina mwa zomwe pulezidenti Mutharika yemwenso ndi tchansala wa sukuluzi walamula kutsatira mkumano wake ndi atsogoleri a bungwe loyang’anira ophunzira m’sukulu  za ukachenjede la UMSU omwe udachitikira ku nyumba ya boma ya Kamuzu pa nkhani yakukwera kwa fizi m’sukuluzi.\r\nIye adalamulanso kuti boma lake lipereka ndalama zokwana K1.4 biliyoni ku khonsolo ya sukulu za ukachenjede kuti zigwire ntchito zina zomwe khonsoloyi ingalephere kugwira potsatira kutsitsidwa kwa fizi.\r\nSukulu ya ukachenjede ya Malawi (University of Malawi) ili ndi makoleji anayi omwe ndi koleji ya Chancellor, koleji ya Polytechnic, koleji ya udotolo ya Medicine ndi koleji ya unamwino ya Kamuzu.\r\nPulezidenti Mutharika adatinso ophunzira omwe osowetsetsa azipatsidwa mwayi wotenga ngongole zothandizira maphunziro awo kudzera ku bungwe lomwe limayang’anira ngongole la National Commission for Higher Education (NCHE). \r\nA Mutharika atinso ophunzira omwe akupitiriza maphunziro awo ndipo amazilipirira okha azithanso kupatsidwa mwayi wangongoleyi.','local_news','2017-04-13','2017-04-13 11:17:26'),(16,'DAMU LA LIKWENU M’MBOMA LA ZOMBA LIKUFALITSA MATENDA A TAYIFODI','Matenda a tayifodi omwe tsopano akhala akuvuta kwa nthawi yayitali m’boma la Zomba afala malingana ndi kusaikapo mtima kwa anthu pa nkhani zokhuza kusamala madzi omwe anthu a m’bomali amagwiritsa ntchito komanso ukhondo wawo. \r\nMatendawa omwe akhudza kwambiri anthu akumudzi akumadziwika ndi kunjenjemera, kuoneka mwachikasu komanso kufooka kwa munthu wodwalayo zomwe ndi zofanana ndi zizindikiro za matenda a malungo. Koma munthuyo akamuyeza sakumapezeka ndi matenda a malungo. \r\nPakadali pano anthu a m’bomali ali pachiopsezo chodwala matendawa, omwe akhudza anthu ochuluka tsopano zomwe zikuchititsa anthu kukhala mwa mantha. \r\nZimenezi zidachititsa kuti ophunzira a kusukulu ya unamwino ya St. Luke’s komanso sukulu ya sekondale ya Malosa m’bomali, atsekere mwansanga ndi masabata awiri.\r\nTsopano anthu omwe akhudzidwa ndi matendawa ndi ophunzira 200 a pasukulu ya Malosa ndi ena 100 a pasukulu ya St Luke. Chiwerengero cha anthu odwalac ndi chochuluka m’malo omwe mumakhala anthu ambiri ngati m’malo ophunzirirapo.\r\nMkulu wa zaumoyo m’boma la Zomba yemwe wati ofesi yake ikuyesetsa kupeza njira zothetsera matendawa wati akulephera kufotokoza zomwe zikuchititsa kuti chiwerengero cha anthu odwala matendawa chikwere kwambiri ngati momwe zilirimu.\r\nNgakhale izi zili chomwechi, vuto lalikulu ndi loti akuluakulu akulephera kugwirizana za momwe angathetsere chiyambi cha matendawa. \r\nPomwe matendawa akukhudzana kwambiri ndi utchisi, m’derali matendawa akufala mu njira zambirimbiri zokhunzana ndi umve. Anthu odwala matendawa akumakhala ofowoka ndipo kufookaku kukumankirankira chifukwa choothera dzuwa. \r\nOdwala akumafookanso kwambiri pomwe akumakhala akumwa mankhwala a malungo m’malo mwa makhwala a tayifodi chifukwa akumazindikira mochedwa kuti matenda omwe akudwalawo si malungo akapita ku chipatala.','local_news','2017-04-13','2017-04-13 11:17:56'),(17,'Bullets yapitilira mchikho cha Calrsberg','Timu ya Nyasa Bullets dzulo yagonjetsa timu ya Azam Tigers ndi chigoli chimodzi kwa zii mu masewero a m’chikho cha Carlsberg omwe adachitikira pa bwalo la Kamuzu mu mzinda wa Blantyre. Zateremu, timu ya Azam Tigers tsopano yatuluka m’chikhochi.\r\nChigawo choyamba chidatha osagoletsana chigoli chilichonse ngakhale kuti timu ya Azam imasewera bwino ndipo idali ndi mwayi wogoletsa. \r\nKoma Mussa Manyenje wa Bullets adagoletsa chigoli chomwe chidachititsa kuti timu ya Azam iwone khomo lotulukira mu chokhi cha Carlsberg mu chigawo chachiwiri mu mphindi ya 86.\r\nKutsatira kugoletsedwaku, m’phunzitsi wa timu ya Azam adayang’ana kumwamba mosweka mtima kufuna mayankho.\r\nKoma wachiwiri kwa m’phunzitsi wa timu ya Bullets a Mabvuto Lungu adati akadatha kuchita bwino m’malo movutika ndi timu ya Azam.','sports_news','2017-04-13','2018-02-21 10:31:42'),(19,'KOLERA WAKWEKWESA ANTHU 289 - LILONGWE WAKHUDZIDWANSO','Boma latsimikiza kuti anthu 289 ndiwo akhudzidwa ndi matenda otsekula m\'mimba a kolera (Cholera) dziko lonse la Malawi.\r\n\r\nLipoti lomwe akuluakulu ku unduna wa zaumoyo atulutsa dzulo pa 25 January, 2018 laonetsa kuti matendawa akhudza anthu ambiri okhala m\'chigawo chakumpoto.\r\n\r\nPosachedwapa munthu wina wa ku Karonga amupeza ndi nthendayi komanso ena awiri okhala mu mzinda wa LIlongwe.\r\n\r\nAkuluakulu ku unduna wa zaumoyo ati boma likuyembekeza kulandira mankhawala a katemera wa matenda a kolerawa kuchokera ku mangalande mothandizidwa ndi bungwe loona za umoyo pa dziko lonse la World Health Organisation (WHO).\r\n\r\nAnthu akupemphedwa kusamba m\'manja akachoka kuchimbudzi, kuvindikira zakudya popewetsa ntchentche komanso kuwiritsa madzi omwe akuganiziridwa kuti si abwino ngati mbali imodzi yothetsa ndi matendawa.\r\n\r\nMatenda a Kolera amapha mwachidule ngati odwala sathamangira kuchipatala.\r\n\r\n','local_news','2018-01-26','2018-01-26 14:17:02'),(20,'Zipani zotsutsa azichenjeza','Akatsiwiri pa nkhani za ndale achenjeza zipani za ndale zomwe ndi zotsutsa boma kuti ngati atsogoleri a zipanizi atapitiliza mikangano komanso kusagwilizana, palibe chomwe adzaphule pa chisankho cha 2019.\r\nAkatswiriwa omwenso achenjeza chipani cholamula cha DPP ati ngakhale kuti mikangano ifikanso mu chipani cha DPP,  zipani zotsutsa ndizomwe zingavutike kwambiri ngati atsogoleri saziyankhula liu limodzi ati kamba koti chipani cha DPP chili ndi kuthekera kogwiritsa ntchito zinthu za boma kuti alimbane ndi zipani zotsutsazi.\r\nM\'modzi wa akatsiwiriwa ndi a Happy Kayuni omwe amaphunzitsa pa sukulu ya za ukachenjede ya Chancellor College mu mzinda wa Zomba.\r\nA kayuni ati zipani zotsutsa zikuyenera kugwirizana ndi cholinga choti asapereke mpata ku chipani cholamula kuti chitengerepo mwai pa zofooka zawo.\r\nKatswiri winanso pa ndale a George Phiri a ku sukulu ya ukachenjede ya Livingstonia wauza nyuzipepapala ya The Nation kuti kupitilira kukangana mzipani zotsutsa kupereka mwai kuti chipani cha DPP chidzapambane pa chisankho ckubwerachi. A phiri ati kusamvanaku ngati kukafika ku Msonkhano waukulu wa zipanizi , nzachidziwikire kuti mavuto akakhalapo ochuluka.\r\nNaye mkulu owona zomenyela ma ufulu a anthu a Timothy Mtambo wati ngati atsogoleri akuplephera kuthetsa mavuto omwe akukumana nawo mzipani , nzovuta kuti anthu awakhulupilire kuti angathetse mavuto a mdziko.\r\nMwachiysanzo iwo ati kuchotsedwa kwa a Richard Msowoya , Gustave Kaliwo komanso mai Jessie Kabwila pa maudindo awo mchipa cha MCP kuchititsa kuti anthu ochokawa agawanitse anthu\r\nChupani china chomwe mwabukanso mpungwepungwe ndi cha Peoples - PP chomwe chinachotsa a Uladi Mussa, Ralph Jooma, komanso Werani Chilenga pa maudindo ati kamba kopanga zinthu zosemphana ndi chipani.\r\n\r\nPakadalipano zipani zotsutsazi zauwa The Nation kuti anthu asadye mfulumira poganiza kuti kusagwiriza kulipoku kungadzalepheretse zipanizi kulowa m\'boma.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n','local_news','2018-01-30','2018-02-21 10:35:06'),(21,'Manoma Zawakanika - Sapita ku kukasewera mu CAF','Akatswiri a ligi yayikulu ya mpira wa miyendo mdzikomuno ya TNM a Mighty Be Forward Wanderers omwe amadziwika bwino kuti MANOMA alephera kukachita nawo mpikisano wa ma timu otsogola m\'maiko a mu WA CAF pazifukwa zomwe sizinafotokozedwe bwino.\r\nMalipoti ochokerea pa masamba osiyanasiyana a pa internet akusonyeza kuti omwe amathandiza timuyi a Beforward Wanderers ndiokhumudwa kamba ka kunyanyala-nyala komwe osewera mu timuyi akhala akuchita ndicholinga chofuna kukakamiza akulu-akulu oyendetsa timuyi kuti awapatse ndalama zawo.\r\nMANOMA amayenera kunyamuka sabata la mawa kupita mdziko la Congo ( DRC)  komwe pa 11 mwezi uno amayenera kuthambitsana ndi timu ya  AS Vita m\'masewero awo oyamba. Chikonzero chawo chinali choti pa ulendo wawo, ayamba asewera masewero opimana mphamvu ndi timu ya Nyasa Big Bullets loweruka likudzali kenako akaime  mdziko la Zambia komwe amafuna kukasewera masewero opimana mphamvu ena ndi timu ya Red Arrows.\r\nMANOMA adakhazikitsa ntchito yosaka ndalama zoti timuyi ithandizikire popita ku mpikisanowu koma kufikira lero zinthu sizinadyere. \r\nZateremu maso ali ku timu ya Masters Security yomwenso idalembetsa kuti ikachita nawo mpikisanowu ngakhale anthu ena akhala akunena kuti timuyi yachepa nazo ndipo ikadayamba yadikira kuti ikhwime.','sports_news','2018-02-01','2018-02-21 10:31:02'),(22,'Njala tithana nayo - Watero Mutharika','Mtsogoleri wa dziko a Peter Mutharika wati anthu asadandaule ndi njala yomwe ikuyembekezeka kukhalako chakachino kamba ka ng\'amba, ponena kuti boma linasunga chimanga chambiri mu nkhokwe zake.\r\nA Mutharika amayankhula izi lamulungu ku Nchalo komwe anachititsa msonkhano. Iwo ati akuzindikila kuti anthu ambiri ali pa chiopsezo cha njala ndipo sakolora moyenera kamba koti mvula sikugwa bwino m\'madera ambiri.\r\n\" Ine ndi boma langa tinasunga chimanga chambiri chokwanira anthu omwe akhudzidwe ndi njala. Anthu ena ankafuna nditagulitsa chimanga chonse koma ndinaletsa ndipo ankati sindinachite bwino, koma nanga lero taonani\" anatero a Mutharika.\r\nKupatula njomba pa kabweredwe ka mvula, m\'madera ambiri, tizilombo taononganso mbewu zambiri  ndipo akatswiri a kafuku-fuku wa zamalimidwe mu unduna wa zamalimidwe ndi chitukuko cha madzi sanapezebe njira yachangu yophera tizilomboti.\r\nChaka chatha dziko la Malawi lidakolola chimanga chochuluka zomwe zidachititsa kuti mitengo yake nayo ikhale yotsika ndipo ambiri sadapeze phindu.\r\nBungwe losamalira nkhokwe zachimanga la National Food Reserve Agency NFRA linagula chimanga chochuluka kuchokera kwa alimi mdzikomuno.\r\nMchaka cha 2016 njala idasautsanso kwambiri zomwe zidachititsa boma kuitanitsa chimanga kuchokera ku maiko akunja kuphatikizapo dziko la Zambia.','local_news','2018-02-05','2018-02-21 10:34:30'),(23,'Bullets Ithambitsa Masters Security','Fischer Kondowe komanso Chiukepo Msowoya anadzetsa chimwemwe ku timu ya Nyasa Big Bullets yomwe lamulungu lapitali  imachita masewero opimana mphamvu ndi timu ya Masters Security yomwe ikuyembekezeka kusewera masewero ake oyamba mu mpikisano wa CAF sabata ya Mawa.\r\nBullets inayamba masewerowa ndi cholinga maka pozindikila kuti neba (Manoma) cha dzulo lake anawayimba kuti alowetse basi mbwalomo kuti iwachinyire zigoli potsatira kugonja kwawo ndi timuyi ndi zigoli ziwiri kwa du apa masewero enanso opimana mphamvu omwe manoma anachita ndi Nyasa Big Bullets pokonzekera mpikisano omweu. Aka kanali koyamba kuti osewera a Nyasa Big Bullets akwere bus yapamwamba yomwe yagulidwa posachdwapa.\r\nZaterumu timu ya Masters yalephera masewero ake onse atatu omwe yasewera pokonzekera  mpikasonowu. Koyamba adagonja ndi Manoma ndi zigoli zinayi kwa du, kenako adafanana mphamvu  ndi Timu ya TN Stars  yomwe  yakwezekedwa kumene kumenya ligi yayikulu atalepherana ndi zigoli ziwiri kwa ziwiri.\r\nPa masewero omwe analipo ndi timu ya Nyasa Big Bullets Masters Security inayamba kudzitolera mchigawo chachiwiri koma nkuti zinthu zitathina kale.\r\nMphunzitsi wamkulu wa Masters Security Abas Makawa  wati wati anyamata ake otseka kumbuyo sanasewere bwino kamba koti zigoli zomwe achinyidwa sizimayenera kukhala zigoli ndipo wati akonza mavutowa asananyamuke kupita ku mpikisanowu. \r\nMasters Security isewera masewero ake omaliza okonzekera ulendowu ndi timu ya Silver Strikers lachiwiri pa 6 February pa bwalo la Masewero la Bingu.\r\nKumbali yake othandizira mphunzitsi wamkulu ku timu ya Nyasa Big Bullets a Eliya Kananji anati osewera ambiri anasewera bwino ndipo anatengerapo mwai oyesera osewera ena atsopano omwe agwire ntchito ku timuyi mchakachi.','sports_news','2018-02-05','2018-02-21 10:30:09'),(24,'Alimi afodya apha makwacha - TCC','Pali kuthekera koti alimi omwe anachilimika kulima fodya chakachino apha makwacha ochuluka kamba koti chiwerengero cha fodya yense yemwe walimidwa mdzikomuno chatsika ndi makilogalamu khumi ndi mphambu ziwiri pa zana lililonse (12kg) poyerekeza ndi fodya yemwe akufunidwa ndi ogula.\r\nOgula adauza bungwe loyang\'anira za malonda a fodya mdzikomuno la Tobacco Control Commission TCC kuti akufuna ma kilogalamu 171 million a fodya wa mitundu yosiyanasiyana.\r\nZotsatira za kafukufuku oyamba yemwe bungwe la TCC linachita  waonetsa kuti ma kilogalamu osachepera 149 million ndi omwe angapezeke pa msika.\r\nBungwe la TCC lati chiwerengerochi chitsikirapo  mwa zina ati kamba koti  ng\'amba inafalikira madera ambiri ndikuchititsa kuti alimi abzale mochedwa komanso kuti fodya asakule bwino.\r\nMkulu wa TCC a Kaisi Sadala wati achitanso kafukufuku otsiriza ndipo kuthekera kulipo kuti zinthu zikhoza kusintha.Kafukufuku  omaliza ayambe pa 26 February ndipo adzatha pa 10 March, 2018.\r\nAlimi afodya 41,000 ndiwo adalembetsa ku TCC kuti alima ma kilogalamu a fodya osachepera 162 million. \r\nM\'mau ake mkulu wa bungwe la alimi a fodya mdzikomuno la TAMA a Mathews Zulu ati ndiokondwa kuti chiwerengerochi chakwera poyerekeza ndi chakachatha pomwe alimi adalima ma kilogalamu 124 million okha ndipo anaonjezera kuti akuyembekeza mitengo yabwino ngakhale kuti zitengeranso ndi ubwino wa fodya.\r\nChakachatha ndalama zochoka ku Malonda onse a Fodya zinatsika kufika  pa 155 billion kwacha kuchoka pa 201 billion kwacha mchaka cha 2016.','local_news','2018-02-09','2018-02-21 10:33:54'),(25,'Manoma ndi Masters akuti nkhondo akamenya pa galaundi','Matimu a Mighty Beforward Wanderes kapena kuti MANOMA ndi Masters Security ati nkhondo akamenya pa galaundi pomwe akuyamba masewero awo a mpikisano wa Confederation of African Footbal  (CAF) omwe matimu osewera ma ligi osiyanasiyana ochokera mu Africa amalimbirana chikho.\r\nTimu ya Masters Security ndiyomwe itayambe kusadzulana ndi Timu ya Atletico Petroleos ya mdziko la Angola loweruka pomwe Manoma ayamba masewero awo lamulungu pomwe akumane ndi AS vita ya mdziko la Congo.\r\nMlembi wamkulu wa timu ya Masters a Zachariah Nyirenda ati ngakhale kuti sanachite bwino m\'masewero opimana mphamvu omwe anasewero pakatipa, ali ndi chiyembekezo kuti zinthu zikayenda. Pa masewero atatu omwe anali nawo ndi ma timu a Nyasa Big Bullets, Wanderers , ndi TN Stars Masters inapambana masewero amodzi okha pomwe anagonjetsa TN Stars ndi zigoli zinayi kwa zitatu.\r\nEna mwa osewera atsopano a Masters omwe apita ku Angola ndi monga Chimwemwe Kumkwawa,Zeliat NKhoma, Suwedi Limbani, Rafik Mussa komanso Kondwani Lufeyo.\r\nKumbali yawo Manoma kudzera kwa wachiwiri kwa otsogolera timuyi Alfred Manyozo Junior, ati masapota awo ayembekeze zabwino.\r\nVita ndi akatsiwiri mu ligu yaku DRC pomwe kuno kumudzi Manoma ndiwo akusunganso chikho zomwe zikupereka chiymebekezo kuti wankhodzo zapusi, uliko kumeneko.','sports_news','2018-02-09','2018-02-21 10:29:41'),(26,'Imfa ya Sam Mpasu yakhudza ambiri','Imfa ya m\'modzi mwa anthu odziwika bwino pa ndale komanso zolembalemba a Sam Mpasu yakhudza anthu ambiri mdzikomuno omwe ati munthuyi anali okhazikika komanso katakwe mu zinthu zambiri.\r\n\r\nA Sam Mpasu omwe anakhalapo nduna ya boma komanso sipika wa nyumba ya malamulo anapezeka atamwalira kuchipinda komwe amagona- kunyumba kwawo lachinayi m\'mawa.\r\n\r\nMalinga ndi kauniuni yemwe madotolo a ku sukulu ya ukachenjede wa zaumoyo ya College of Medicine anachita , apeza kuti a Mpasu anamwalira kamba ka vuto la kuthamanga kwa mtima (BP).\r\n\r\nApolisi ndiwo anapeza thupi la a Sam Mpasu kuchipinda kwawo potsatira lipoti lomwe musuweni wa malemuwa anakapereka kupolisi.\r\n\r\nNkhani ikuti mwana wina wa malemu a Mpasu yemwe amakhala kunja kwa dziko lino (UK) anaimbira msuweni  wake yemwe akudziwika kuti bambo Wasi kuti apite kunyumba akaone bambo ake kamba koti wakhala akulephera kulumikizana nawo pa lamya ya m\'manja. Popeza unali usiku m\'malo mwake a Wasi analawira kunyumbako m\'mawa ndipo atafika kunyumbako anapeza windo la kuchipinda lili lotsekula koma akuoneka chigonele pa kama lawo. Poopsedwa ndi zomwe anaona bambo Wasi anayitana apolisi ndikutsekula zitseko mokakamiza ndipo apa ndipomwe anawepeza atamwalira.\r\n\r\nMtsogoleri wakale wa dziko lino a Dr Bakili Muluzi omwe anagwirapo ntchito kwambiri ndi a Mpasu pa nthawi yomwe anali ku chipani cha UDF wati a Mpasu anali munthu olimba mtima pa ndale komanso olimbika pa mfundo zomwe amakhulupilira.\r\n\r\nNdipo nduna yofalitsa nkhani a  Nicholas Dausi ati dziko la Malawi lataya munthu ofunika yemwe anatenga nawo gawo lalikulu pa ntchito yoptititsa patsogolo ufulu wa demokalase.\r\n\r\nMneneri wa chipani cha MCP a Ezekiel Ching’oma wati chipani cha MCP chakhudzidwa ndi imfayi maka polingalira  kuti a Mpasu anali munthu yemwe sanali otengengeka pa zilizonse komanso wanzeru.\r\n\r\nKupatula ndale a Mpasu amakonda kulemba ndipo adasindikizapo mabuku osiyanasiyana. Ichi nchifukwa chake m\'modzi wa anthu okonda zolembelemba a Alfred Msadala ati malemu a Mpasu anali ndi luso komanso amalemekeza luso la zolembalemba.\r\n\r\n\" A ,Mpasu sadakhale pansi kumandiphunzitsa kulemba koma kalembedwe kawo kamapatsa chikoka kotero kuti kumakhala kovuta kuti owerenga asiyire panjira osamaliza zomwe amasindikiza\" atero a Sadala.\r\n\r\nA Mpasu amwalira ali ndi zaka 73 ndipo asiya ana asanu ndi m\'modzi. Mwambo oyika m\'manda thupi la a Mpasu uchitika sabata yomwe ino akafika ana omwe alikunja kwa dziko lino.','local_news','2018-02-16','2018-02-21 10:33:26'),(27,'','','local_news','2018-02-16','2018-02-16 10:43:50'),(28,'Madzi osefukira, ng\'amba zavuta ku Phalombe','Madzi osefukira kamba ka mvula ya mphamvu achititsa kuti maanja 329 akhudzidzwe zomwe zinachititsanso kuti wachiwiri kwa mtsogoleri wa dziko lino a Saulos Chilima akayendere anthuwa ndikuwapatsa kangachepe kochokera ku boma.\r\n\r\nMadzi osefukirawa akhudza midzi isanu ndi umodzi ya  Likatchale, Mwanyewe, Hamela, Nampinga, Tibu ndi Harapera yomwe ili m\'mudzi mwa mfumu yayikulu Kaduya\r\n\r\nZina mwa zinthu zomwe zapelekedwa kwa anthuwa ndi monga makapu , mapepala a pulasitiki, mbale komanso ma bulangete mwa zina.\r\n\r\nPoyankhula ku Phalombe a chilima omwenso anapatsidwa ntchito yolimbana ndi kuchepetsa ngozi zogwa mwa dzidzidzi  ati dziko la Malawi likuyenera kulimbikitsa ndondomeko zomwe zingathandize kukweza ntchitozi kuti anthu asamavutike kawirikawiri.\r\n\r\nIwo ati misewu ndiyofunika kukonzedwa komanso mtsinje wa Namphende omwe umachititsa kuti madzi asefukire ndiofunika kuukumbanso ati kamba koti unakwililika zomwe zimachititsa kuti madzi adzisiya njira yake ndikuoononga nyumba, katundu komanso miyoyo ya anthu ambiri.\r\n\r\nKomabe a chilima ati kuti izi zitheke mpofunika ndalama.\r\n\r\nIwo ati ndondomeko ya boma yomangira anthu nyumba zamalata ndi zooneka bwino ithandizanso kuchepetsa chiwerengero cha anthu okhudzidwa pa ngozi za mtunduwu ati kamba koti nyumbazi zikamangidwa bwino zimapilira ku ngozi.\r\n\r\nBwanankubwa wa boma la Phalombe a Gossam Mafuta wati nzovetsa chisoni kuti kupatula kusefukira kwa madziku, bomali linakhudzidwanso ndi vuto la ng\'amba.\r\nBoma la Phalombe ndi limodzi lomwe limakhudzidwa ndi ngozi zogwa mwadzidzidzi kamba ka kuonongeka kwa zachilengedwe.\r\n','local_news','2018-02-16','2018-02-21 10:32:50'),(29,'Waya Wapsa wa ku Mangalande!','Mary Waya yemwe ndikatakwe pa nkhani za mpira wa ntchembere mbaye wapeza ntchito ku Mangalande komwe akhale akuphunzitsa timu ina kumeneko.\r\nMalipoti akuti a Waya asayinira mgwirizano wa chaka chimodzi ndi timuyo ndipo anasankhidwa kamba koti Timu ya dziko lino yakhala ikuchita bwino pa masewero ake.\r\nMkulu wa timuyi yomwe ndi mavericks a Ratnapala  wati ali ndichiyembekezo kuti a Waya komanso anthu ena omwe awalemba ntchito athandiza kukweza ntchito za timuyi.\r\n\r\nWaya anasewerapo timu ya ntchembere mbaye ya dziko lino ndipo wakhalanso akuthandizira kuphunzitsa. A Waya asankhidwa patangodutsa masabat aochepa pomwe  anauzidwa kuti sakuyenera kuhunzitsanso timu ya ntchembere mbaye ya dziko lino kamba koti a Griffin Saenda ndi omwe abwelera kugwira ntchitoyi.\r\nChiyitengereni timu ya ntchembere mabaye ya dziki linoyi yalephera masewero okwana khumi zomwe akatswiri a zamasewero ati szabwino.\r\n','sports_news','2018-02-16','2018-02-21 10:28:33'),(30,'Buju ndi mzake amangidwa kamba koopseza ndi mfuti','Anthu anayi ali mchitokosi cha apolisi atamagwidwa kamba kowaganizira kuti amachita mchitidwe oopseza ndikuba katundu pogwiritsa ntchito Mfuti.\r\n\r\nAnayiwa ndi a  Marumbo Mkandawire a zaka  20, Victor Granta zaka  25, Andrew Bulawayo omwe amatchuka kuti Buju wa zaka 22 komanso Khasu Felix wa zaka 26. Onsewa amachokera ku Naperi ku Blantyre.\r\n\r\nAnthuwa anamangidwa lachitatu ndipo awamanga milandu yopezeka ndi mfuti popanda chilolezo.\r\n\r\nMneneri wa apoli ku Blantyre a Augustus Nkhwazi wati teketivu odziwika bwino kuchokera ku LIlongwe a Bob Mtekama ndiye wamanga anthuwa\r\n\r\nApolisi ati adalandira lipoti loti anthu ena omwe akupezeka pa malo ena omwera zakumwa zoziritsa kukhosi ndi zoledzeretsa akumaopsezedwa ndi anthu ena omwe sakudziwika bwino koma ali ndi mfuti ndipo atawatsatira anawapeza ndikuwamanga.\r\n\r\nAnayiwa akusungidwa ku polisi ya Soche ku Blantyre komweko ndipo akaonekera ku bwalo lamilandu zofufuza zikatha','local_news','2018-02-16','2018-02-21 10:32:15'),(31,'Aphungu Ojomba Azidulidwa Ndalama - Sipika','20th February, 2018\r\nAphungu akunyumba ya malamulo omwe ali ndi chizolowezi chosapezeka m\'nyumba ya malamulo pomwe anzawo akuchita zokambirana tsopano aziwadula ndalama zomwe amalandira.\r\nSipikala wa nyumba ya malamuloyi a Richard Msowoya alengeza izi lolemba komiti yomwe imakonza zokambirana m\'nyumbayi itakambirana za mchitidwewu.\r\nMasiku apitawa olembe nkhani akhala akujambula zithunzi komanso kulemba kuti aphungu ambiri sakumaoneka mnyumbayi angakhale kuti pochoka kumudziko amati akukaimilira anthu awo mzokambirana zosiyansiyana m\'nyumbayi.\r\nChoimitsa mutu chinali choti pomwe sipikalayu amalengeza izi nkuti m\'nyumbayi muli aphungu khumi asanu ndi m\'modzi a mbali ya boma komanso oima paokha, komanso makumi atatu okha kumbali ya otsutsa. Izi zinali chomwechi ngakhale kuti nyumbayi ili ndi aphungu okwana 190.\r\nKomabe anthu ena ati ali ndi chikaiko ngati izi zingalolondezedwe pozindikira kuti aka sikoyamba kuti aphunguwa achenjezedwe zodulidwa ndalama.\r\nAphunguwa amalandila 50 , 0000 pa tsiku ndipo amalandiliratu asanayambe zokambirana zawo kuphatikizaponso ndalama yamafuta.\r\nMkumano wa aphungu wa pakadalipano umaunika momwe ndondomeko ya zachuma cha boma yakhala ikuyendera ndipo akhala akukumana kwa masabata anayi.\r\nZokambirana zawo zitha lachisanu pa 2 March, 2018.','local_news','2018-02-20','2018-02-21 10:10:05'),(32,'Ma Jaji Ochedwetsa Milandu Azilangidwa','20th  February, 2018\r\n\r\nAnthu ambiri mdziko muno amadandaula ndi mchitidwe wa ma Jaji kapena kuti oweruza milandu ena omwe amakhalira nkhani kwa zakazaka asanapereke chigamulo kapena kuyamba kuweruza, zinthu zomwe zimazunzitsa anthu okhudzidwa.\r\nPa msonkhano omwe oweruza milanduwa anali nawo m\'boma la Mangochi, mkulu owona zamilandu ku ma bwalo akulu Agnes Patemba anauza oweruza milanduwa kuti aliyense ochedwetsa milandu azikaonekera ku komiti yomwe imawalemba ntchito kuti akafotokoze zifukwa zawo ndipo ngati ndisosamveka apatsidwa chilango motsatana ndo malamulo a ntchito.\r\nKugwirizanaku kwadza Mkulu wa ma khoti mdzikomuno a Justice Andrew Nyirenda atadandaula ndi mchitidwe wa ena mwa oweruza milanduwa omwe amatenga nthawi milandu yawo isanathe.\r\nAnthu ambiri kuphatikizapo bungwe la oyimilira anthu pa milandu la Malawi Law Society akhala akudandaula za izi.\r\nPakadalipano mkulu wina omenyera ufulu wa anthu a Robert Mkwezalamba wauza nyuzipepapala ya Nation yomwe yasindikizanso  nkhaniyi kuti zomwe agwirizanazo ndizabwino ndipo amalawi ayembekeza kuti aone kusintha.\r\nPakatipa pakhala pakutuluka nkhani za anthu omwe atha zaka zambiri ali ku ndende koma milandu yawo sinaweruzidwe zomwe ndikuphwanya ufulu wawo.','local_news','2018-02-20','2018-02-21 10:09:11'),(33,'Cholera Wapha Anthu  9','20th January, 2018\r\n\r\nChiwerengero cha anthu omwe amwalira kamba ka matenda a cholera tsopano chafika pa asanu ndi anayi 9 , unduna wa zaumoyo watsimikiza izi mchikalata chomwe atulutsa. Undunawu watinso ukuchita chotheka kuthandiza kuti matendawa asapitilire kufalikira kwa anthu ochuluka.\r\nPakadalipano chiwerengero cha anthu omwe akhudzidwa ndi matendawa dziko lonse la Malawi chafika pa 541 kuchokera pa 527. Maboma 13 ndi omwe akhudzidwa kwambiri ngakhale kuti boma la Karonga ndikomwe kuli chiwerengero chokwera cha anthu 273 motsatana ndi LIlongwe komwe anthu 163 akhudzidwa.Ku salima anthu 44 ndiwo akhudzidwa pomwe ku Nkhata Bay chiwerengero chili pa 20.\r\nPakadalipano anthu mazanamazana m\'boma la Karonga akuyembekezeka kuyamba kulandira Katemera wa matenda a Cholera yemwe boma mothandizidwa ndi mabungwe ena anaitanitsa kuchokera ku maiko a kunja.\r\n','local_news','2018-02-20','2018-02-21 10:06:27'),(34,'Ndinakhonza Mayeso - Watero Gabeya','20th February, 2018\r\n\r\nKatswiri otchinga kumbuyo kwa timu ya Nyasa Big Bullets Miracle Gabeya wati chomwe iye akudziwa ndichoti anachita bwino ku mayeso omwe anakachita ku timu ya Highlands Park mdziko la South Africa ndikuti pano akungodikira mgwirizano pakati pa timu ya Nysa BIg Bullets ndi Hghlands Park kuti amvane asanayambe kusewera kumeneko.\r\n\"Ineyo ndinapambana, ndikungodikira akuluakulu akambirane koma sindikukaika , pompano ndibwereranso ku South Africa kuti ndikasewere kumeneko\" anatero Gabeya poyankhula ndi olemba nkhani wa nyuzipepala ya Nation.\r\nMkulu wa timu ya Nyasa Big Bullets a Fleetwood Haiya wati iwo akudikira timu ya HIghlands kuti iwafotokozere momwe zotsatira za Gabeya zinayendera.\r\n\" Ife tikudikira anzathu ku South Africa kuti atiuze bwino bwino m\'mene osewera wathu anachitira , koma pakadalipano Gabeya timulembetsabe pa m\'ndandanda wa osewera omwe akhale ku timuyi m\'masewero a ligi yayikulu a TNM\"  watero Haiya\r\nHaiya watinso akukumana ndi zovuta zomwezi ndi Emmanuel Zoya yemwe akuyenera kupita ku timu ya Red Arrows ku Zambia\r\n\r\n','sports_news','2018-02-20','2018-02-21 10:12:04'),(35,'Njenjenje! -Okhaulitsa Manoma, Masters Security Afika','20th February, 2018\r\n\r\nAmbiri akusimbabe za chitonzo chomwe matimu a Masters Security komanso Be forward Wanderers FC anakumana nacho atasewera ndi anzawo aku DRC komanso Angola sabata yapitayo.\r\nMasters inabwerako ndi zigoli zisanu kwa du itasewera ndi Atletico Petroleos ya ku Angola pomwe Manoma anasenza zawo zokwana zinayi kwa chilowere atasewera ndi As VIta ya ku DRC.\r\nLachiwiri masana Masters Security ikuchita masewero ake achibwereza pa bwalo za masewero la Bingu ndipo mphunzitsi wawo Abasi Makawa wapempha osewera ake kuti amenye nkhodo mosafooka.\r\nAkatswiri ena ati ngakhale kuti chikhulupiliro chimasuntha mapiri komanso kuti mpira ndiozungulira ndizovuta kwambiri kuti timu ya Masters igoletse zigoli zisanu ndi chimodzi kuti apambane mu mpikisanowu omwe ndi wa matimu a mu Africa osewera ma ligi osiyanasiyana.\r\nPalibe kuthawa zagwa zatha, lachitatu Manoma akumana ndi AS Vita kuti abweze ngongole komanso chipongwe chomwe adachiona ku DRC.\r\nMphunzitsi wa Manoma Ysin Osman posachedwapa adati mulungu yekha ndiye akudziwa zomwe zidzachitike patsikuli , ndipo anati sizingakhale zophweka kupambana ndi zigoli zisanu.\r\nAkatswiri ena pa zamasewero akhala akunena kuti matimuwa chomwe angachite ndikuchepetsa ngongole komanso chitonzo chomwe anachiona ndikuti ndizovuta kuti apambane.\r\nMatimuwa obwerawa akuoneka kuti zokonzekera zawo zinali bwino ndipo ali ndi ndalama zokwanira kamba koti mwachitsanzo timu ya ku Angola yabwera pa ndege ya hayala pomwe kuno kumudzi matimu ali mu ngongole kamba kochitana nawo masewerowa.\r\n','sports_news','2018-02-20','2018-02-21 10:11:22'),(36,'Mulandu wa Bakili Muluzi ukupitilirabe','Mulandu wa Dr. Bakili Muluzi yemwe anakhalapo mtsogoleri wa dziko lino ukupitilirabe ngakhale kuti patha zaka khumi ndi mphambu ziwiri ukadali ku bwalo la milandu.\r\nPakatipa mlanduwu udayamba waimitsidwa ati kamba koti a Muluzi adapempha bwalo lalikulu lamilandu kuti lichotse gawo 32(2) la Malamulo okhudza za katangale kuti lisakhale lamulo ponena kuti limatsutsana ndi gawo 42 la Malamulo a dziko lino.\r\nGawo 32 la malamulo othetsa katangale limati munthu yemwe adzafufuzidwa ndikupezeka kuti akukhala moyo wapamwamba osagwirizana ndi chuma chomwe anali nacho kapena ali nacho adzapezeka olakwa pa mlandu wa katangale.\r\nLamuloli malingana ndi oyimiilira a Muluzi ati likutsutsana ndi gawo 42 la Malamulo a dziko lino lomwe limati munthu aliyense ali ndi ufulu osayankha mafunso mu bwalo lamilandu ndikuti munthu oteroyo sadzatengedwa olakwa mpaka bwalo la milandu litamupeza chomwecho.\r\n\r\nKoma ma mulumuzana oweruza milandu okwana atatu omwe ndi Jaji Dingiswayo Madisi, Dorothy Nyakaunda Komanso Jack Nriva ataunika za pempho la Dr Muluzi agamula kuti sizingatheke kuti lamulori alichotse ati kamba kamba koti silamulo loyima palokha ndipo likhonza kuchepetsedwa mphamvu ndi malamulo ena.\r\n\r\nMa Jajiwa atinso kukhala chete ku bwalo la milandu sikotetezedwa kwa thunthu ndipo ati kuti lamulori lichotsedwe anthu azichita katangale mdzikomuno ndipo kuzikhala kovuta kuwafufuza.\r\nDr Muluzi amaganiziridwa kuti anasokoneza ndalama za boma zosachepera 1.7 billion kwacha  pa nthawi yomwe anali mtsogoleri.\r\nDr Muluzi ndi mtsogoleri oyamba mu ulamuliro wa demokalase ndipo anamangidwa koyamba mchaka cha 2006.','local_news','2018-02-22','2018-02-22 12:02:00'),(37,'Akufa ndi Kolera akwana 12 -Lilongwe ali pa chiopsezo','23/02/18\r\n\r\nLipoti lomwe unduna wa za umoyo watulutsa likusonyeza kuti chiwerengero cha anthu omwe amwalira ndi matenda a kolera tsopano chafika pa khumi ndi  ziwiri (12).\r\nChiwerengerochi chakwera anthu ena awiri atamwaliranso ndi nthendayi pa zipatala zazing\'ono za Matapila komanso Kang\'oma zomwe zili pansi pa mfumu yayikulu Tsabango ku Lilongwe.\r\nOfalitsa nkhani ku unduna wa za umoyo a Joshua Malango ati nacho chiwerengero cha anthu omwe akhudzidwa ndi matendawa chachoka pa 546 kufika pa 560 zomwe wati ndizodandaulitsa kwambiri.\r\nA Malango ati chiwerengero cha anthu okhudzidwa ndi matendawa chikukwera chomwechi kamba koti anthu ambiri sakutsatira ndondomeko za ukhondo komanso akumapita kuchipatala mochedwa zinthu zitavuta kale.\r\nUndunawu sabata yomwe ino unadzudzula anthu ena omwe ati akumachedwa nkupita kwa sing\'anga pomwe munthu amva mthupi poganizira kuti nzaufiti m\'malo mothamangira ku chipatala.  \r\nBoma la Koronga lili ndi anthu 281 omwe apezeka ndi matendawa chomwe ndi chiwerengero chokwera kwambiri motsogozana ndi Lilongwe komwe anthu 171 ndi omwe apezeka ndi matendawa. \r\n\r\nMaboma ena omwe akhudzidwa ndi nthendayi ndi kuphatikizapo Salima, NKhata Bay , Likoma, Nsanje, Rumphi, Dowa, Mulanje, Dedza, Kasungu, Blantyre ndi Chikwawa.\r\nPakadalipano ntchito yopeleka katemela wa Kolera  kwa anthu a m\'boma la Karonga ilimkati ndipo mgawo lachiwiri ntchitoyi ifikira ma boma ena okhudzidwa.\r\nBungwe la zaumoyo padziko lonse la WHO limati matenda a Kolera amadza kamba ka kudya zakudya kapena kumwa madzi omwe alowa tizilombo toyambitsa matendawa.','local_news','2018-02-23','2018-02-23 15:02:10'),(38,'Kalembera wa unzika akupitilirabe','23/02/18\r\n\r\nBungwe lowona za kalembera mdzikomuno lati ntchito yolemba nzika za dziko lino mu kaundula wa nzika yayambiranso m\'maboma onse 28 a dziko lino.\r\nChikalata chomwe bungweli latulutsa chomwe wasayina ndi ofalitsa nkhani ku bungweli a Norman Fulatira chati bungweli likulingaliranso kuti ntchitoyi izichitikira ku malo omwe kuli ma positi ofesi kuti ayandikirane ndi anthu omwe ali kutali,  poonjezera pa kalembera yemwe akuchitika ku ma ofesi a  Bwanankubwa. \r\nChikalatachi chapempha nzika za dziko lino zomwe ndizopitilira zaka khumi, zisanu ndi mphambu ziwiri 16 kuti ngati sizinalembetse zichite changu kukalembetsa.\r\nPakadalipano nzika zokwana 9.1 million ndi zomwe zinalembetsa mu kaundulayu ndipo ntchito yopereka ziphaso ili mkati.\r\n\r\nBungwe la zachisankho linalengeza kuti lizagwiritsanso ntchito ziphasozi polemba kaundula wa voti komanso kuzindikira nzika za dziko lino pa nthawi yoponya voti.','local_news','2018-02-23','2018-02-23 15:01:45'),(39,'Katangale wafikapo ku Malawi - Lipoti','23/02/18\r\nLipoti lomwe latulutsa bungwe lina lokhazikika bwino ndipo limachita kafukufuku pa momwe maiko akugwilira ntchito zawo posachita zakabisira ndi zachinyengo lasonyeza kuti mchitidwe wa ziphuphu komanso katangale ukupitilira mdzikomuno.\r\nLipotili lomwe amatulutsa ndi a Transparency International lasonyeza kuti dziko la Malawi  lili pa nambala 122 chakachino kuchoka pa nambala 120 chaka chatha pa mndandanda wa maiko omwe umasonyeza momwe ntchito zopewe mchitidwewu pakagwiridwa ka ntchito za boma ukuyendera.\r\nPakadalipano katsiwiri pa nkhani za chuma Prof. Ben Kalua a ku Chancellor College ati  zotsatirazi zikusonyeza kuti dziko la Malawi silikuchilimika pa ntchito yolimbana ndi katangale zinthu zomwe zingathamangitsenso a nthu a bizinesi.\r\nA Jeffrey Kabondo omwe ndi m\'modzi wa akuluakulu a bungwe la Integrity Platform lomwenso ndi membala wa bungwe lomwe latulutsa lipotili ati mpofunika mbali zonse zokhudzidwa zigwirane manja ndikuyamba kutengapo gawo polimbana ndi katangale komanso ziphuphu.\r\n\r\nNayae ofalitsa nkhani ku bumgwe lolimbana ndi katangale komanso ziphuphu la Anti Corruption Bureau -ACB a Egrita Ndala ati ku mbali yawo akuyesetsa kuchita mbali yawo.\r\n\r\nMneneri wa boma a Nicholos Dusi ati amalawi asataye chikhulupiliro kamba koti malikisi omwe patsidwa sanasinthe kwa zaka zitatau zomwe zikutanthauza kuti ntchito ikugwirika bwino.','local_news','2018-02-23','2018-02-23 15:01:29'),(40,'George Nyirenda tsopano ndi osewera wa ku Namibia','23/02/18\r\n\r\nGeorge Nyirenda yemwe anali katswiri otseka kumbuyo kwa timu ya Nyasa Big Bullets ayamba kusewera ku timu ya mdziko la Namibia.\r\nIzi zachitika patangodutsa masabata atatu pomwe timu ya Nyasa Big Bullets inachotsa ntchito osewerayu ku timuyi.\r\nUnchindami Kaira yemwe ndi mkhalapakati pakati pa George Nyirenda ndi timu ya United African Tigers yomwe ndi timu yomwe yatenga osewerayu watsimikiza za nkhaniyi.\r\nUnited African Tigers ndi akatsiwiri a ligi yayikulu yakumeneko.\r\nMkulu wa timu ya ku Namibia wati George Nyirenda anamudziwa kuchokera pomwe amasewera ku timu ya Caps United ku Zimbabwe.\r\nTimu ya Big Bullets yatsimikiza kuti kontalakiti ya George Nyirenda ndi timuyi imatha pa 28 February ndikuti palibe choletsa Nyirenda kusewera ku timu yatsopanoyi.\r\nOsewera wina yemwe anasewerako ku timuyi ndi Muzipasi mwangonde.','sports_news','2018-02-23','2018-02-23 15:00:53'),(41,'Masters ndi Manoma apuma sabata imodzi yokha','23/02/18\r\nMatimu a Masters Security komanso Be forward wanders ati apuma kwa sabata imodzi yokha atatuluka mu chikho cha mpikasano wa matimu osewera  ma ligi a mu Africa wa CAF.\r\nMasters security inagonja ndi timu ya Atletico Ptroleos ya ku Angola ndi zigoli zisanu kwa du zomwe zinachinyidwa atapita kwawo ndipo masewero omwe anachitikira pakhomo ku bwalo la zamasewero la Bingu masewero anatha popanda zigoli.\r\nBe forward wanders anatuluka atachinyidwa zigoli zisanu ndi chimodzi 6 kwa chimodzi ndi timu ya AS Vita ya ku DR Congo. Koyenda manoma anachinyidwa zigoli zinayi ndipo pakhomo anachinyitsa zigoli ziwiri ndipo anachinya chimodzi.\r\n Timu ya wa Be-forward wanderers yati inapindula pa maesewerowa ndipo ziwakonzekeretsa pomwe ligi yayikulu ikuyamba posachedwapa kuno kumudzi.\r\nNayo timu ya Masters Security yati adziwa zofooka zako ndipo akufuna aonjezere osewera ena atatu kuti aonjezere mphamvu.\r\n Masewero omwe Be-forward wanderers inasewera ndi AS Vita anapeza ndalama zokwana 9 million kwacha ndipo. ','sports_news','2018-02-23','2018-02-23 15:00:39'),(42,'Dausi Wakanitsitsa ndalama za a Chaponda','28/02/18 Pomwe mlandu wa yemwe anali nduna ya zamalimidwe yemwenso ndi wachiwiri kwa mtsogoleri wa chipani cha DPP kumwera  a George Chaponda ukupitilira, nduna ya zofalitsa nkhani a Nicholas Dausi akanitsitsa kwa mtu wagalu za kukhudzidwa kulikonse ndi ndalama zankhaninkhani zomwe a bungwe lofufuza za katangale ndi ziphuphu la ACB adazipeza kunyumba kwawo chakachatha.\r\nMlanduwu unapitilira lachiwiri ku ku Banki yayikulu yosunga ndalama ya Reserve ku LIlongwe komwe ozenga mlanduwu amakatsimikizira a Chaponda za ndalama zomwe anazipezazo komanso kukamva kwa mkulu wina opeleka ziphaso zovomereza munthu kusunga ndalama zakunja ku bankiyo ngati ndi zoona kuti a Chaponda anali ndi chilolezo chosunga ndalama zakunja zochuluka.\r\n\" Ine pa nkhani ya ndalamazi sindikudziwapo kanthu, mwina pa nthawi yomwe anzangawa ankanena izi anali atasokonekera maganizo pozindikira kuti izi zikakuchitikira sizimatengera udindo kapena mphamvu, ndizosowetsa mtendere\" anatero a Dausi kuwuza ozenga mlandu Paul Chiotcha wa ku Zomba.\r\nA Dausi amayankha mafunso awo mosafuna kuyang\'anana maso ndi maso ndi a Chaponda pomwe a Chaponda anali ndi chidwi kuyang\'anitsitsa momwe a Dausi akufotokozera umboni wawo.\r\nOyimira a Chaponda pa Mlanduwu a Tamando Chokotho analankhula zambiri zofuna kustimikizira kuti a Chaponda ndi munthu wa ndalama ndipo ali ndi katundu wambiri yemwe angathe kuwabweretsera ndalama.\r\nKomabe ozenga mlandu wa bungwe la ACB anati nkhani siyakulemera kapena kupezeka kwa ndalama zokha koma kuti a Chaponda ananamiza bungwe la ACB kuti ndalama zina zomwe anazipeza zokwana 95 million kwacha zimayenera kudzatengedwa ndi a Dausi ndikuti ndi zachipani cha DPP, zinthu zomwe a Dausi akana. \r\nA Chaponda aonekanso abodza pokhala kuti mkulu ogwira ku banki yayiyikulu wakana zoti a Chaponda anali ndi chiphaso chowavomereza kusunga ndalama zakunja zochuluka ngakhale kuti a Chaponda anaonetsa khotili chikalata chonga cha mtunduwu chomwe akuti ndichosayinidwa ndi nduna ya zachuma.\r\nKatswiri wina pa ndale Henry Chingaipe wati zomwe a Dausi anena zikusonyeza kuti chipani cha DPP nacho sichikufuna kukhudzidwa mwa njira ina iliyonse ndi nkhaniyi ndikuti zikuonetsa kuti a Chaponda awasiya kuti athane nazo okha.\r\nMlanduwu ulowanso mu khothi pa 6 March, 2018.\r\n','local_news','2018-02-28','2018-02-28 12:11:39'),(43,'Nyerere zili pa mavuto - Kanyenda wathawako','28/02/18 Mavuto sakukata ku banja la nyerere - Manoma - Be forward Wanderers kamba koti katswiri yemwe anachinya zigoli zochuluka mu ligi yatha yemwenso ndi katswiri odziwika bwino Essau Black Mamba Kanyenda wasiya ntchito ku timuyi.\r\nMasiku apitawa Banja la Manoma linaonetsedwa mazangazime ndi timu ya AS Vita ya ku DRC pomwe inachinyidwa zigoli 6 kwa chimodzi. Asanapite kumasewerowa Manoma adalengeza kuti sapitanso ku DRC ndipo sachita nawo mpikisano kamba koti owathandiza anakana sapeleka ndalama kamba koti osewera ake anakhala akunyanyala kusewera mpira kamba kosowa ndalama zinthu zomwe sizinasangalatse  akuluakulu a Be forward ku Japan. Atabwerako ku DRC nkhani zinamvekanso kuti Manoma ali ndi ngongole zochuluka zomwe anayendera ulendo wa ku DRC kamba koti sanalandirebe thandizo kuchoka ku kampani ya Be Forward yomwe imathandiza timuyi.\r\nPakadalipano tsogolo la thandizo lopita ku timuyi silikudziwikabe ati kamba koti akanakambirana za mavuto omwe alipo pakati pa mbali ziwirizi. \r\nPakusiya ntchito kwa Kanyenda mlembi wa timuyi a Mike Butao ati sakufunanso kuyankhula ndi atolankhani pa zamavuto awo ati kamba koti ndi zimodzi mwa zinthu zomwe sizikusangalatsa ma bwana awo ku Japan.\r\nKu timuyi kulinso mpungwepungwe pa za tsogolo la yemwe ndi Mphunzitsi wa timuyi a Yasin Osman.\r\nKanyenda watsimikiza kusiya kusewera ku timuyi ati kamba koti ndiotanganidwa.\r\n\r\nKoma Joseph Shakira Kamwendo yemwe ndi kaputeni wati kukuchitika zambiri ku timuyi ndipo adzayankhula mu nthawi yoyenera akakambirana ndi akuluakulu, apa kamwendo sanatambasule bwino koma zikupeleka mlozo kuti zinthu zina sizikuyenda bwino ku timuyi.\r\n\r\nA Butao ati akhala akukumana ndi anthu osiyanasiyana oyendetsa timuyi ndipo sakukayika kuti zinthu zikhala bwino.  \r\n','sports_news','2018-02-28','2018-02-28 12:29:15'),(44,'Chanthunya wafika kumudzi - Apolisi ati mlandu uyamba','02/03/2018 Misozi Chanthunya yemwe anathawa mdzikomuno mchaka cha 2010 kupita ku South Africa ndipo amamuganizira kuti anapha bwenzi lake Linda Gasa wafika m\'dzikomuno lachinayi kudzera ku bwalo la ndege la Kamuzu ku Lilongwe.\r\nChanthunya wakahla ali m\'manja mwa apolisi ku South Africa kuchokera pomwe anamugwira ndipo wakhala akuyesa njira zosiyanasiyana kuti asabwere kuno kumudzi kuzamuzenga mlandu koma zakhala zikukanika.\r\nAtafika pa bwalo la ndege anthu onse anatsika mu ndege ndipo iye anali otsiriza. Pomwe amatuluka mu ndegeyi apolisi anamuzungulira kupita naye ku ofesi yoona za anthu olowa ndikutuluka mdzikomuno.\r\n\r\nOlemba nkhani sanaloledwe kutenga zithunzi pafupi koma atatuluka mu ofesi yowona za anthu olowa ndikutuluka apolisi anathira unyolo m\'manja a Chathunya , chitsimikizo afika dziko lomwe anapalamulira mlandu.\r\nLInda Gasa yemwe anali bwenzi la a Chathunya anapezeka atamwalira ku malo ena ogona alendo ku Mangochi ndipo anamukwilira pansi.\r\nMalipoti amati awiriwa anali limodzi pa ulendo wakunyanjawo.\r\nLInda Gasa anali bwe','local_news','2018-03-02','2018-03-02 13:08:57'),(45,'Joseph Kamwendo akufuna kuzisiya','2/03.2018 Potsatira kusintha kaputeni wa timu ya Mighty Be Forward Wanderers posankha osewera pakati Alfred Manyozo Junior kuchotsa Joseph Kamwendo mpungwepungwe wafikanso ku timuyi.  Joseph Kamwendo wati walemba kalata yopempha kuti amulore kuti akasewere ku timu ina yakumtima mwake mobwerekera pomwe akudikira kuti mgwirizano wake ndi timuyi uthe.\r\nWapampando wa timu ya Wanderers Gift Mkandawire komanso watsimikiza kuti osewera kumbuyo kwa timuyi Lucky Malata komanso Mike Kaziputa osewera pakati ndiwo akhale achiwiri kwa Manyozo Junior \r\nPakadalipano akulu akulu a wanderers ati sakudziwapo kanthu pa malingaliro omwe Joseph Kamwendo alinawo ati pozindikira kuti udindo wa kaputeni omwe anamupatsa unali ongogwirizira kuchokera pomwe Francis Mlimbika anati sakwanitsa kukhala pa udindowu.','sports_news','2018-03-02','2018-03-02 13:08:39'),(46,'Pasaka ya mu mdima - Mphamvu ya magetsi yatsika , ESCOM','28/03/18\r\nBungwe logulitsa magetsi mdziko muno la ESCOM latulutsa chikalata chomwe chati  mu nyengo ya pasaka ya chakachino dziko la Malawi likhala ndi mphamvu yamagetsi yochepa zomwe zichititse kuti anthu ambiri asakhale ndi mwayi wa magetsi,\r\n\r\nBungwe la ESCOM lati izi zili chomwechi kamba koti akhala akukonza ena mwa makina opangira mphamvu ya magetsi ku Nkula.\r\nMakina omwe akukonzedwawa ali pansi pa kampani yopanga magetsi ya Electricity Generation Company Limited (EGENCO)\r\nBungwe la ESCOM latinso ngati mbali imodzi yofuna kuchepetsera vutoli ma jeneleta omwe amapanga mphamvu yamagetsi ati akhala akugwira ntchito  ma ola khumi ndi awiri kuti athandizire kusokelera mphamvu ya magetsiyi.\r\nESCOM inagula ma jeneleta mwezi wa January  omwe adawaika ku Blantyre komanso kanengo. Cholinga chogulira ma jeneletawa ndikuthandizira kupanga mphamvu ya magetsi pa nthawi yomwe mphamvu yamagetsi ochokera ku madzi sikuyenda bwino.\r\nKomabe akatswiri ena akhala akunena kuti mphamvu ya magetsi ochokera ku jeneleta ndiyokwera mtengo kamba ka mafuta.\r\nDziko la Malawi limadalira mphamvu yamagetsi yochokera kumadzi ndipo zinthu zakhala zisakuyenda bwino kamba koti kawirikawiri madzi omwe akumafika ku mtsinke wa Shire akumakhala ochepa kamba ka mvula yochepa angakhale kuti nthawi zina ngakhale mvula igwe yambiri madzi samakhazikika kamba ka kuonongeka kwa chilengedwe.\r\nDziko la Malawi mwa zina likufuna lizigula magetsi kuchokera ku dziko la Mozambique motsatana ndi mgwirizano omwe maiko awiriwa adasainirana ndipo ndalama zake zichokera ku banki yayikulu pa dziko lonse ya World Bank.\r\nKubwera kwa ma jeneleta kudachittsanso kuti mtengo wa magetsi ukwele.','local_news','2018-03-29','2018-03-29 13:45:02'),(47,'Nduna ya zachuma yati 4 biliyoni yopita kwa aphungu ndimaganizo chabe','29/03/18\r\nNduna ya zachuma a Goodal Gondwe yati 4 biliyoni ya chitukuko yomwe amayenera kulandira aphungu ndi maganizo chabe kamba koti ndalamayo pakadalibe.\r\n\r\nA Gondwe ati bungwe la MRA likuyenera kutolera ndalamayo komanso kuti aphungu akuyenera kulemba ndondomeko yopempha chitukuko chomwe akufuna.\r\n\r\nPa mkumano omwe wapitawu aphungu a nyumba ya malamulo adagawana 4 billion kwacha potsatira malipoti omwe adatuluka kuti pachiyambi ndalamayi imapita kwa aphungu owerengeka omwe amaganiziridwa kuti ndi omwe adathandiza boma kuti ma bilo osintha kayendetsedwe ka chisankho asadutse mnyumbayi.\r\n\r\nAnthu akhala akudzudzula boma kamba kosafotokoza bwino komwe itatenge ndalamazi komanso posankha aphungu ochepa kuti apindule , ndipo mbali ina mtsogoleri wa zipani zotsutsa ku nyumba ya malamulo Dr Lazarous Chawera wakhalanso akudzudzulidwa kamba kovomera kuti aphungu agawane ndalama zomwe ndondomeko yake sinatsatidwe bwino.\r\n\r\nKu nyumba ya malamulo kuli aphungu 193 ndipo mtsgoleri wa boma m\'nyumbayi a Kondwani Nakhumwa wakhalanso akupemphedwa kuti atule pansi udindo wawo.\r\nMabungwe omwe si a boma akonza zioonetsero zokakamiza boma kuti ndalama zomwe aphungu anagawana asalandire ndikutinso nduna ya zachuma a Goodal Gondwe  komanso a Kondwani nankhumwa atule pansi ma udindo wawo.','local_news','2018-03-29','2018-03-29 14:10:33'),(48,'Malawi Flames ikutheka - Mphunzitsi','29/03/18 Mphunzitsi wa timu ya mpira wa miyendo ya dziko lino Ronny Van Geneugden wati tsopano tsogolo la timu ya mpira wa dziko lino likuonekeka lowala. \r\nIye wati izi zilichomwechi kamba koti wakwanitsa kupeza osewera omwe akhoza kuwadalira ndikuti kwatsalako nkochepa zedi. \r\nPosachedwapa timuyi inasewera ndi timu ya dziko la Uganda pa masewero a ubale ndipo unatha popanda zigoli. Mphunzitsiyu wati pali kusintha kwakukulu pa momwe osewera akuchitira ndipo ali ndi chiyembekezo kuti zipatso ziyamba kuoneka.\r\nM\'masewero omwe timuyi yakhala ikusewera kochiyu wakhala akudalira osewera monga Charles Swini ngati oyamba kusunga pagolo pomwe Brighton Munthali akamakhala wachiwiri. Kumbali ya anyamata otchinga kumbuyo Limbikani Mzava Gomezgani Chirwa, Stanley Sanudi komanso Dennis Chembezi ndi omwe akumayamba. Kumbali ya osewera pakati Frank Banda, John Banda , Robert Ng\'ambi, Robin Ngalande komanso Gerald Phiri ndiwo akhala ali patsogolo pomwe kutsogolo Mphunzitsiyu wakhala akudalira Gabadinho Mhango komanso Richard Mbulu.\r\nMphunzitsiyu wakhala akugwiritsa ntchito kwambiri osewera achisodzera ndipo m\'masewero apitawa ndi timu ya Uganda Precious Phiri wa timu ya anyamata osafika zaka makumi awiri ya dziko lino anasewera masewero ake oyamba ku timu yaikulu ya Flames.\r\nChitengereni timuyi Mphunzitsiyu wapambana masewero ake awiri okha, walepherana mphamvu ndi matimu 7 ndipo walephera katatu pomwe anasewera ndi Madagascar kawiri komanso Tanzania.\r\nKatswiri wa owunika nkhani za masewero a  mpira Charles Nyirenda wati Mphunzitsiyu sanalakwe kukonza timu yake yokhazikika koma chofunika ndikupambana pa masewero.\r\n\r\nMphunzitsiyu watsala ndi chaka chimodzi akuphunzitsabe timuyi.','sports_news','2018-03-29','2018-03-29 14:50:43'),(49,'Bullets ndi Wanderers akuzembana','29/03/18Pa mayere ofuna kupeza matimu omwe atsegulire masewero a mpira a chakachino matimu a Bullets komanso Wanderers sanayanjane. Mapeto ake Timu ya Bullets ndiyo isewere ndi Kamuzu Barracks pomwe timu ya Wanderers isewera ndi Silver Strikers ena amangoti ma \"bankers\"\r\nMpikisano wa masewero osiyanasiyana usanayambike ma timu amasewera chikho chomwe chimakhala cha chifundo ndipo ndalama zake amathandizira komwe kuli zosowa. \r\nChakachino malinga ndi akuluakulu a FAM ndalama zomwe atapeze akathandizira ophunzira a pasukulu ya ana osaona ku  Ekwendeni.\r\nMaelewa achitika dzulo.\r\n\r\n ','sports_news','2018-03-29','2018-04-03 15:33:57'),(50,'Dziko la South Africa likulira mai Winnie Mandela','03/04/18 Dziko la South Africa lili pa chisoni chachikulu potsatira imfa ya yemwe anali mkazi wa mtsogoleri wa dziko la South Africa malemu Nelson Mandela. \r\nMalipoti otsimikizika ati Mai Mandela amwalira ku chipatala cha Net Care Milpark komwe anapita kukalandira chithandizo atadwala. \r\nKuchokera kumayambiliro a chaka chino mayi Mandela akhala akudwaladwala kufikira lolemba pomwe amwalira.\r\nMai Mandela anali munthu ochilimika pomenyela ufulu wa anthu maka polimbana ndi mchitidwe othetsa tsankho pakati pa anthu akuda ndi azungu.\r\nKamba ka kuchilimika kwawo potsutsana ndi ulamuliro wa tsankhowu , mai Mandela anakhala akumangidwa kangapo konse.\r\nChenicheni chomwe chapha mai Mandela sichinadziwike koma akuti lachisanu anali nawo pa mapemphero a Pasaka ku mpingo wina ku soweto mdziko lomwelo ndipo pa nthawi yomwe amapita nawo kuchipatala akuti anali atavutika ndi matenda a chimfine.\r\nMalipoti  ena akuti mai Mandela amadwala matenda a Diabetes kapena kuti shuga omwe akuti anakhudzanso impso.\r\nMai Mandela amwalira ali ndi zaka 81.','local_news','2018-04-03','2018-04-03 15:09:23'),(51,'Msika wa Fodya Sukhalitsa - Malonda ayamba pa 9 April','03/04/18 Kafukufuku wachiwiri ofuna kudziwa kuchuluka kwa chiwerengero cha Fodya yemwe dziko lino likolore wasonyeza kuti Fodya sanalimidwe wambiri chakachino.\r\nIzi zingachititse kuti nyengo yogula fodya ikhale yaifupi.\r\nKafukufukuyu waonetsa kuti chiwerengero cha Fodyayu chatsika ndi ma kilogalamu  khumi ndi awiri pa zana limodzi lilironse (12%) poyerekeza ndi chakachatha.\r\nKampani zogula Fodya zimayenera kugula ma kilogalamu okwana 171 miliyoni koma zadziwika kuti pakutha pa zonse ndi makilogalamu 149 miliyoni omwe atapezeke.\r\nMkulu wa bungwe la TCC a Kayisi Sadala wati chiwerengerechi chadza kamba ka ng\'amba yomwe inakhudza madera ena pakati pa miyezi ya February ndi March.\r\nKomabe iwo ati chiyembekezo ndichakuti malonda a chaka chino ayenda bwino ndipo sakuyembekeza mavuto oimitsidwa kwa msika mwachisawawa.\r\nMsika wa ku Kanengo ku LIlongwe autsekulira pa 9 April pomwe ku chinkhoma ku Kasungu ayamba pa 11 April.\r\nKu Mzuzu msikawu udzayamba pa 23 April ndipo ku Limbe autsekulira pa 16 Mwezi uno.\r\nWapampando wa bungwe la Aret a Reuben Maigwa wati ogula Fodya akungoyenera kugula mitengo yabwino kamba koti Fodyayu akhoza kukhala olimbirana.\r\nKomabe atafunsidwa kuti anenepo pa zachiyembekezo cha momwe malondawa atayendere chakachino , akulu akulu ku bungwe la TCC anati malonda a Fodya amakhala ovuta kunena mwachindunji kumbali ya mitengo.\r\nMzaka zino malonda a Fodya akulowa pansi kamba ka kukula kwa nkhani ya mchitidwe olimbikitsa athu kuti asamasute Fodya kamba koti amaononga moyo.\r\n','local_news','2018-04-03','2018-04-03 15:09:11'),(52,'Jimmy Zakazaka wabwerera kuchisa','03/04/18 Mchaka cha 2003 Jimmy Zakazaka anali osewera wa Tigers FC komwe kudamupangitsa kuti atchuke pa nkhani za masewero.\r\nLuso lake lidamutengera ku timu ya Bullets komwe sadakhalitsekonso kamba koti pakati pa zaka za 2005 kufika 2013 luso la myamatayu linapita patali zomwe zidachitsa kuti matimu akunja kwa dziko lino azimukhetsera dovu. Ena mwa matimu akunja omwe wasewerapo ndi monga Free State Stars, Bay United, Thanda Royal Zulu, African Wanderers komanso FC Cape Town.\r\nPakadalipano akulu-akulu a timu ya Tigers FC atsimikiza kuti Zakazaka wabwerera ku timu yake yoyamba zinthu zomwe zilimbitse timuyi.\r\nRobin Alufandika yemwe ndi mkulu wa timuyi wati akuyembekeza kuti Zakazaka komanso katswiri wina wakale Victor Nyirenda athandiza kulimbikitsa anyamata achisodzera omwe ali ku timuyi.\r\nNyirenda naye wati amulandira bwino ndipo anasewera nawo pa masewero opimana mphamvu omwe timu yake  inali nawo ku Mulanje ndi timu ya Big Bullets komwe anagonjetsedwa ndi zigoli ziwiri kwa du!.\r\nTigers FC yatenganso Blessings Phiri yemwe anali ku timu ya Wizard FC.\r\nNyirenda anayamba kudziwika mchaka cha 2005 ali ku  timu ya ESCOM yomwe pano inathetsedwa. Mchaka cha 2006 anayamba kusewera ndi Wanderers FC yomwe pano ndi Be Forward Wanderers koma mchaka cha 2010 anachokonso kumeneku ndipo anasewera matimu akunja monga APR FC ya ku Rwanda komanso Berjaya Dong Nai ya ku Vietnam.\r\nAnyamata onsewa adali nawo mu timu ya mpira wa miyendo ya dziko lino mchaka cha 2010 pomwe inachita bwino kufika ndime yapatsogolo mu mpikisano wa matimu a m\'maiko a mu Africa , zinthu zomwe zinali zisanachitikepo mzaka 26.','sports_news','2018-04-03','2018-04-03 15:33:39'),(53,'Mneneri Bushiri  Akufufuzidwa pa Milandu ya Ndalama','Nthambi ya apolisi ofufuza milandu ikulu ikulu mdziko la South Africa masiku apitawa adati akufufuza m\'neneri Shephered Bushiri yemwe ati akumuganizira kuti wakhala akuzembetsa ndalama zankhani- nkhani kuchokera m\'dzikolo kupita nazo mdziko la Malawi.\r\nM\'neneri Bushiri watsimikiza kuti pakuchitika zinthu zomwe zikusonyeza kuti akufufuzidwa ndipo wati izi zinayambika sabata zapitazo pomwe anachitidwa chipikisheni chopyola muyeso pa nthawi yomwe amachoka mdziko la Malawi kubwerera ku South Africa komwe amagwira akutumikira komanso kupanga ma bizinesi.\r\nSabata yatha a Bushiri analandidwa makina a kompyuta komanso lamya za m\'manja ndi apolisi ofufuzawa pa nthawi yomwe amachokera ku Amerika komwe amakatumikira.\r\nPakadalipano mabungwe ena omwe si a boma ati zomwe akuchita apolisi mdziko la South Africa ndikuzunza chabe ndipo awapempha kuti agwire ntchito yawo mwachilungamo.\r\n Mmodzi wa akuluakulu a mabungwewa a Robert Mkwezalamba wati ndi okhumudwa kuti apolisi sanafotokozere a Bushiri zifukwa zomwe awalandira katundu wawo komanso chipikisheni chomwe akupanga zinthu zomwe ati ndizodandaulitsa. Iwo ati sizoona kuti a Bushiri azimva m\'manyuzipepapla kuti akufufuzidwa pomwe iwo eni sanawauze kalikonse.\r\nPachifukwa ichi iwo apempha apolisiwa kuti agwire ntchito yawo monga kuyenerera.\r\nMneneri wa nthambi ya zofufuza fuufuza mdzikolo  a Brigadier Hangwani Mulaudzi ati iwo ntchito yawo ndiyofufuza zomwe anauzidwa ndipo ati achita izi mopanda mantha komanso kukondera.\r\nMneneri Bushiri kwawo ndi Malawi konkuno koma wakhazikika kwambiri mdziko la South Africa komwe wakhala akutumikira kwa zaka zingapo ndipo amati ali ndi buzinesi zosiyana siyana kuphatikizapo migodi ya miyala ya mtengo wapatali, mafakitole, kampani ya lamya zam\'manja kungotchulapo mwa zina.\r\nIwowa akuwaganizira kuti amazemba misonkho komanso kuti amathawitsa ndalama za mdzikolo kupita nazo ku Malawi, zinthu zomwe eni ake a Bushiri sanauzidwe ndi ofufuzawo koma akuti ndizabodza , zongofuna kuipitsa mbiri yawo.\r\n','local_news','2018-04-18','2018-04-18 12:42:38'),(54,'Wachiwiri wina kwa sipika, Chiwaya  wasiya ndale','17/04/18 Wachiwiri wina kwa sipika wa nyumba ya Malamulo yemwenso ndi phungu wa dera la pakati m\'boma la Mangochi walengeza kuti wasiya ndale.\r\n A Clement Chiwaya anena izi kudzera mchikalata chomwe atulutsa ndipo ati udindo wawo ukatha pa 21 May chaka cha mawa sadzapikisana naonso pa zisankho zikubwerazi , ndipo ati achita izi atakambirana bwino ndi banja lawo.\r\nA Chiwaya anayamba ndale zawo mchaka cha 2003 ndipo mu ulamuliro wa malemu BIngu wa Mutharika , anawasankhapo kukhala nduna yowona za anthu olumala. \r\nAkulu akulu a chipani cha UDF ati alandira kalata yomwe a Chiwaya atumiza ndipo akudikira kuti abwere ku Amerika komwe apita kuti adzakambe nawo ndikumva chenicheni chomwe chawapangitsa izi.\r\nKumbali yawo a Muluzi awuza nyuzipepapla ya Daily Times kuti ndiokhumudwa ndi chisankho chomwe achita a Chiwaya angakhale kuti akumvetsa khumbo lawo.\r\n','local_news','2018-04-18','2018-04-20 13:52:24'),(55,'Ngumuya wati a Mutharika asayime 2019','18/04/18 Mvula sikukata ku chipani cholamula cha Democratic Progressive Party potsatira zomwe wanena phungu wa chipani cha DPP ku dera lina la mzinda wa Blantyre a Allan Ngumuya kuti Mtsogoleri wa dziko lino Aurthur Peter Mutharika sakuyenera kuimanso pa chisankho cha chaka cha mawa.\r\nZomwe ayankhula a Ngumuya omwenso ndi odziwika bwino poimba nyimbo za uzimu zikutsatira zomwe anayankhula mayi Callista Mutharika kuti a Chilima ndiwo akuyenera kudzimira chipani cha DPP pa chisankho chikubwerachi osati a Mutharika omwe ndi alamu awo ndipo anati akula.\r\nAtayankhula izi anthu ena kuphatikizapo a Ben Phiri omwe anali othandizira a Mutharika, a Louis Ngalande omwe ndi mtsogoleri wa achinyamata kuchipani cha DPP anavomerezana ndi maganaizo oti a Chilima ndiwo akuyenera kudzaimira chipani cha DPP.\r\nKomabe a Ben Phiri pa msonkhano wa olemba nkhani sananene mwachindunji kamba koti iwo anati a Mutharika ndi a Chilima ndi omwe angathandize kupitilira kukweza dziko lino.\r\nMoto omwe mayi callista anauyamba watentha mitima ya akuluakulu ena a chipani cha DPP omwe akunka nachititsa misonkhano tsiku ndi tsiku kunena kuti Arthur Peter Mutharika ndiyemwe adzaimire chipanichi mchaka cha 2019.\r\nAkulu akuluwa akumati a Mutharika akadali ndi mphamvu komanso nzeru zowayenereza kukhala mtsogoleri ndipo sakukaika kuti adzapambana ndi mavoti ochuluka chikafika chisankho.\r\nPakadalipano a Mutharika komanso a Chilima sanayankhulepo kalikonse pa nkhaniyi ndipo sizikudziwika ngati pakati pa awiriwa pali kusagwirizana.\r\nA Mutharika anasankha a chilima kukhala wachiwiri wawo pa masankho a mchaka cha 2014 ndipo akatswiri andale amati zinawathandizira a DPP kuti apambane chisankho.\r\nAkatswiri a ndalewa ati a Chilima akuyenera kubwera poyera ndikuuza dziko la Malawi maganizo awo, koma ofesi ya a Chilima yati sali okakamizidwa kutero ndipo adzayankhula nthawi ikakwana.','local_news','2018-04-18','2018-04-20 13:52:08'),(56,'Mwawi Kumwenda Sakutheka!','Katswiri osewera timu ya mpira ya ntchembere mbaye mdzikomuno Mwawi kumwenda walandiranso mphoto pokhala yekhayo yemwe wachinya zigoli zochuluka pa mpikisano wa matimu a m\'maiko 53 omwe analamulidwapo ndi dziko la Britain.\r\nAka ndi kachiwiri kuti Mwawi alandire mphoto yotereyi ndipo wayamika anzake osewera nawo mu timuyi kamba komupatsira mipira yabwino. \r\nMwawi anachinya zigoli 254 ndipo pa mwayi zana limodzi ochinya  uliowonse omwe amaupeza amaphonyapo zigoli zisanu ndi zitatu zokha.\r\nMchaka cha 2014 anapambananso mphotoyi atachinya zigoli 230.\r\nWachiwi kwa Mwawi ndi osewera wa mdziko la Uganda yemwe wachinya zigoli 202.\r\nPakadalipano timu ya dziko la Malawi ili pa nambala 7 pa dziko lonse kuchoka pa nambala 4.\r\nAnthu okonda masewerowa ati timuyi ikuyenera kusintha osewera ena pobweretsa achisodzera kuti iyambenso kuchita bwino.','sports_news','2018-04-18','2018-04-18 13:34:25'),(57,'Mvumbi wa zigoli poyamba Chikho cha TNM','Pafupi fupi zigoli 20 ndizo zachinyidwa pa masewero osiyanasiyana omwe analipo kumathero a sabata yatha pomwenso chikho cha TNM chimayamba.\r\nTImu ya Eagles inachinya TN Stars ya ku Kasungu ndi zogoli zinayi kwa chimodzi, Red LIons inathambitsa Dwangwa United ndi zigoli zinayi pomwe Nyasa Big Bullets inagoletsa Kamuzu Barracks ndi chigoli chimodzi kwa chilowere. Nchalo United yomwe yangobwerera kumene mu mpikisanowu inagonjetsanso Mzuni FC ndi chigoli chimodzi kwa du.\r\nPakadalipano Red Lions ili pamwamba ndi ma points anayi itasewera kawiri motsatana ndi Blue Eagles yomwe yasewera kamodzi komanso Wanderers ndi Nyasa omwe ali ndi ma points atatu aliyense  atasewera kamodzi.\r\nLoweluka Azam Tigers isewera ndi Moyale ku Mulanje, Mafco ikumana ndi Mzuni ku chitowe, Blue Eagles ikumana ndi Civil Sporting pa Nakhaka, Wanderers isewera ndi Masters Security ku Balaka pomwe Nchalo United isewera ndi Karonga United pa bwalo la masewero la Kalulu. \r\nLamulungu Nyasa Big Bullets iswana ndi Moyale Barracks pa Kalulu , Dwangwa ndi Mzuni ku Chitowe, Red Lions ndi Karonga United ku Balaka pomwe silver strikers iphana ndi Kamuzu Barracks pa bwalo la Silver.','sports_news','2018-04-18','2018-04-18 13:49:04'),(58,'Chenjerani - Mavenda ku Lilongwe akugulitsa nsomba za poizoni osungira maliro','19/04/18 Mkwiyo wakula pakati pa anthu a mu mzinda wa Lilongwe zitadziwika kuti ena mwa mavenda ogulitsa nsomba zaziwisi mu mzinda wa Lilongwe akumathira nsombazo mankhwala omwe achipatala amagwiritsa ntchito akafuna kusunga maliro kwa kanthawi kuti asaonongeke mwachangu.\r\nIzi atsimikiza ndi a bungwe loyeza mlingo ndi ubwino wa wa zinthu la Malawi Bureau of Standard lomwe masiku apitawo linapatsidwa nsomba ndi mkulu wina yemwe anagula nsombazo kwa mavenda koma anazikayikira ndipo anakazisiya ku bungweli kuti akaziunike bwino.\r\nMkulu odandaulayu Charles Masi yemwenso ndi dalaivala wa ndege ku kampani ya Malawian Airways amupempha kuti apereke ndondomeko ya anthu omwe anamugulitsa nsombazo zomwe zinalipo Khumi , koma anali ataphikapo ziwiri.\r\nAkatswiri a zachipatala komanso kafukufuku wa pa makina a intaneti akusonyeza kuti mankhwala osungira malirowa ali ndi ziopsezo zosiyana siyana pa moyo wa munthu kuphatikizapo kuyambitsa matenda a khansa, kuononga impso, komanso kubweretsa mavuto a kapumidwe kapena kuti munthu kumakhala ndi mpweya ochepa okokera mkati kamba koonongeka kwa mapapo ndi ziwalo zina.\r\nMkulu owona za ufulu wa anthu ogula a John Kapito wati mpofunika kuti akulu-akulu a boma alimbikitse kuyendera ochita malondawa ndikuonetsetsa kuti akugulitsa zinthu zabwino pozindikira kuti si onse angakwanitse kumakagula nsombazi ku sitolo zomwe zimaoneka zodalilika. \r\nIwo ati izi, nzokhumudwitsa.\r\nNkhambakamwa zina zikuti mchitidwewu wakhala ulipo kwa kanthawi ndipo la fote linakwana.\r\n','local_news','2018-04-20','2018-04-20 13:51:49'),(59,'Ku DPP Kulibe Mpungwe pungwe - ma Gavanala atero','19/04/18 Gulu la ma gavanala a chipani cholamula cha Democratic Progressive Party DPP lati ku chipani kwawo kulibe mpungwe pungwe uliwonse pa nkhani ya yemwe adzaimire chipani cha DPP pa chisankho cha 2019.\r\nIwo anena izi poyankhapo zomwe ena akunena ponena kuti a Saulos Chilima ndiwo akuyenera kuimira chipani cha DPP osati a Mutharika omwenso ndi mtsogoleri wa chipanichi komanso dziko la Malawi pakadalipano.\r\nMa gavalanawa omwe ndi a mchigawo chapakati ndipo analipo 23 auza olemba nkhani kuti kusayankha kwa a Chilima pa za pempho lomwe mayi Callista anapereka komanso anthu en akuti a Chilima ndiwo adzaimire chipani cha DPP ati pozindikira kuti  a Mutharika akula.\r\nMa gavanalawa ati Mutharika ndi yemwe akasankhidwe ku msonkhano waukulu wa chipani cha DPP ndikuti alibe opikisana naye.\r\nIwo ati anthu ena osafunira zabwino chipani cha DPP ndi omwe akuchita izi pofuna kudanitsa awiriwa zinthu zomwe ati sizitheka kamba koti akugwira ntchito zawo bwino.\r\nIwo ati pakanakhala chovuta a Chilima akanayankhula ndipo dziko likanamva.','local_news','2018-04-20','2018-04-20 13:51:36'),(60,'Malawi ikumana ndi Mauritius - Chikho cha COSAFA, RVG aiphula?','20/04/18 Zadziwika kuti timu ya mpira wa miyendo ya dziko lino iyamba masewero ake olimbirana chikho cha m\'maiko akumwera kwa Africa cha COSAFA ndi timu ya mdziko la Mauritius.\r\nAkulu akulu-akulu oyendetsa mpikisanowu ndiwo atulutsa mndandanda osonyeza momwe matimu asewerere mchikhochi kuyambira pa 28 Mwezi uno.\r\nm\'masewero awo achiwiri adzathambitsana ndi timu ya mdziko la Botswana pa 30 ndipo masewero awo omaliza mu gulu B adzakumana ndi timu ya Angola.\r\nChakachatha timu ya  dziko la Malawi inatuluka mu mpikisanowu italephera kugoletsa zigoli m\'masewero ake onse atatu.\r\n\r\nYemwe adzapambane mu gulu B adzakumana ndi timu ya dziko la Zimbabwe mu ndime yomaliza yachipulula.\r\nMasiku apitawa timu ya dziko la Botswana inakasewera ndi timu ya Zimbabwe mu mzinda wa Harare pa masewero opimana mphamvu ndipo alendo ndio anachita zakupsa pochinya chigoli chimodzi.\r\nUwu ndi myeso wina wautali wa mphunzitsi wa timu dziko lino RVG yemwe wakhala asakupeza zigoli zokwanira kapena kupambana mipikisano imene wakhala akutsogolera timuyi.\r\nMphunzitsiyu komanso akulu akulu oyendetsa mpira wa miyendo mdzikomuno (FAM) akhala akutsindika kuti kumanganso timu yatsopano sikufunika phuma ndipo m\'malo mwake ali ndichikhulupiliro kuti RVG akugwira bwino ntchito yake ati poona kuti tsopano anyamata akusewera mpira opatsirana, wadongosolo ndiokhazikika.\r\nKamabe ena amati mpira ndizigoli ndipo funso nkumati kodi ku COSAFA tiphulako kanthu?\r\n','sports_news','2018-04-20','2018-04-20 13:05:57'),(61,'Gulu la a Chewa latengera ku khothi nduna  pa nkhani za ufumu','20/04/18 Gulu la achewa mdzikomuno la Chewa Heritage lakasuma ku bwalo la milandu kufunsa bwalolo kuti limange nduna ya zamaboma ang\'ono a Kondwani Nankhumwa kamba kochitira mwano chigamulo cha khothi polonga ufumu wa Kabunduli ngakhale kuti panali chiletso.\r\nOimira milandu gululi a Rodrick Makono atsimikiza izi.\r\nKu banja la Kabunduli kwakhala kuli kusamvana kwa zaka Khumi ndi chimodzi 11 potsatira kumwalira kwa omwe anali a Mfumu. Kusamvanaku kunadza kamba koti mwana wa malemu kabunduli anakatenga chiletso ku bwalo la milandu kuti asuwani a malemu kabunduli omwe malinga ndi mwambo wa a chewa ndi omwe amayenera kulongedwa ufumu asalongedwe ufumu ndikuti m\'malo mwake akhale iyeyo.\r\nPotsatira kusamvana komwe kunalipo a Willet Phiri ndi omwe akhala akugwirizira udindowu.\r\nPakadalipano banja la a phiri lati zachitikazi ndi ndale .\r\nWapampando wa gulu la achewali a George Kanyama Phiri wati zomwe lachita boma ndikusalemekeza malamulo ndi chikhalidwe cha a chewa ndipo akalineneza kwa Gawa undi pa msonkhano wawo omwe amakhala nawo chaka ndi chaka ku Mkaika  mwezi wa August. \r\nIwo ati akuyembekeza kumva kwa Gawa undi kuti chichitike nchiyani koma ati sakuyembekeza kuti yemwe walongedwa kukhala mfumu Kabunduli pakadalipano angakapezeke ku msonkhano wa achewawo  kamba koti ndondomeko  zolongera ufumu wa a chewa sizinatsatidwe.Iwo ati nchifukwa chakenso pa mwambo olonga ufumuwu panalibe mafumu a Chichewa monga momwe zimakhalira.\r\nM\'mau ake nduna ya zamaboma a ng\'ono a Kondwani Nakhumwa ati iwo sakudziwa za chiletso china chilichonse ndipo wauza odandaulawo kuti akasume ku bwalo la milandulo. Izi ndi malingana ndi zomwe nyuzi pepala ya Daily Times yalemba.','local_news','2018-04-20','2018-04-20 14:01:13'),(62,'Chakwera akufuna mlandu wa chiletso uthe','20/04/18 Mtsogoleri wa chipani cha MCP Dr Lazarous Chakwera wati akufuna kuti mlandu omwe anakatenga Chiletso ku bwalo la Milandu pofuna kuti  a Gustave Kaliwo omwe ndi mlembi wa chipani cha MCP asachititse msonkhano waukulu wa chipanichi uthetsedwe.\r\nMwezi wa April chaka chatha a Kaliwo anayitanitsa msonkhano waukulu wa chipani cha MCP omwe unkayenera kuchitika mwezi wa July pa 7 mpaka pa 9 ati potsatira mikangano ndi madandaulo omwe analipo ku chipanichi.    \r\nJaji Charles Mkandawire ndiye akumva mlanduwo ndipo dzulo anakumana ndi oyimila milandu chipani cha MCP a Titus Mvalo omwe auzidwa kuti akalembe zikalata zoyenerera zopempha khothili kuthetsa mlanduwu.\r\nKoma mbali ya a Kaliwo ati iwo amayembekeza kuyi mlanduwu upitilire polola a Chakwera kuti akapereke maganizo awo ku bwalo la milanduli..\r\nOimila a Kaliwo a Powell Nkhutabasa ati akanakonda kuti nkhaniyi ifike ku mapeto koma ati ngati odandaula omwe ndi a Chakwera akufuna kutulukamo mu mlanduwu alibe nazo vuto ndikuti azisiya m\'manja mwa khoti kuti lichite momwe lingathere.','local_news','2018-04-20','2018-04-20 13:56:30'),(63,'Zavutabe ku Chipani cha DPP - Masangwi wati palibe kugwirizana','23/04/18 M\'modzi wa akulu akulu a chipani cha DPP yemwenso ndi phungu wa dera la ku m\'mawa mu mzinda wa Blantyre a Noel Masangwi wati kusemphana maganizo pa yemwe adzaimire chipanichi pa chisankho chikubwerachi kungathe kulepheretsa mwayi oti chipanichi chdzachite bwino.\r\n\r\nA Masangwi anena izi kudzera mu kalata ya pa WhatsApp yomwe yaululika. Kalatayi imapita ku gulu la akulu-akulu a chipani cha DPP ndipo kwakukulu mkalatamo a Masangwi anatsindika kufunika koti a Mutharika omwe ndi mtsogoleri wa chipani cha DPP komanso dziko lino ayitanitse msonkhano wa akulu akulu oyendetsa chipanichi kuti akambirane ndikumanga mfundo imodzi.\r\nMalinga ndi a Masangwi nzokhumudwitsa kuti chipani cha DPP sichinachititsepo msonkhano wa akulu akulu oyendetsa chipanichu kuchokera mchaka cha 2013 ndipo ati izi ndizopereka chiopsezo ku demokalase. \r\nIwowa adzudzulanso akulu akulu ena a chipanichi omwe ati ndiwo akusokoneza mtsogoleri wa dziko lino pomupatsa uphungu olakwika ndipo m\'modzi wa iwo anatchulapo a George Chaponda omwe anakhalapo nduna koma anachotsedwa atakhudzidwa ndi nkhani za katangale komanso ndipo milandu yawo ikadali ku bwalo la milandu.\r\nMayi Callista Mutharika ndiwo anayambitsa nkhani yoti a Mutharika asayimenso ndipo m\'malo mwake a Chilima apatsidwe mpata.\r\n','local_news','2018-04-23','2018-04-24 08:03:49'),(64,'Joyce Banda akubwera - Apolisi akuti chikalata chowamangira chilipobe','24/04/18 Mtsogoleri wakale wa dziko lino Dr Joyce Banda afika mdziko muno lachisanu kudzera ku bwalo la ndege la chileka. Chikalata chomwe watulutsa m\'neneri wa  mayi Banda Andekuche Chanthunya chati mayi Banda adzafika 12 Koloko masana ndipo akuyembekezeka kuchititsa msonkhano mu mzinda wa Blantyre.\r\nChikalatacho chati kubwera kwa Joyce Banda kwachitika atamaliza kugwira ntchito zawo zosiyana-siyana ku America ndi maiko ena.\r\nPatha zaka zinayi Joyce Banda ali kunja kwa dziko lino ndipo anthu ambiri amati anachita izi pothawa kumangidwa pa milandu ya kusakazidwa kwa chuma cha boma komwe kunakhudza anthu ambiri kuphatikizapo zina mwa zomwe zinali nduna zake pa nthawi yomwe anali mtsogoleri.\r\nKomabe mayi Banda akhala akunena nthawi ndi nthawi kuti alibe mlandu uliwonse ndipo amanena mobwereza bwereza kuti adzabwera mdziko muno nthawi ina iliyonse.\r\nPoyankhula ndi nyuzi pepala ya Nation apoilisi atsimikizabe kuti chikalata chomwe chikuwapatsa mphamvu kuti a Banda amangidwe chikanalipobe zomwe zingatanthauze kuti mayi Banda angathe kumangidwa.\r\nKatswiri wina  pa ndale Hennry Chingaipe wati mayi Banda akabwera akuyenera kupanga zina osati ndale kamba koti sakukhulupilira kuti angakhalenso ndichikoka chokwanira pa ndale.\r\nKomabe chikalatacho chati mayi Banda akafika apitiliza kukhala mtsogoleri wa chipani cha PP ndipo pali kuthekera koti angathe kudzapikisana nawo pa chisankho cha 2019\r\n','local_news','2018-04-24','2018-04-24 08:03:26'),(65,'Thupi la Abel Mwakilama lifika lachisanu','Thupi la Abel Mwakilama yemwe anali katswiri osewera kutsogolo mu timu ya mpira wa miyendo ya achinyamata achisodzera osapitilira zaka 17 ya dziko lino lifika mdziko muno lachisanu kuchokera ku Portugal komwe wamwalira lamulungu atadwala malungo a mu ubongo.\r\nAbel Mwakilama anapita ku Portugal komwe amasewera ku timu ina kumeneko ndipo anali ndi luso lopereka chiyembekezo ku tsogolo lake komanso masewero a mpira kuno kumudzi. Chipitileni akuti anasewera masewero 12 ndipo anachinya zigoli zokwana zisanu ndi chimodzi 6 , ndipo m\'masewero asanu ndi awiri amakhala oyamba kulowetsedwa.\r\nImfa ya Abel yakhudza anthu ambiri maka pozindikiranso kuti sabata ziwiri zapitazo anali mdziko muno pomwe timu yachisodzerayi imasewera ndi anzawo a mdziko la Swaziland. Iyeyu sanakhale nawo pa masewero achibwereza omwe analiko mathero a sabata yatha komwenso timuyi inapitilira mu ndime ina italepherana ndi chigoli chimodzi chimodzi ndi timu ya Swaziland koma yapitilra mu ndime ina ya mpikisanowu komwe akumane ndi Angola.\r\nMalinga ndi Richard Mbulu yemwenso ali ku timu yomweyi koma amakhala motalikirana ndo mzakeyu , Abel anamuyimbira foni kuti sakupeza bwino ndipo anamuuza kuti ayankhule ndi mtsogoleri wawo kuti apite kuchipatala koma malipoti akuti momwe ankafika naye kuchipatala nkuti ubongo wake utaonongokea kotero madotolo anayesetsa ngakhale kupita naye kuchipatala chachikulu koma sizinathandize.\r\n','sports_news','2018-04-24','2018-04-24 07:49:36'),(66,'Zionetsero ziliko - Chilima wakananso kulandira chikalata','24/04/18 Wachiwiri kwa mtsogoleri wa dziko lino Saulos Chilima wakana kuti adzalandire chikalata chomwe mabungwe omwe si aboma alemba chopempha boma kuti lisapereke 4 billion kwacha yomwe aphungu anavomereza kuti agawane kuti ikhale yachitukuko. Chikalatachi akachipereka pomaliza pa zionetsero zomwe zichitike mzigawo zonse za dziko lino.\r\nMalinga ndi m\'modzi wa anthu omwe akonza zionetserozi a Timothy Mtambo komanso a Gift Trepence ndizoona kuti analemba kalata yopempha a Chilima kuti ndiwo akalandire chikalatacho ati pozindikira kuti a Mutharika anakana kutero. Iwo ati yankho lomwe lachoka ku ofesi ya wachiwiri kwa mtsogoleri wa dziko linoyu lati ofesi ya presidenti ndi kabineti ipeza munthu oti akalandire chikalatachi osati a Chilima.\r\nPakadali pano a Mtambo ati akuyembekezeka kuyankha kalatayo lero koma atsimikiza kuti zionetsero zilipo.\r\nOdziwa ndale ati sizikanakhala zomveka kuti a chilima avomereze kulandira chikalata cha madandaulochi chonsecho bwana  wawo yemwe ndi a Mutharika anakana kutero. Katswiri pa ndaleyu wati uku kukanakhala kulakwa pa ndale komanso pa ntchito.\r\nKu Lilongwe zionetserozi zikayambira pa Chisomo Private kudutsa msewu wa  Kamuzu Central Hospital mpaka kukafika ku ma ofesi a  boma. Ku Blantyre akayenda kuchokera pa bwalo la zamasewero la Kamuzu  kufika ku khonsolo ya mzindawu ndipo ku Mzuzu akayenda kuchokera pa Katoto kukafika ku khonsolo ya mzindawo.\r\nChichitikireni zioonetsero zomwe zinaononga katundu wankhani nkhani pa 20 July mchaka cha 2012, anthu ambiri amakhala ndi mantha ochita zionetsero maka pozindikira kuti anthu ena anataya miyoyo yawo.','local_news','2018-04-24','2018-04-24 08:09:53'),(67,'Apolisi achenjeza ochita zionetsero asachite zipolowe','25/04/18 Apolisi mdzikomuno achenjeza kuti athana ndi onse omwe akonzeka kudzachita zaupandu komanso chipolowe pa zionetsero zomwe mabungwe si a boma akonza lachisanu pa 28 April, 2018.\r\nMalinga ndi chikalata chomwe apolisiwa atulutsa ndipo chasainidwa ndi mkulu wa nthambi yofalitsa nkhani kupolisiku a James Kadadzera , apolisi atsinidwa khutu kuti pali anthu ena omwe akonzeka kudzachita za updandu pa tsikuli poyambitsa zachipolowe ndikuononga katundu wa anthu osalakwa.\r\nIwo ati apolisi mdzikomuno akonzeka kudzathana ndi anthu komanso magulu aliwonse omwe adzayambitse za upanduzi ndipo apempha iwo omwe akufuna kuchita zionetsero kuti adzachte izi mwa bata.\r\nMabungwe omwe si aboma ati akonza zionetserozi pofuna kukakamiza boma kuti lichitepo kanthu pa mavuto osiyana siyana omwe ali mdzikomuno komanso.\r\nKwakukulu mabungwewa ati akufuna kuti ndalama zokwana 4 billion kwacha zomwe aphungu akunyumba ya malamulo anavomereza kuti zipite m\'madera mwawo popanda ndondomeko zolongosoka asazipereke kwa aphunguwa.\r\n\r\n','local_news','2018-04-25','2018-04-25 15:31:20'),(68,'Kambuku wadya nyerere - Tigers FC 2 : Nomads - 0','02/05/18 Pachichewa pali mawu omwe amati mwamuna nzako mpachulu . Timu ya Mighty Be Forward wanderers lachiwiri lapitali inalephera kuonetsa ukulu wake pomwe yagonjetsedwa ndi timu ya Tigers FC zigoli ziwiri kwa chilowele. \r\nTigers FC inachinya zigoli zonse mchigawo choyamba kudzera kwa anyamata awo Chikaiko Baxton ndi Luke Chima. Malipoti ati mchigawo choyamba TIgers FC inabanikitsa manoma ndipo izi zikupitilira kusonyeza kuti timuyi yayamba ndi mphamvu ndipo pakadalipano ili pa nambala 10 pa mndandanda wa matimu omwe akusewera mu mpikisano olimbirana chikho chachikulu cha masewero a mpira wa miyendo mdzikomuno. Pa nambala 10 pomwepo palinso timu ya Nyasa Big Bullets koma Tigers ili ndi zigoli zambiri.\r\nM\'mau ake m\'modzi wa akatswiri ophunzitsa timuyi \'abambo\' Robin Alufandika wachenjeza matimu omwe asewere ndi timuyi ponena kuti asewera mpira omwe sanasewereponso ndipo ndi okondwa kuti zikuyenda ndipo sakukayika kuti afikira pomwe akufuna. Iwo ati akufunitsitsa kuti masewero onse omwe azisewera pa bwalo la zamasewero la Mulanje azipambana kamba koti anasankha bwaloli kukhala pakwawo.\r\nAka kanali koyamba kuti timu ya manoma ipunthwe mu mpikisanowu ndipo mphunzitsi wa timuyi Yasin Osman wati kulephera kwao kwadza kamba koti mchigawo choyamba anyamata ake anayamba mofooka kwambiri ndipo ngakhale anayesetsa kupanikiza mchigawo chachiwiri zinthu sizinayende. A Osman ati zigoli zambiri zinaphonyedwa mchigawo chachiwirichi ndikutinso anyamata ake anayamba ndi mtima oderera. Manoma alephera kupambana pomwe loweluka lapitali anafanana mphamvu ndi Nyasa BIg Bullets pa masewero omwe anavuta kwambiri ndipo Nyasa Big Bullets inachinya zigoli ziwiri zomwe zinakanidwa  - offside. \r\nM\'masewero ena Nyasa Big Bullets yagonjetsa Nchalo United yomwenso yabwerera kumene mu mpikisanowu ndi zigoli ziwiri kwa chimodzi. Nyasa Big Bullets ndiyomwe inayamba kuchinya kudzera kwa Chiukepo  Msowoya patangotha mphindi khumi ndi zisanu (15) koma Nchalo inabweza kudzera kwa osewera wawo Osman Balala. Komabe pokumbutsa chikale choti \"Bullets nkumadzulo\" Patrick Phiri anachinya chigoli chomaliza cha Nysa Big Bullets kutatsala mphindi ziwiri kuti masewerowa athe.\r\nOthandizira mphunzitsi wa Nyasa Big Bullets Elia Kananji anali ndichimwemwe kuti apambana koma anavomereza kuti Nchalo united inakonzeka kuchita chipongwe timu yawo.\r\nCharles Manda yemwe akuphunzitsa anyamata olima nzimbewa wati cholinga chawo kunali kutseka kumbuyo kuti Nyasa Big Bullets isachinyenso koma zinaonetsa kuti anyamata ake omwe ambiri ndikoyamba kusewera mpikisano oterewu akanalibe upangiri oyenelera. \r\nM\'masewero ena Masters security yaona zakuda itasambitsidwa ntibu wa zigoli ndi Blue Eagles yomwe inachinya zigoli zinayi.','sports_news','2018-05-02','2018-05-02 08:27:07'),(69,'ACB Ikufufuzabe Joyce Banda - Matemba','02/05/18 Mkulu wa bungwe la Anti Corruption Bureau Reyneck Matemba watsutsa zomwe zakhala zikunenedwa ndi mtsogoleri wakale wa dziko lino Dr Joyce Banda kuti bungweli lidamumasula kuti sakukhudzidwa ndi nkhani za katangale. \r\n\r\nMai Banda anafika mdzikomuno loweluka lapitali atakhala kunja kwa dziko lino pafupifupi zaka zinayi ndipo mwa zina apolisi komanso bungweli akhala akunena kuti akuwafufuza pa nkhani zokhudza kusakazidwa kwa chuma cha boma pa nthawi yomwe anali mtsogoleri wa dziko lino (2012- 2014) . Apolisi miyezi iwiri yapitayo adanena kuti ali ndi chikalata chomwe chikuwapatsa mphamvu kumanga mai Banda koma kufika lero sanamangidwe ngakhale kuti ofalitsa nkhani za apolisi James Kadadzera watsimikizanso posachedwapa kuti apolisi ali ndi chikalatachi koma sadanene zifukwa zomwe sakumangira mayi Joyce Banda chifikireni mdzikomuno.\r\nMayi Banda atangofika kumene adanena kuti ali ndi kalata yochokera ku bungwe la apolisi pa dziko lonse (Interpol) chowatsimikizira kuti sanalandire uthenga uliwonse owadziwits akuti awamange pankhani ina iliyonse.\r\nKomabe poyankhula ndi nyuz- pepala ya Nation a Matemba ati palibe tsiku lomwe ACB inanena kuti mai Joyce Banda ndi mfulu pa nkhani zomwe anthu omwe akuyankha milanduyi anawatchula. I wo ati akufufuzabe nkhanizi kuphatikizaponso nkhani ya kayendetsedwa ka bungwel la Mudzi Transformation Trust (MTT) lomwe mai Joyce Banda anayambitsa mchaka cha 2014 ndi cholinga chomangira anthu osauka nyumba zabwino komanso kuwathandiza mu zosowa zina ndi zina. Ena mwa anthu omwe anatchula mayi Banda pa nkhanizi ndi a Oswald Lutepo omwe ali ku ndende , a Leonard Kalonga komanso malemu Treza Senzani.\r\nPoyankhula ndi wailesi ya Zodiak posachedwapa iwo ananenetsa kuti sanabe ndalama ya boma iliyonse ndipo ndi okonzeka kufufuzidwa ndi apolisi. Iwo  anatinso ali  ndi umboni omwe ukusonyeza kuti boma limakakamiza anthu ena kuti akachitire umboni wa bodza omwe ungathandizire kuti iwo azengedwe akhudzidwe ndi nkhani zosakaza chuma cha bomachi.\r\nMneneri wa mai Joyce Banda Andekuche Chanthunya wati ndi odabwa kuti bungwe la ACB layamba kusintha maganizo ake pa zakumangidwa kwa mai Banda.\r\nPa nkhani za ndale mai Banda akhala akutsindika kuti sayankhulapo kanthu pokhapokha atakumana ndi akuluakulu a achipani cha PP chomwe iwo akuti chikadali cha moyo ngakhale kuti ena mwa akulu-akulu ake ambiri monga a Brown Mpinganjira, a Ralph Jooma komanso a Uladi Mussa anatuluka chipanichi.\r\nEna akuganizira kuti mai Banda anakambirana ndi a Peter Mutharika kuti abwere ndipo adzawathandize ku chipani chawo cha DPP koma ena akuganiza kuti main Banda akhoza kuchita mgwirizano ndi chipani cha MCP ati kamba koti pa tsiku lomwe mayiwa amafika ku bwalo la ndege la chileka mu mzinda wa Blantyre, amayi ena omwe anavala nsalu za MCP anali komweko kuvina ndi amayi a PP omwe anakachingamira Dr. Joyce Banda.','local_news','2018-05-02','2018-05-02 08:37:23'),(70,'Kalembera wa zisankho ayamba pa 26 June','Bungwe loyendetsa chisankho mdzikomuno la Malawi Electroral Commission lalengeza kuti kalembera wa chisankho cha patatu ayamba pa 26 June osati pa 25 May monga mwa chikonzero cha poyamba.\r\n\r\nMkulu wa chisankho ku bungwe la MEC Sammy Al-fandika ndiye watsimikiza izi mchikalata chomwe ataulutsa ndipo ati izi zachitika kamba koti zipani komanso mabungwe anapereka madandaulo osiyanasiyana.\r\nBungweli lati kalembelayu azachitika m\'magawo asanu ndi limodzi (6) kuyambira chigawo chapakati pomwe ma boma a Kasungu, Dowa, Mchinji, Nkhotakota komanso Ntchisi adzayambe. Izi zidzachitika kuchokera pa 26 May mpaka 9 July\'\r\nKuchokera pa 13 mpaka 26 July kalembera adzachitika m\'maboma a LIlongwe , Salima, komanso Likoma.\r\nGawo lachitatu lidzayamba pa 30 July mpaka 12 August m\'maboma a Dedza, Blantyre , Nsanje komanso Ntcheu.\r\nGawo lachinayi lidzachitika pa 16 mpaka 29 August m\'maboma a Luchenza, Chiradzulu, Mwanza, Neno , Thyolo , Phalombe, Mulanje, Chikwawa ndipo gawo lachisanu lidzachitika pakati pa 2 ndi 15 September m\'maboma a Mangochi, Zomba, Balaka komanso Machinga.\r\nGawo lomaliza lidzakhudza ma boma a kumpoto kwa dziko lino omwe ndii Mzuzu, Karonga, Chitipa, Rumphi ndi Nkhatabay.\r\n\r\n\r\n','local_news','2018-05-03','2018-05-03 10:26:24'),(71,'Mneneri Bushiri aonekera ku polisi mdziko la Southa Africa','07-05-18  Mneneri Shephered Bushiri yemwe akukhala mdziko la South Africa loweruka madzulo anakaonekera ku polisi ina mdziko la South Africa pa nkhani yomwe akuti anatchula mzimayi wina kuti ndi mfiti pa nthawi yomwe amalalikira zaka zitatu zapitazo.\r\nApolisi a mdzikolo anapita ku mpingo wa a Bushiri komwe amafuna awatenge koma sanawapezeko ndipo madzulo ake cha m\'ma 6 koloko a Bushiri anakadzipereka okha ku polisiko. Apolisi analimbana kwambiri ndi achitetezo a Bushiri pa nthawi yomwe anapita ku mpingo wakeyo ati poganiza kuti amawanamiza kuti a Bushiri apita ku Malawi ndipo zinatengela oyimila a Bushiri pa milandu kuti ayankhule ndi apolisiwo ndipo bata linabwera.\r\nMzimayiyu yemwe ndi Lebogang Mpane anasuma milanduyi mwezi watha ndipo ofalitsa nkhani za a Bushiri Ephraim Nyondo watsimikiza izi.\r\nMasiku apitawa a Bushiri analembedwanso nkhani zoti akufufuzidwa ndi apolisi a mdziko la South Africa kamba kothawitsa ndalama zankhani nkhani kuchokera mdziko la South Africa kupititsa ku Malawi zinthu zomwe a Bushiri akhala akukana.','local_news','2018-05-07','2018-05-07 12:15:44'),(72,'Bullets Nkumadzulo - BB 1;  Moyale 0','07-05-18 Timu ya Nyasa Big Bullets lamulungu yakwanitsa kuchinya asilikali a Moyale chigoli chimodzi kwa du m\'masewero oyamba a ndime yachipulula ya Chikho cha Airtel Top 8 chomwe matimu asanu ndi anayi akulimbirana.\r\nKomatu chigolichi chomwe anachinya ndi Patrick Phiri pa bwalo la zamasewero la Kalulu ku Nchalo chinadza nthawi yowonjezera ithatha kale ndipo aliyense anavomereza kuti matimuwa alepherana.\r\nKoma Phiri yemwe analowa mchigawo chachiwiri atatulitsidwa Bright Munthali anavumbuluka  pa nthawi yomwe osewera a Moyale sanayembekeze.\r\nPanali chiyembekezo chakuti Nyasa Big Bullets ikanatha kuchinya zigoli zambiri koma sanagwiritse bwino ntchito mwayi omwe umapezeka\r\nMasewero achibwereza akachitikira ku Mzuzu ndipo pakufuika kuti a Moyale akagoletse zigoli zosachepera ziwiri kuti akapambane kufika mu ndime yomaliza ya mpikisanowu. Mphunzitsi wa Moyale Charles Kamanga wati tsogolo lawo lili pa masewero otsatira ngakhale anadandaula kuti pena masewerowa sanayimbilidwe bwino.\r\nNaye mphunzitsi wa timu ya Bullets Elia Kananji wati nkhondo ikadalipo ndipo anavomereza kuti mwayi wambiri ochinya zigoli sanaugwiritse ntchito.\r\nLoweluka timu ya Silver Strikers inagonjetsa timu ya Civo ndi chigoli chimodzi. Kumasewerowa kunali anthu ambiri kamba koti apeza ndalama zosachepera 7 million kwacha.\r\nM\'masewero a mpikisano wa chikho chachikulu mdzikomuno cha TNM Manoma alepherana mphamvu ndi Karonga United zinthu zomwe zinakwiyitsa otsatira timuyi omwe anafika ku bwalo la zamasewero la Balaka ndipo anafuna kumenya osula timuyi koma apolisi analowerapo mwachangu.\r\nTN Stars ya ku Kasungu yapambana masewero ake oyamba muchikho cha TNM itagonjetsa Masters Security ndi zigoli ziwiri kwa chimodzi\r\nKamuzu Barracks yagonja ndi zigoli zitatu kwa ziwiri ndi asilikali a Red Lions pa masewero omwe anali ku Mangochi pomwe Dwangwa United yalepherana ndi asilikali a Mafco pa masewero omwe anachitikira pa Nankhaka\r\n ','sports_news','2018-05-07','2018-05-22 06:52:15'),(73,'Jack Africa Chamangwana Wamwalira','Dziko la Malawi lataya mutu pa nkhani zamasewero - Jack Africa Chamangwana. A Chamangwana sanali munthu wamba pa mbiri  ya masewero mdzikomuno ndipo wamwalira pa udindo wa m\'modzi wa akulu akulu a timu ya Beforward wanderers.\r\nA Chamangwana amwalira ku chipatala chachikulu cha Queen Elizabeth mu mzinda wa Blantyre atadwala.  Malipoti akuti iwowa anagonekedwa mchipatala lachitatu lapitalo. \r\nMwazina a Chamangwana anali gawo limodzi la osewera omwe anathandiza timu ya mpira wa miyendo ya dziko lino kuti ikafike mu ndime yapamwamba mu chikho cha maiko a mu Africa  mchaka cha 1984 , ndipo ngati m\'modzi wa aphunzitsi anathandizanso timuyi kuti ikafikire ndime ina mu mpikisano omwewu mchaka cha 2010.\r\nKupatula kuphunzitsa timu ya mpira wa miyendo ya dziko lino, komanso Manoma, a Chamangwana anaphunzitsaponso matimu monga Kaizer Chiefs ya mdziko la South Africa komanso Young Africans ya mdziko la Tanzania.\r\nIwo analinso Mtsogoleri wa timu ya mpira wa miyendo ya dziko lino pomwe anapambana chikho china chapakati pa maiko a kum\'mawa ndi pakati pa Africa mzaka za m\'ma 1978 ndi 1979..\r\nM\'modzi wa akuluakulu a timu ya wanderers a Stevie Madeira wati imfayi yawakhudza kwambiri.','sports_news','2018-05-07','2018-05-07 12:31:09'),(74,'Chamangwana wagoneratu','09/05/18 Thupi la Katswiri osewera pa nkhani za masewero Jack Chamangwana yemwe anamwalira lamulungu lapitali aliika m\'manda ku Misesa mu mzinda wa Blantyre.\r\nKhamu la anthu kuphatikizapo akulu akulu a zamasewero, andale, amalonda komanso mtsogoleri wa dziko lino ndi wachiwiri wake anali nawo ku mwambowu.\r\nMtsogoleri wa dziko lino anati ndi okhudzidwa ndi imfa ya bambo chamngwana omwe asiya mbiri yosafufutika pa nkhani za masewero kamba ka luntha ndi kuchita bwino komwe anali nako.\r\nPoyankhula m\'malo mwa akubanja a Samuel Kaphuka anati banja lawo lataya mzati ndipo anayamika boma kamba ka thandizo lomwe apereka kuphatikizapo kugula bokosi.\r\nA Kaphuka anapemphanso mtsogoleri wa dziko lino kuti boma likhale ndi ndondomeo yapadera yothandizira osewera mpira mdzikomuno kuti pomwe asiya kusewera mpira ndipo akumana ndimavuto otere , azitha kulandira chisamaliro chapadera kamba koti masewero ali ndi kuthekera kotukula chuma cha dziko.\r\n\r\nA Chamangwana amwalira ku chipatala chachikulu cha Queen Elizabeth mu mzinda wa Blantyre atadwala.  Malipoti akuti iwowa anagonekedwa mchipatala lachitatu lapitalo atandaula ndi balo lomwe anali nalo lomwe achipatala napeza kuti linayamba ndi shuga ndipo panthawiyi nkuti itakwera kwambiri.\r\nMwazina a Chamangwana anali gawo limodzi la osewera omwe anathandiza timu ya mpira wa miyendo ya dziko lino kuti ikafike mu ndime yapamwamba mu chikho cha maiko a mu Africa  mchaka cha 1984 , ndipo ngati m\'modzi wa aphunzitsi anathandizanso timuyi kuti ikafikire ndime ina mu mpikisano omwewu mchaka cha 2010.\r\nKupatula kuphunzitsa timu ya mpira wa miyendo ya dziko lino, komanso Manoma, a Chamangwana anaphunzitsaponso matimu monga Kaizer Chiefs ya mdziko la South Africa komanso Young Africans ya mdziko la Tanzania.\r\nIwo analinso Mtsogoleri wa timu ya mpira wa miyendo ya dziko lino pomwe anapambana chikho china chapakati pa maiko a kum\'mawa ndi pakati pa Africa mzaka za m\'ma 1978 ndi 1979..\r\nM\'modzi wa akuluakulu a timu ya wanderers a Stevie Madeira wati imfayi yawakhudza kwambiri.','sports_news','2018-05-09','2018-05-09 14:39:27'),(75,'MCP yabwezeretsa a Msowoya, Kaliwo, Kabwila andi ena pa mipando.','09/05/18 Chipani cha MCP chabwezera mchipani ena mwa akulu akulu ake omwe anayamba achotsedwa  kamba ka kusagwirizana pa mfundo zina za utsogoleri.\r\nEna mwa akulu akulu omwe abwezeretsedwa ndi wachiwiri kwa mtsogoleri wa chipani cha MCP a  Richard Msowoya, Mlembi wamkulu wa chipanichi a Gustav Kaliwo, msungichuma a Tony Kandiero , wachiwiri kwa mlembi wamkulu mchipanichi a  James Chatonda Kaunda komanso ofalitsa nkhani za chipanichi mayi Jessie Kabwila.\r\nWachiwiri kwa mtsogoleri wa chipani cha MCP a MacDonald Lombola alengeza izi pa msonkhano wa olemba nkhani omwe unachitikira ku likulu la chipanichi mu mzinda wa Lilongwe.\r\nA lombola ati chiganizochi chadza potsatira zomwe komiti yayikulu yoyendetsa chipanichi yagwirizana kuti chipanichi chikuyenera kuthetsa kusamvana kulikonse komwe kungachititse kuti chipanichi chisadzachite bwino pa masankho omwe ali nkudza mchaka cha 2019.\r\nA Kaliwo komanso a Chakwera anasiyana maganizo pomwe anadzudzula a Chakwera podzera mchikalata chomwe chinabwera poyela kuti mtsogoleri wao sakutsatira malamulo oyendetsera chipanichi.\r\nMwazina a Msowoya ndi a Kaliwo adati siokondwa ndi ndondomeko zomwe akutsata pofuna kusankha ma udindo mchipani cha MCP.\r\n\r\nIzi zachitika pomwe khothi linapatsa mphamvu chipani cha  MCP  kuchititsa msonkhano waukulu omwe a Kaliwo adakasuma ku khoti ndipo nawonso dzulo laliwisili apatsidwanso chikalata china ndi bwalo la milandu chotsutsana ndi zomwe khothi lina linanena zomwe zachidziwikire kuti chipanichi chalingalira kuti izi ziwachedwetsa ndikuwataitsa nthawi.','sports_news','2018-05-09','2018-05-09 14:39:15'),(76,'MCP ichititsa msonkano waukulu loweruka lino','10/05/18 Chipani cha Malawi Congress MCP chati msonkhano wake waukulu uchitika loweluka likudzali pa 12 May, 2018 mu mzinda wa Lilongwe.\r\n\r\nPali kuthekera kwakulu koti a Chakwera ndiwo akasankhidwe kukhala Mtsogoleri wa chipanichi ndipo a Sidik Mia ndiwo akhale wachiwiri wawo.\r\n\r\nAkulu akulu a chipani cha MCP atsimikiza kuti alandira uthenga oti akonzekeretse anthu awo kuti akapange msonkhano waukulu.\r\n\r\nPali chiyembekezo choti ku Blantyre kuchoka anthu 104 omwe akavote ku msonkhanowu.\r\n\r\nMlembi wamkulu wa chipani cha MCP yemwe wangobwezeretsedwa kumene pa udindo wake Gustave Kaliwo wauza nyumba zina zosindikiza mawu kuti  anayankhulana ndi a Chakwera pa zakufunika kwa msonkhanowu.\r\nMsonkhano waukuluwu ukuchitika pomwe khothi lalikulu kwambiri lachotsa chiletso chomwe a Kaliwo ndi anzawo anatenga.\r\nWachiwiri kwa mlembi wa chipani cha MCP  a Eisenhower Mkaka ati ngakhale kuti mlanduwu udzapitilira pa 17 May, iwo akukhulupilira kuti sudzasintha kalikonse kukhudza zotsatira za msonkhano omwe ukuchitika loweruka.\r\n\r\nMCP inabwezeretsanso mchipani ana mwa akuluakulu ake monga a Richard Msowoya, James Chatonda komanso a Jessie Kabwila kungotchulapo ochepa chabe.\r\n','local_news','2018-05-11','2018-05-11 10:18:29'),(77,'Bungwe la MACRA lachenjeze nyumba zoulutsa mawu.','11/05/18 Bungwe loyang\'anira ntchito zofalitsa ma uthenga pogwiritsa ntchito njira zamakono la Malawi Communications Regulatory Authority (MACRA) lachenjeza nyumba zoulutsa mau kuti zikuyenera kugwira ntchito zake mosakondera komanso motsata malamulo.\r\n\r\nIzi zanenedwa pa msonkhano omwe bungweli linachititsa mu mzinda wa Lilongwe.\r\nBungweli lati litseka nyumba zomwe zimagwira ntchito mosatsata ndondomeko zabwino zakayendetsedwe ka chuma komanso zomwe zikuulutsa mau mokondera ndi mosatsata malamulo ati kamba koti izi zikusemphana ndi malamulo omwe amayenera kutsata powapatsa ziphaso zoyamba kugwilira ntchito zawo mdzikomuno.\r\n\r\nM\'modzi mwa akulu akulu ku bungwe la MACRA a Benson Tembo wati ubwino wake nkhaniyi siyachilendo kamba koti eni nyumbazi amadziwa bwino lomwe za ndondomekozi.\r\nIwo ati ndondomeko ya zachuma ya nyumbazi imathandiza kuti bungweli lizitolera bwino msonkho wina omwe mwa zina cholinga chake ndikupititsa patsogolo ntchito za makina a intaneti komanso kafalitsidwe ka mauthenga potsata njira za makono.\r\nPoyankhapo pa madandaulo oti nyumba zofalitsa nkhani sizimagwira ntchito zake motsata malamulo maka pomwe dziko la malawi likuyandikira zisankho  m\'modzi mwa akulu akuklu a bungwe la MARCA  a Fergus Lipenga wati sasiya kulondoloza momwe nyumbazi zikugwilira ntchito  mdzikomuno.\r\nA lipenga apempha eni nyumba zoulutsa mauzi komanso olembankhani kuti apewe mchitidwe omatenga gawo polemba nkhan zawo ndikuti athandize dziko la Malawi pouza anthu chilungamo chokha- chokha.\r\n','local_news','2018-05-11','2018-05-11 10:19:17'),(78,'Ng\'ambi ndi Phiri Jr. sakupita ku COSAFA','11/05/18 Osewera a timu ya mpira wa miyendo ya dziko lino omwe ali ku South Africa ku timu ya Platinum Stars yomwe yatuluku mu ligi yayikulu ya mdzikolo awasiya pa zokonzeker aza ulendo wa ku Cosafa komwe timu ya dziko lino ikachite masewero ake.\r\nM\'malo mwake mphunzitsi wa timuyi watenga osewera ena akunja monga Richard Mbulu yemwe akusewera ku Portugal , Dalitso Sailesi yemwe ali ku Zambia, John Banda kuchokera ku Mozambique, Robin Ngalande komanso Chawanangwa Kaonga.\r\nMphunzitsi wa timu ya dziko linoyi wati osewerawa ndi omwe adatsindika kuti adzapezeka.\r\nKomabe ena ati kusiyidwa kwa Robert Ng\'ambi komanso Gerald Phiri Junior  kwadza kamba koti awiriwa adakana kusewera nawo masewero omwe timu ya dziko lino idali nawo ndi timu ya uganda Mwezi wa March ponena kuti anali otanganidwa pofuna kuthandiza timu yawo kuti isatuluke mu ligi yayikulu ya dzikolo kamba koti pa nthawiyo mpikisano unali utavuta.\r\nKupezeka kwa osewera akunja mu timuyi yomwe ikupita ku mpikisano wa Cosafa kwadzetsabe zokamba-kamba maka kamba koti ena akukhulupilira kuti uwu unali mwayi oti mphunzitsiyu akanagwiritsa ntchito osewera omwe ali kale mdzikomuno kuti akaonetse luso lawo.\r\nMtsogoleri wa timuyi Limbikani Mzava adati sadzapezeka pa masewerowa kamba koti akukhulupilira kuti ndi masewero omwe akufunika osewera omwe ali mdziko muno kuti akapeze luso lina.\r\nGabadinho Mhango komanso Atusaye Nyondo sasewera nawonso ati kamba koti anavulala.\r\n','sports_news','2018-05-11','2018-05-11 10:45:35'),(79,'Ng\'ambi ndi Phiri Jr. sakupita ku COSAFA','11/05/18 Osewera a timu ya mpira wa miyendo ya dziko lino omwe ali ku South Africa ku timu ya Platinum Stars yomwe yatuluku mu ligi yayikulu ya mdzikolo awasiya pa zokonzeker aza ulendo wa ku Cosafa komwe timu ya dziko lino ikachite masewero ake.\r\nM\'malo mwake mphunzitsi wa timuyi watenga osewera ena akunja monga Richard Mbulu yemwe akusewera ku Portugal , Dalitso Sailesi yemwe ali ku Zambia, John Banda kuchokera ku Mozambique, Robin Ngalande komanso Chawanangwa Kaonga.\r\nMphunzitsi wa timu ya dziko linoyi wati osewerawa ndi omwe adatsindika kuti adzapezeka.\r\nKomabe ena ati kusiyidwa kwa Robert Ng\'ambi komanso Gerald Phiri Junior  kwadza kamba koti awiriwa adakana kusewera nawo masewero omwe timu ya dziko lino idali nawo ndi timu ya uganda Mwezi wa March ponena kuti anali otanganidwa pofuna kuthandiza timu yawo kuti isatuluke mu ligi yayikulu ya dzikolo kamba koti pa nthawiyo mpikisano unali utavuta.\r\nKupezeka kwa osewera akunja mu timuyi yomwe ikupita ku mpikisano wa Cosafa kwadzetsabe zokamba-kamba maka kamba koti ena akukhulupilira kuti uwu unali mwayi oti mphunzitsiyu akanagwiritsa ntchito osewera omwe ali kale mdzikomuno kuti akaonetse luso lawo.\r\nMtsogoleri wa timuyi Limbikani Mzava adati sadzapezeka pa masewerowa kamba koti akukhulupilira kuti ndi masewero omwe akufunika osewera omwe ali mdziko muno kuti akapeze luso lina.\r\nGabadinho Mhango komanso Atusaye Nyondo sasewera nawonso ati kamba koti anavulala.\r\n','local_news','2018-05-11','2018-05-11 10:46:56'),(80,'Mabungwe Akaikira Chidwi cha Boma Kwa Achinyamata','Mabungwe omwe si aboma ati sakuganiza kuti chidwi chomwe boma laonetsa ponena kuti mu ndondomeko ya zachuma ya chaka chino achinyamata apeza mwai wa ntchito ndiyowona. Ambiri alankhulapo kuti ndondomeko ya chumayi yomwe yaperekdwa ku nyumba ya malamulo lachisanu lapitali ndi olemekezeka a Goodall Gondwe yangokhala yokopela anthu kuti adzavotere chipani cha DPP.\r\nMwazina a Gondwe anatsimikiza kuti kuyambira mwezi wa July achinyamata okwana 17 thousand apeza mwayi wa ntchito. Ndunayi inati boma laika padera ndalama zokwana 9.8 billion kwacha zomwe achinyamata agwiritse ntchito pobwezeretsa mitengo ndi zachilengedwe komanso kuwapatsa mwai ophunzira ntchito maka kwa iwo omwe angomaliza kumene maphunziro awo.\r\nM\'modzi wa akulu akulu a mabungwewa ndi a Charles Kajoloweka a bungwe la Youth and Society (YAS) omwe ati nzodabwitsa kuti boma l ladzidzimukira pa nkhani zotukula achinyama pomwe zaka zapitazi achinyamatawa akhala akudandaula.\r\nKoma izi malinga ndi m\'neneri wa boma a Nicholus Dausi ndi zosamveka kamba koti boma linakhazikitsa ndondomeko yotukula miyoyo ya chinyamata ya zaka zisanu komwe ganizoli lachokera ndipo sakuona chifukwa chomwe ndondomekoyi ingalephere kupitilizidwa mtsogolomu.\r\nA Dausi ati boma lili ndi chidwi potukula achinyamata mdzikomuno ndipo panafunika kuti anthu agwile ntchito limodzi mdzikomuno kuthandiza kuti miyoyo yawo ipite patsogolo.','local_news','2018-05-21','2018-05-21 08:14:04'),(81,'Manoma Yadutsa !','Ntchito ilipo, Manoma adutsa kufika gawo lomaliza la ndime yachipulula ya chikho cha Airtel Top 8 komwe matimu anayi akwapulane kulimbirana ndime yotsiriza yomwe matimu awiri adzachite mpikisano omaliza.\r\nJoseph Shakira Kamwendo ndiye anamwetsa chigoli cha Be-forward Wanderers kugonjetsanso asilikali a Kamuzu Barracks kachiwiri. M\'masewero oyamba asilikaliwa anagonjanso ndi chigoli chimodzi zomwe zikutanthauza kuti timuyi yagonja ndi zigoli ziwiri kwa du.\r\nChigoli cha Kamwendo chinali cha penate yomwe inamenyedwa bwino kwambiri kupangitsa khamu la anthu omwe anasonkhana kudzaonelera masewerowa kupumira m\'mwamba.\r\nAtatha masewero a mpira Kamwendo anauza atolankhani kuti masewerowa anali ovuta ndipo anali okondwa kuti anachinya chigoli chofunikira.\r\nMphunzitsi wa timu ya Kamuza Barracks Temwa Msuku anavomereza kulephera koma anati si okondwa ndi momwe oyimbira masewero anagwilira ntchito yake pa tsikulo.\r\nChipukuta misozi kwa asilikaliwa anali Dave Banda yemwe anasankhidwa kukhala osewera yemwe anachita bwino pa masewerowa ndipo analandira MK 50, 000\r\nLoweruka lapitali timu ya Big Bullets nayonso inapambana kufika ndime yomweyi itagonjetsanso asilikali a Moyale pa kwawo.','sports_news','2018-05-21','2018-05-21 07:16:06'),(82,'Ana aonetsa ukulu.  Angola 1  -  Malawi 4','Zovuta kumvetsa koma zachitika. Timu ya osewera mpira wa miyendo a chisodzera  ya dziko lino yachita zakupsa zomwe mwina iwo eni ndi mhunzitsi wawo Meke Mwse amayembekeza kuti zingachitike posasantha timu ya chisodzera ya ku  Angola ndi zigoli zinayi kwa chimodzi zomwe zachititsa timu ya dziko linoyi kupitilira mu ndime ina ya mpikisano wa chikho cha mu Africa cha matimu achisodzera. Awa anali masewero achibwereza kamba koti masewero oyamba omwe anachitikira mdziko muno, timuyi inagonja ndi zigoli ziwiri kwa chimodzi.\r\nKelvin Kadzinje ndiye anatsekulira ntibu wa zigoliwu patangotha mphindi khumi za masewerowa ndipo sipanathe nthawi pomwe Auspicious Kadzongola anaonjezera moto wina. Pomwe zimatha mphindi makumi atatu naye Chikondi Mbeta anapeza mpata omwetsa chigoli china . Atalefuka ngati mlenje obwera chimanja manja ku uzimba ndipo amayembekeza kuti akupume ndikulingalira zomwe zawachitikira chigawo choyamba  Peter Banda anachiona chanzeru kuthiranso chigoli china zomwe zinabalalitsa anayamata a Angola pamaso pa makolo awo ndi gulu la ochemelera timuyi.\r\nChigawo chachiwiri eni bwaloli anayesa kuponya mzinga omwe unagwedeza ukonde wa golo la timu ya Malawi koma sunali okwanira kuphwasula linga lomwe anyamatawa anamanga.\r\nMphunzitsi wa timuyi yemwe analonjeza kuti akabweza anati osewera ake anachita chamuna, sanakhumudwitse ndipo anathamanga kosalema ngati mkango wanjala kuthamingitsa gwape. \r\nMkulu wa bungwe la FAM Walter Nyamilandu Manda wati zotsatira za masewerowa ndizonyaditsa ndipo wati anyamatawa achita zomwe ambiri amaziona kuti nzosatheka.\r\nNyamilandu wauza nyuzipepala ya Nation yomwe yasindikiza nkhaniyi kuti anyamatawa akupeleka chiyembekezo ku dziko la Malawi.','sports_news','2018-05-21','2018-05-21 08:15:07'),(83,'Mwawi Kumwenda , Joyce Mvula azunguza matimu akunja!','Akatswiri a mpira wa ntchembere mbaye omwe akusewera kunja kwa dziko lino Mwawi Kumwenda komanso Joyce Mvula akupitilira kuchita bwino ku matimu awo omwe akusewera.\r\nloweluka lapitali Mwai Kumwenda yemwe ali ku Australia  anathandizira timu yake ya Melbourne Vixens kuti ifike pa nambala ya chiwiri mu mpikisano wina atagonjetsa timu ya Adelaide Thunderbirds ndi zigoli 72 kwa 50. Makina osindikiza nkhani za timu yomwe Mwawi akusewera anasindikiza kuti Mwawi akusewera bwino osati pang\'ono ndipo pa masewero apitawa anapeza mwawi ochinya okwana 47 ndipo sanaphonyepo kutanthauza kuti yekha anakwanitsa zigoli 47. Zateremu timu ya Mwai tsopano ili ndi ma pointsi 21 pomwe anzawo omwe awachinyawo nawo analimbikila kuti apambaneko koyamba chiyambireni mpikisanowo koma sizinatheke. Mwawi Kumwenda anati ndi okondwa kuti timu yawo pali mgwirizano ndipo ndikuti anakwanitsa kupambana masewerowa. Ku England Joyce Mvula yemwe akusewera ku Manchester Thunder anapambananso kachiwiri kukhala osewera wabwino pa masewero omwe anapikisana ndi timu ya Seven Stars ya komweko. Iyeyu anambananso mphoto ya osewera othyakuka bwino pa mwezi watha zomwe anati zikumulimbikitsa.\r\nM\'mau ake Mvula wati akuyamika chimvano chomwe chilipo ku timu yake ndipo anati ali ndi chiyembekezo choti achita bwino koposa mtsogolomu.','sports_news','2018-05-21','2018-05-21 07:56:43'),(84,'Mapepela a pulasiti akupha ziweto , kuononga nthaka','Dziko la Malawi linachita nawo mwambo okumbukira zachilengedwe pa dziko lonse omwe mutu wake unali kuthetsa mapulasitiki owononga chilengedwe. Tsikuli linakhazikitsidwa ndi bungwe la mgwirizano wa maiko pa dziko lonse la United Nations ndicholinga cholimbikitsa maiko kulimbikitsa kofunika kusamalira zachilengedwe.\r\nLoweruka lapitali bungwe la olemba nkhani za chilengedwe la Association of Environment Journalists in Malawi AEJ linakonza ulendo wa ndawala omwe cholinga chake kunali kuzindikiritsa mtundu wa a Malawi za kufunika kopewa kugwiritsa ntchito komanso kutaya mosasamala mapepala a pulasitiki.\r\nAnthu ochuluka anatenga nawo gawo pa ulendo wa ndawalawu ndipo m\'modzi wa akuluakulu a nthambi ya boma yowona zachilengedwe mai Taonga Mbale Luka anati amalawi akuyenera kuzindikira kuti mapepala a pulasitiki sakupereka chiyembekezo cha tsogolo la bwino ku dizko la Malawi.\r\nKupatulu kupha ziweto komanso kugugitsa nthaka, mapepalawa amatha kuyambitsa matenda a khansa, kudzetsa kusefukira kwa madzi komba koti amatseka njira zodutsa madzi  komanso amatha kukhudza ntchito za usodzi kunyanja.\r\nKuno ku Malawi ntchito yoletsa kupanga, Kugulitsa komanso kuitanitsa kunja mapepala a pulasitiki inayamba yayima kamba ka kuchedwa kwa chigamulo cha khothi.\r\n ','sports_news','2018-06-12','2018-06-12 09:18:46'),(85,'Khoti lavomereza kuletsa mapepala a pulasitiki','Bwalo lalikulu la milandu la High court ku Blantyre lagamula kuti boma likhoza kupitilira ndi malingaliro ake oletsa mapepala a pulasitiki omwe ali ndi chiopsezo chachikulu ku chilengedwe kamba koti amachedwa kuwola. Izi zili chomwechi potsatira zomwe Jaji wina oweruza milandu ku bwaloli a Healey Potani agamula pochotsa chiletso chomwe anatenga eni kampani zopanga  mapepala a pulasitiki.\r\nBoma linayamba kuletsa mapepalawa mwezi wa June mchaka cha 2015 koma eni kampani zopanga mapepalawa akhala akunena kuti akufuna atapatsidwa nthawi yokwanira kuti amalize kugulitsa mapepala a nkhaninkhani omwe anapanga kale komanso kuti apeze makina atsopano omwe angawathandize kupanga mapepala oyenelera. Koma boma linauza bwalori kuti anthuwa anapatsidwa chenjezo komanso nthawi yokwanira kuti akonze mavuto omwe anadandaula kotero kukakamiza khoti kuti lisungebe chiletsochi kunali kusokoneza zinthu.\r\nPakadali pano boma kudzera kwa mkulu wa nthambi ya boma yowona za chilengedwe mai Taonga Mbale Luka ati ndi okondwa ndi chigamulo chomwe bwalori lapereka. Iwo ati pakadalipano apitilira ndi ndondomeko zomwe zinalipo zoletsa makampani ndi anthu  kupanga, kugulitsa, kuitanitsa  komanso kugwiritsa ntchito mapepala a pulasitiki opyapyala.\r\nChigamulochi chabwera patangotha masiku ochepa mabungwe osiyanasiyana atayankhulapo pa za chigamulo pa nkhaniyi chomwe chinatenga zaka ziwiri chisanatuluke.\r\nMwa zina mapepala  a pulasitike amagugitsa nthaka, kupha ziweto, kutseka maenje odutsa zoipa komanso madzi komanso amatha kuyambitsa matenda a Khansa pomwe aotchedwa kamba koti mpweya wake ndi oipa.\r\n','local_news','2018-06-19','2018-06-19 08:22:34'),(86,'Khoti lavomereza kuletsa mapepala a pulasitiki','Bwalo lalikulu la milandu la High court ku Blantyre lagamula kuti boma likhoza kupitilira ndi malingaliro ake oletsa mapepala a pulasitiki omwe ali ndi chiopsezo chachikulu ku chilengedwe kamba koti amachedwa kuwola. Izi zili chomwechi potsatira zomwe Jaji wina oweruza milandu ku bwaloli a Healey Potani agamula pochotsa chiletso chomwe anatenga eni kampani zopanga  mapepala a pulasitiki.\r\nBoma linayamba kuletsa mapepalawa mwezi wa June mchaka cha 2015 koma eni kampani zopanga mapepalawa akhala akunena kuti akufuna atapatsidwa nthawi yokwanira kuti amalize kugulitsa mapepala a nkhaninkhani omwe anapanga kale komanso kuti apeze makina atsopano omwe angawathandize kupanga mapepala oyenelera. Koma boma linauza bwalori kuti anthuwa anapatsidwa chenjezo komanso nthawi yokwanira kuti akonze mavuto omwe anadandaula kotero kukakamiza khoti kuti lisungebe chiletsochi kunali kusokoneza zinthu.\r\nPakadali pano boma kudzera kwa mkulu wa nthambi ya boma yowona za chilengedwe mai Taonga Mbale Luka ati ndi okondwa ndi chigamulo chomwe bwalori lapereka. Iwo ati pakadalipano apitilira ndi ndondomeko zomwe zinalipo zoletsa makampani ndi anthu  kupanga, kugulitsa, kuitanitsa  komanso kugwiritsa ntchito mapepala a pulasitiki opyapyala.\r\nChigamulochi chabwera patangotha masiku ochepa mabungwe osiyanasiyana atayankhulapo pa za chigamulo pa nkhaniyi chomwe chinatenga zaka ziwiri chisanatuluke.\r\nMwa zina mapepala  a pulasitike amagugitsa nthaka, kupha ziweto, kutseka maenje odutsa zoipa komanso madzi komanso amatha kuyambitsa matenda a Khansa pomwe aotchedwa kamba koti mpweya wake ndi oipa.\r\n','local_news','2018-06-19','2018-06-19 08:22:39'),(87,'Siliva yatsogola pomwe Manona yayaka moto! -TNM Ligi','25th June, 2018\r\nMasewero olimbirana chikho cha TNM akupitilira ndipo pofika lamulungu madzulo zinali zitadziwika kuti Silver Strikers ndiyo ikulamulira ukadaulo wa chikhochi pakadalipano itapeza ma pointsi atatu pa masewero ake omwe inali nawo ndi timu ya Karonga United ku Karonga. Karonga United inagonja ndi zigoli ziwiri kwa chimodzi ndipo izi zachititsa anyamata a Silver kukhala ndi ma pointsi 23 kuchokera ku masewero khumi omwe asewera kale pakadalipano.\r\nVictor Limbani komanso Jack Chiona ndiwo anagoletsa zigoli za Silver pomwe Sherriff Shamama ndiye anamwetsa chigoli cha chipepeso cha osewera a Silver Strikers. Mkulu wina  otsogolera timu ya Silver Strikers Francis Songo anati ndi okondwa kuti zomwe amalingalira zatheka ndipo akufunitsitsa atapitiliza kuchita bwino pa masewero omwe akubwera mtsogolomu.\r\nPa masewero ena omwe analipo kumapeto a sabatayi Manoma atolera ma pointsi asanu ndi imodzi 6 zomwe zachititsa kuti akwere kufika pa nambala 8 ndipo ali ndi ma points 14 tsopano kuchokera ku masewero asanu ndi atatu 8 . Lamulungu anathira mizinga nkhwazi zaku area 30 ndipo pakutha pa zonse mizinga itatu inagwedeza ukonde wa apolisiwa, zida zawo zomwe komanso pakwawo. 3-0.\r\nLoweruka nyerere zinakokera ku una asilikali a Kamuzu Barracks nkuwamwetsa fumbi la zigoli ziwiri koma anabweza ndi chimodzi chomwe sichinapheretu nyerere zonse.\r\nSteven Madeira yemwe ndi m\'modzi wa ophunzitsa Manoma anati ndi okondwa kuti mphamvu zabweramo ndikuti omwe anayamba kuwaseka kuti zawo zada, akuyenera kuganiza kawiri.\r\nBlue Eagles yomwe yagonja masewerowa inati kwa iwo sanaseweretse anyamata omwe akuwadalira pokonzekera masewero omaliza a chikho cha Airtel omwe aliko kumathero a sabatayi. Essau Kanyenda ndiye anagoletsa zigoli ziwiri za za wamders pomwe Peter Wadabwa ndiye anatsindika ndi mzinga omaliza.\r\nM\'masewero ena Masters security yabuulitsa mikango ya ku Kaning\'ina -Red Lions ndi chigoli chimodzi kwa chilowere pomwe Azam Tigers ndi Nchalo United anafanana mphamvu pogoletsana chigoli chimodzi kwa chimodzi.','sports_news','2018-06-25','2018-06-25 08:52:50'),(88,'Anong\'a asemphana ndi Airtel Money?','25th June, 2018\r\nSizikudziwika ngati katswiri osewera pakati  ku timu ya Nyasa Big Bullets Fischer Kondowe yemwe anthu amangoti Anong\'a asewere nawo masewero omaliza a chikho cha Airtel Top 8  omwe aliko kumapeto a sabata ino.\r\nAnong\'a anavulala pa masewero apitawa ndipo sanasewero nawo masewero a chikho cha TNM omwe timu ya Nyasa Big Bullets inasewera ndi Dwangwa United ndipo anatha 2:2.\r\nM\'modzi wa otsogolera anyamata a Nyasa Big Bullets James Chilapondwa anati Fischer ndi m\'modzi wa osewera yemwe akumudalira kamba koti samafooka chisawawa komanso ali ndi kuthekera luso lomwe alinalo kamba koti wakhala akusewera  mpira kwa nthawi yayitali. \r\nChilapondwa wati osewerayu sikuti wavulala kodetsa nkhawa koma sanafune kuti asewere masewero ndi Blue Eagles powewa kuvalala kwambiri.\r\nOphunztsa timu ya Nyasa Big Bullets Rogers Yasini wati masewero akubwerawa akhala ovuta ndipo zokonzekera zomwe ziyambe lero akukhulupilira kuti Anong\'a apezekako.\r\nNayo timu ya Eagles yomwe yagonja kwa Silver Strikers inati osewera ake odalilika sanasewere sabata ino pokonzekera mpira wa wafa-wafa omwe uliko loweruka lino ku bwalo la zamasewero la Bingu mu mzinda wa Lilongwe.\r\n','sports_news','2018-06-25','2018-06-25 09:10:18'),(89,'Chilima wapempha amalawi kuti akalembetse  mu kaundula wa chisankho!','                                                                                        25th June, 2018 \r\nWachiwiri kwa mtsogoleri wa dziko lino Saulos Klauss Chilima wapempha a Malawi kuti akalembetse mu kaundula wa chisankho yemwe wayambika m\'madera ena a dziko lino. A Chilima amayankhula izi pomwe anakakhala nawo pa mwambo wa mapemhero a mpingo wa katolika wa Kagwa oyera mu mzinda wa Lilongwe.\r\nA chilima anati voti ndi chida chokhacho chomwe nzika za dziko lino zingagwiritse ntchito posintha zinthu mdziko muno.\r\n\" Kusintha mtundu wa nkhuku sikusosola nthenga ayi koma kusintha Tambala\" anatero a Chilima kwinaku anthu akuomba m\'manja, kuseka komanso kululutira.\r\nAka sikoyamba a Chilima kuyakhula mokuluwika komanso kugwiritsa ntchito miyambi.\r\nA chilima anati chisankho si monga masewero a mpira omwe anthu amakhala kunja nkumaonelera zikuchitika koma kuti ndizofunika aliyense kutengapo gawo pokalembetsa komanso kudzaponya voti monga zifunikira.\r\nBungwe la zachisankho la MEC linalengeza kuti kalembera wa chisankho ayambika pa 26 June mpaka pa 9 November chakachino m\'magawo osiyana siyana.\r\nGawo loyamba liyambika pa 26 June lachiwiri pomwe kalembera akhale akuchitika ku Dowa, Kasungu komanso Ntchisi mpaka pa 9 July.\r\nA Chilima adachititsa msonkhano wa olemba nkhani komwe adati akulingalira zotuluika mchipani cha DPP ndipo zoyankhula zawo zakhala zili zonyazitsa boma maka ku nkhani za katangale.\r\nKomabe mneneri wa boma a Nicholus Dausi adayankhapo a Chilima kuti iwo ngati wachiwiri kwa mtsogoleri wa dziko lino akuyenera kuchitapo kanthu pothetsa katangale kamba koti ali mu ulamuliro omwewo.\r\n','local_news','2018-06-25','2018-06-25 10:52:21'),(90,'Malamulo astopano a malonda  Fodya athandiza alimi -TCC','                                                                                        25th June, 2018 \r\nBungwe loyendetsa malonda a Fodya mdziko muno la TCC lati lili ndi chikhulupiliro kuti aphungu a kunyumba ya malamulo adutsitsa bilo yokhudza kuunikidwanso kwa malamulo oyendetsera ulimi komanso malonda a fodya mdziko muno.\r\nMkulu wa bungwe la TCC a Kaisi Sadala ndiwo anena izi pa msonkhano wa olemba nkhani. \r\nI wo ati cholinga cha malamulo atsopanowa mwa zina mdikuteteza alimi kwa akambele-mbele komanso mtundu wa fodya omwe dziko lino limalima.\r\nIwo atinso malamulowa akavomerezedwa adzathandiza kuthetsa mchitidwe wa a mkhala pakati pa omwe amagula fodya kwa alimi pa mitengo yotsika komanso mosavomerezeka.\r\nIwo ati a mkhalapakati omwe amagula fodyayu kwa alimi ndi omwe amatumiza fodya osasankha bwino ku msika zinthu zomwe zimachititsa kuti malonda a fodya azisokonekera mdzikomuno ndikukhaulitsa alimi omwe amakhala avutika chaka chonse kulima fodyayu.\r\nPalinso malipoti akuti anthu ena kuphatikizapo ogula fodya komanso onyamula fodya apindula ndi malamulo atsopanowa.\r\nImodzi mwa kampani zogula fodya mdzikomuno ya JTI Leaf yati lamuloli likavomerezedwa lipangitsa kuti malonda kapena ulimi wa  mgwirizano kapena kuti kontilakiti pakati pa alimi a fodya komanso makampani zikhale zovomerezeka ndi malamulo a dziko lino.\r\nNduna ya zamalimidwe a Joseph Mwanamvekha yatsimikizira nyuzipepala ya Daily Times kuti sabata ino biloyi iyamba kuoneka pa mandandanda wa zokambirana omwe umatulutsidwa ndi nyumba ya malamuloyi.\r\nMalamulo a fodya a pakadalipano ndi akele kwambiri kamba koti anapangidwa mchaka cha 1979 zomwe ndi zaka 38 zapitazo ndip zintha zambiri sizikugwirizana ndi momwe zinthu zasinthira pakadalipano.','local_news','2018-06-25','2018-06-25 10:51:18'),(91,'Kalembera wa chisankho wayambika','26-06-18\r\nBungwe loyendetsa chisankho la Malawi Electoral Commission MEC lero layamba ntchito yolemba nzika za dziko lino mu kaundula wa chisankho kuti zidzaponye nawo voti ya patatu mwezi wa May chaka cha mawa.\r\nMneneri wa bungwe la MEC a Sangwani Mwafulirwa ati zokonzekera zonse za kalemberayu zayenda bwino kamba koti katundu komanso zipangizo zoyenelera azitumiza kale ku malo oyenelera.\r\nKalemberayu wayamba ku Kasungu, Dedza ndi Salima ndipo bungweli lapempha onse omwe anakwanitsa zaka 18 kapena adzakhala atakwanitsa zaka 18 pa tsiku loponya voti kuti akalembetse.\r\nA Mwafulirwa atinso  apolisi okwana 589 afika kumalo 280 komwe kukuchitika kalemberayu. Iwowa atsimikizanso kuti omwe alibe chiphaso cha unzika akuyenera kupita ku malo omwe kukachitikire kalembera kamba koti bungwe loona za kalembera wa u unzika la National Registration Bureau latumiza anthu ake omwe azikalemba anthu omwe sanalembetse mu kaundula wa unzika. Omwe alibe chiphaso cha unzika sakuloledwa kuchita nawo kalemberayu.\r\nKalemberayu achitika m\'magawo asanu ndi atatu kudzafika pa 9 November , 2018 koma gawo loyamba litha pa 9 July.\r\nAnthu pafupifupi 9 million ndiwo akuyembekezeka kutenga nawo gawo pa kalemberayu malinga ndi bungwe la zachisankho al Malawi electoral Commission.\r\nBungweli latsimikizanso kuti lakambirana ndi ogwira ntchito kalembera a m\'boma la Kasungu omwe amafuna kunyanyala ntchitoyi ati kamba ka kuchepa kwa malipirol. Ogwira ntchitoyi akupatsidwa MK 65, 0000 kwa sabata ziwiri kuti agwiritse ntchito popeza chakudya, malo ogona, na units a foni ndi zina zofunikira pamoyo wa munthu. \r\n','local_news','2018-06-26','2018-06-27 09:47:48'),(92,'Wadabwa waitanidwa ku Egypt','27/06/18\r\nOsewera wa kutsogolo kwa timu ya Mighty Be Forward Wanderers kapenanso kungoti Manoma waitanidwa ndi timu ina ya mdziko la Egypt yomwe akuti El -Entag El-Harby kuti akachita mayeso osewelera mu timuyo.\r\nMlembi wamkulu wa timu ya Manoma a MIke Butao atsimikizira nyuzipepala ya Daily Times kuti izi ndi zoona ndipo kalatayo ailandira sabata yomwe ino ndipo aiyankha posachedwapa. A Butao ati alibe lingaliro loletsa Wadabwa kukayesa mwai ku Egypt.\r\nM\'buyomu Wadabwa adaseweraponso ku matimu a Escom United, Silver Strikers mdzikomuno komanso matimu a Thanda Royal Zulu, Golden Arrows ndi Blackburn Rovers  mdziko la South Africa.\r\nWadabwa wati ulendo ulipo chomwe akudikira ndi ziphaso zofunikira kuti akalowe mdziko la Egypt ndipo wati pakadalipano sanauzidwe kuti mayeso omwe akupitira akakhala a nthawi yayitali motani.','sports_news','2018-06-27','2018-06-27 09:58:09'),(93,'Bello wakana ndudu za Nyasa','27/06/18\r\nTimu ya Nyasa Big Bullets yalephera kugula Amos Bello, katswiri osewera kutsogolo wa mdziko la Nigeria yemwe pakadalipano akukhala mdziko mommuno atalephera kumvana chimodzi. Bello adali osewera wa timu ya Might Beforward Wanderers. Malinga ndi zomwe nyuzipepala zalemba a Bello anapatsidwa mwai oti alandire ndalama zowagulira zokwana 3 million kwacha zomwe awapatse kwa miyezi itatu komanso kuti azilandira ndalama zokwana 330, 000 kwacha mwezi ulionse mwa zina.\r\nYemwe amathandiza Bello pa migwirizano yotere Duncan Kamwendo watsimikiza kuti Bello wakana kusayina mgwirizanowo ati kamba koti Nyasa Big Bullets sinali yokonzeka kumupatsa ndalama yomugulirayo kwa nthawi imodzi.\r\nJoseph Kamwendo yemwe ndi mzake wa Bello wati Amos Bello sanafune kuti ndalama yake amupatse modula-dula ngakhake anayesa kumuthandiza maganizo kuti asayine mgwirizanowo.\r\nEna mwa osewera kutsogolo kwa timu ya Big Bullets omwe akuchita bwino ndi monga Chiukepo Msowoya, Patrick Phiri,Bright \"Bweke\" Munthali komanso Mussa Manyenje.','sports_news','2018-06-27','2018-06-27 10:10:15'),(94,'Gerald Phiri Wanunkhira ku Mamelodi','Malipoti amveka mdziko la Southa Africa kuti osewera pakati wa dziko lino yemwe ali ku South Africa Gerald Phiri akhoza kupita ku timu ya Mamelodi Sundowns kuchoka ku Bidvest Wits komwe ali pakadlipano.\r\nMalipoti ati matimu awiriwa akufuna asinthane osewera kamba koti Bidvest Wits ikufuna osewera kutsogolo kwa timu ya Mamelodi Cuthbert Malajira,\r\nMamelodi Sundows ndiyo yalembera timu ya Wits koma pakadalipano mbali ziwirizi sizinamvane kalikonse.\r\nPoyankhula ndi nyuzipepala ya Nation yomwe yasindikiza nkhaniyi, Geral Phiri anati sakudziwapo kalikonse ndipo anauza mtolankhani wa nyuzipepalayi kuti ayankhulane ndi omuthandizira wake.','sports_news','2018-06-27','2018-06-27 10:17:05'),(95,'Mphunzitsi wa FLAMES alamulidwa asasiye osewera omwe akuchita bwino','27/06-/8\r\nMphunzitsi wa timu ya mpira wa miyendo ya dziko lino amupempha kuti asasiye osewera omwe akuchita bwino mdzikomuno pa masewero omwe timu ya dziko lino ikukakumana ndi timu ya dziko la Morocco m\'masewero olimbirana chikho cha maiko a mu Africa,\r\nWachiwiri kwa mtsgoleri wa bungwe FAM a James Mwenda ndiwo anatsogolera msonkhano omwe bungweli komanso aphunzitsi a timuyi amaunika momwe masewero a m\'buyomu kuphatikizapo kutuluka mu mpikisano wa maiko a kumwera kwa Africa cha COSAF zinayendera. Mphunzitsi wa timu ya FLAMES Ronny van Geneudgen kapena kungoti RVG anapereka lipoti lake pa momwe zinthu zakhala zikuyendera m\'mbuyomu.\r\nAnthu ambiri pakadalipao sakukondwa ndi momwe timuyi ikuchitira pakadalipano.','sports_news','2018-06-27','2018-06-27 10:24:21'),(96,'Jose wavomerezedwa kukhala mkulu wa apolisi','28/06/18\r\nA Rodney Jose omwe amagwirizira udindo wa wamkulu wa apolisi mdzikomuno tsopano awavomereza pa udindowu aphungu ochuluka  a kunyumba ya malamulo atavomereza nawo.\r\nMtsogoleri wa dziko lino olemekezeka a Peter Mutharika ndiwo adasankha udindo a Jose pa mpando wa ogwirizira udindo wa mkulu wa apolisi ndipo monga mwa lamulo iwowa amayenera kuvomelezedwa ndi nyumba ya malamulo.\r\nKusankhidwa kwa a Jose kukhala mkulu wa apolisi mdzikomuno kunadzetsa maganizo osiyana siyana pakati pa anthu kamba koti ena amati mkulu wa apolisiyu amakhudzidwa ndi nkhani ya kuphedwa kwa ophunzira wina yemwe anali pa sukulu ya ukachenjede ya Malawi Polytechnic Robert Chasowa ati kamba koti lipoti lina la komiti yomwe inkafufuza za imfayi inatchulapo dzina lawo zinthu zomwe umboni wake pakadalipano palibe.\r\nKunyumba ya malamuloko, membala wa chipani cha MCP  a Maxwell Thyolera anabwerezanso zomwezo ndipo anati mpofunika dzina la a Jose litaunikidwa bwino. Nao a Kamplepo Kalua omwe amayankhula m\'malo mwa chipani cha Peoples mnyumbayi anati pali zinthu zina zofunika kuziunika bwino a Jose asanavomerezedwe pa udindowu.\r\nKomabe nthawi inakwana ndithu pomwe aphunguwa anaponya voti yawo ya chinsinsi pomwe aphungu 96 anagwirizana nazo pomwe 55 anakana pomwe awiri sanavote.\r\nNduna ya zamdziko mai Cecilia Chazama inauza nyumbayi kuti  a Jose ali chilichonse chowayenereza kukhala pa udindowu kamba ka luntha komanso kudzipereka kwawo.\r\nIwo anati pa nkhani zina zomwe zimakambidwa kuti amakhudzidwa ndi kuphedwa ka Robert Chasowa iwo anati nthambi zina za boma zofufuza ndizo zimayenera kuzama kupeza tsinde la nkhani yonse.\r\nA Jose alowa m\'malo mwa a Lexten Kachama omwe nthawi yawo yogwira nchito m\'boma yawathera kamba ka zaka zawo.','local_news','2018-06-28','2018-06-28 12:21:43'),(97,'Apolisi apepesa olemba nkhani','28/06/18\r\nApolisi mdzikomuno apepesa olemba nkhani mdzikomuno potsatira zomwe apolisi ena anachita pomenya olembenkani awiri ogwira ntchito ku Zodiak Broadcasting Station  Musase Cheyo ndi Towera Kumwenda sabata yatha pomwe amajambula zinthunzi za apolisiwa akuthamangitsa ma venda mu msewu.\r\nKumenyedwa kwa olemba nkhaniwa kunadzetsa mkwiyo komanso chidzudzulo kuchokera ku mabungwe a mdziko muno komanso maiko akunja, kuphatikizaponso zipani za ndale zosiyana siyana ponena kuti izi ndizosemphana ndi ufulu wa kayankhulidwe omwe ulipo pakati pa olemba nkhani.\r\nOfalitsa nkhani za apolisi mdzikomuno a James Kadadzera ati m\'kufufuza kwawo apezadi kuti apolisi ena anamenya olemba nkhaniwa zomwe ndizosemphana ndi malamulo a ntchito yawo ndipo alonjeza kuti malamulo atsatiridwa popereka chilango choyenelera.\r\nA Kadadzera ati chomwe akufuna ndi kulimbikitsa ubale wabwino omwe ulipo pakati pa olemba nkhani ndi apolisi monga momwe zakhala zikukhalira m\'mbuyomu.\r\nWachiwiri kwa wapampando wa bungwe la olemba nkhani la Misa Malawi a Clifton Kawanga ati alandira chipepesochi ngakhale chomwe akufunitsitsa ndi chilango kwa apolisi omwe anachita izi.\r\nIwo ati ndizokhumudwitsa kuti apolisi ndiwo akutsogolera mchitidwe ngati umenewu maka pa nthawi ino pomwe dziko la Malawi likuyandikira nyengo yoponya voti chaka cha mawa.\r\n','local_news','2018-06-28','2018-06-28 13:08:21'),(98,'Faith Mussa atulutsa nyimbo ziwiri','28/06/18 \r\nPomwe akukonzekera kukhazikitsa chimbale chake cha Mdidi pa 4 August mu mzinda wa Lilongwe, Faith Mussa wati ayamba  watulutsa kaye nyimbo ziwiri zomwe zili pa chimbalechi. Nyimbo ziwirizi wati azitulutsa pa 7 July.\r\nNyimbozi ndi Selofoni komanso ina ya mchingerezi yomwe akuti He fights for me kapena kuti amandimenyera nkhondo yomwe waimba ndi Mtali shaka Banda.\r\nMussa wati zokonzekera zonse zikuyenda bwino ndipo anthu ayembekeze zabwino ngati nyimbo ya Mdidi yomwe anthu akhala akumvera kwa kanthawi.\r\nEna omwe adzathandizire oyimbayu pa tsikuli  ndi monga Lusubilo Band ya ku Karonga komanso Mussa Family komwe kunayambila luso lake la maimbidwe.\r\n\r\n','local_news','2018-06-28','2018-06-28 13:06:44'),(99,'Ma Blacks ayenda pa ndege kukakhazikitsa chimbale','28/06/18\r\nGulu loyimba chamba cha Reggae Mdzikomuno la Black Missionaries lomwe anthu amangoti ma Blacks lowerula likudzali liyenda pa ndege kuchokera ku chileka kupita ku Lilongwe komwe lamulungu lake akukhazikitsa chimbale chatsopano cha Kuyimba 11 ku bwalo losewera masewero a Golf mu mzinda wa Lilongwe.\r\nMwambo okhazikitsa chimbalechi uyambira ku Robins Park mu mzinda wa Blantyre lachisanu lino ndipo akutsogolera mwambowu ndi a kampani ya Team Entertainers yomwe pano akuyendetsa ndi mwana wa Jain Banda , Tonderai.\r\nBanda wati kampani yawo yalipira ulendo wa pa ndege ndicholinga choti akakhale ndi nthawi yokwanira yokonzekera lamulungu lisanafike.\r\nOtsogolera mau mu Bandiyi Anjiru Fumulani wati ndi okonzeka kukhazikitsa chimbalechi ndipo wati anthu achikonda kamba koti muli uthenga wabwino okamba za chikondi komanso umodzi.\r\nKu Mzuzu chimbalechi achikhazikitsa pa 28 mwezi wa mawa.\r\nPakadalipano guluri latulutsa nyimbo zoonera pa kanema ziwiri zomwe ndi Special Lover komanso pa Gombe La Nyanja. Anyamatawa anatulutsanso nyimbo zina monga Zofuna Mtima Wanga, Umboni komanso Mbusa zomwe anthu akumvera.\r\nNyimbo za pa chimbale chatsopanochi zakhala zikunenedwa kuti sizinathyakuke bwino pomwe ena akuti zilibwino.\r\n','local_news','2018-06-28','2018-06-28 13:05:21'),(100,'Mbulu wabwerera ku Mozambique','28/06/18\r\nRichard Mbulu wabwereranso ku timu yake mdziko la Mozambique kuchoka ku timu yomwe amasewera ku Portugal potsatira kutha kwa mgwirizano wa chaka chimodzi omwe unalipo.\r\nZateremu ndiyekuti dziko la Malawi lilibe osewera aliyense yemwe angalozedwe ku maiko azungu zomwe ena ati zimachititsa kuti timu ya dziko lino isamachite bwino.\r\nPakadalipano Mbulu sanayankhulepo kalikonse kofotokozera chifukwa chomwe sapitilanso ku Portugal ngakhale kuti timu yake yalemba pa tsamba lake la makina a intaneti kuti Mbulu wayambanso kusewera ndi timu yawo.','sports_news','2018-06-28','2018-06-28 13:18:01'),(101,'Mkulu wa Apolisi wati sanaphe Chasowa','29/06/18\r\nMkulu wa apolisi mdzikomuno yemwe wongovomerezedwa kumene wakana kuti sakudziwapo kanthu pa za imfa ya Robert Chasowa yemwe anali ophunzira wa pa sukulu ya ukachenjede ya Malawi Polytecyhnic.\r\nRobert Chasowa anapezeka atafa zaka zingapo zapitazo ndipo anthu omenyera ufulu akhala akupempha boma kuti lisasankhe a Jose kukhala mkulu wa apolisi kamba koti lipoti lina limati akukhudzidwa ndi imfayi.\r\nKoma poyankhula lachinayi ku likulu la apolisi ku Lilongwe komwe kunali mwambo otsanzikana ndi mkulu wakale wa apolisi bambo Lextern Kachama a Jose anati mtima wawo umawapweteka akamamva anthu akuyankhula za kukhudzidwa kwawo ndi imfa ya a Chasowa.\r\n\"Zimandiwawa, ine ndili ndi mboni ziwiri , mboni yoyamba ndi Mulungu ndipo yachiwiri ndi Mzimu wa Robert Chasowa mwini wake ndipo mzimu wake uwuse mu mtendere\" anatero a Jose.\r\nIwo anaonjezera kuti aliyense amene ali ndi umboni pa nkhaniyi abwere poyera ndikuulula za kukhudzidwa kwao kulekana ndikumayankhula zinthu zopanda umboni.\r\nPa zakagwiridwe ntchito ka apolisi mdzikomuno a Jose anati anthu ataya chikhulupiliro mwa apolisi ndipo ayesetsa kuchita chilichonse kuti anthu ayambenso kukhulupilira ntchito zawo.\r\nKumbali yawo a Kachama anati mu nthawi yawo anayesetsa kukhwimitsa chitetezo poonetsetsa kuti apolisi akupezeka m\'malo oyenelera komanso kuchepetsa umbanda ndi umbava.\r\nNduna ya za m\'dziko a Cecelia Chazama anayamikira kudzipereka kwa a Kachama pomwe anali mkulu wa apolisi. \r\nA Kachama anayamba ntchito yawo mchaka cha 1979 ndipo anasankhidwa kukhala mkulu wa apolisi mdzikomuno pa mwezi wa February mchaka cha 2015.\r\nA Rodney Jose anayamba ntchito ku polisi mcha cha 1983.\r\n\r\n','local_news','2018-06-29','2018-06-29 14:36:54'),(102,'Aphungu akana kuika malire a zaka za mtsogoleri wa dziko','29/06/18\r\nAphungu ku nyumba ya malamulo akana kuika malire pa kuchuluka kwa zaka za munthu yemwe angakhale mtsogoleri wa dziko.\r\nPhungu wina wa ku Nsanje a Chidanti Malunga anapempha aphungu a nzawo mnyumbayi kuti aike malire za munthu yemwe angakhale mtsogoleri wa dziko ponena kuti munthu akakula kwambiri sayenera kukhala ndi udindo wonga wa mtsogoleri wa dziko kamba koti umafuna zambiri,\r\nKoma zipani za MCP komanso DPP zati nkhani yomwe a malunga anayambitsa m\'nyumba ya malamuloyi inali yachibwana kamba koti palibe kugwirizana kulikonse pakati pa nzeru ndi kukula.\r\nPhungu wina wa ku Lilongwe a Peter Dimba anati utsogoleri ndi mphatso ya mulungu ndipo anati a Malunga komanso a Bon Kalindo omwe anavomerezana ndi nkaniyi mnyumbayi ali mbali ya a Saulos Chilima omwe anayambitsa gulu lawo la chipani ndipo akhulupilira kuti akutumidwa,\r\nMalamulo a dziko lino samayi zaka zomwe munthu sakuyenereza kupitiliza kukhala mtsogoleri wa dziko ngakhale pali gawo lomwe limanena kuti okhawo omwe anakwanitsa zaka 35 kupita kutsogolo ndiwo angapikisane nawo pa mpando wa utsogoleri.\r\nKuyankhula komwe anayankhula a Dimba kunadzetsa chikondwelero kwa aphungu ochuluka mnyumbayi.\r\n\r\n\r\n','local_news','2018-06-29','2018-06-29 14:50:17'),(103,'Aphungu ati uphunzitsi wa FLAMES RVG achoke','29/06/18\r\nAphungu a kunyumba ya Malamulo anapanikiza nduna ya zamasewero a Francis Kasaira kuti afotokoze zifukwa zomwe bungwe la FAM silikuchitsera ntchito a Ronny Vangeudgen - RVG ngakhale kuti sakuchita bwino pa mipikisano yosiyanasiyana.\r\nPhungu wina ku mchinji  a Alex Chitete anati bungwe la FAM likuyenera kufotokoza bwino zifukwa zomwe zikusungirabe a RVG ndipo anati amalawi ambiri amakhalanso akudabwa ndi ndondomeko yomwe inatsatidwa polemba mphunzitsiyu.\r\nM\'mau ake ndunayi inati mphunzitsiyu wayetsetsa kuchita bwino mu nthawi yake ndipo pali kusintha. A Kasaira anati RVG anasainira mgwirizano wa zaka ziwiri omwe wangotha chaka ndipo wakhala akuyesera osewera osiyana siyana.\r\nNdunayi inatsimikizira a Malawi kuti adekhe ndipo anati kuchotsa ntchito RVG kungachititse kuti boma lilipire ndala zankhaninkhani.','sports_news','2018-06-29','2018-06-29 14:59:19'),(104,'Bullets yadya chipolopolo -   BE 1 : 0 NBB','2nd July, 2018\r\nMpikisano olimbirana chikho cha Airtel Top 8 sunathe bwino kumbali ya Nyasa Big Bullets kamba ka mzinga omwe asilikali a Blue Eagles anaomba mu nthawi yoonjezera kudzera ku penate.\r\nAnyama a Nyasa Big Bullets anayesetsa kuti alavule chipolopolochi koma sizinatheke kamba koti nthawi inali itatha kale ndipo oyimbira masewerowo anayimba pinto yomaliza kuti wadya chipolopolo wafa.\r\nPosakhalitsa otsatira a Nyasa Big Bullets analowa m\'bwalo la zamasewero momwe ndeu pakati iwo ndi apolisi omwe amaleletsa oyimbira mpira inabuka. Ochemerera timuyi anakwiya kuti oyimbirayu anapereka penate mu nthawi yowonjezera angakhale kuti zifukwa zonse zinali zokwanira kuti inali penate.\r\nMwai wa nzako ndi tsoka la wina - ichi nchifukwa chake ngakhake ochomerera a Bullets amatuluka magazi uku nkuti anzawo a Blue Eagles akuguba pelete kukondwelera kuti apambana chikho komanso agwetsa timu yayikulu. Big Bullets komanso Blue Eagles anakumana komaliza mu ndime yotsiriza ya masewero a chikho mchaka cha 1995 pomwe ankalimbirana chikho cha Chibuku ndipo Bullets inagonjetsedwanso ndi zigoli ziwiri kwa du.\r\nGilbert Chirwa ndiye anagwetsedwa kuti oyimbira mpira Misheck Juwa apereke penate kwa Blue Eagles.\r\nPomwe 90 Minutes imakwana anthu ambiri anali ndi chiyembekezo kuti masewerowa afika ku ma penate koma sizinatero.\r\nOdziwa zamsewero akuti Nyasa Big Bullets yomwe sinasewere mpira monga nthawi zonse nkutheka kuti sinachite bwino kamba koti anadzikhulupilira kwambiri mwa iwo okha pomwe Blue Eagles inakonzeka kupanga mbiri ndipo anaonetsa njala yofuna kugoletsa.','sports_news','2018-07-02','2018-07-02 12:10:39'),(105,'Msika wa fodya ku Limbe autseka mwezi uno','2nd July, 2018\r\nAkulu akulu a bungwe logulitsa fodya la Auction Holdings Limited AHL ati malonda a fodya ku msika waukulu wa Limbe atsekedwa kumapeto a mwezi uno.\r\nMkulu oyang\'anira  msika wa Limbe a Moses Yoramu auza nyuzipepala ya Daily Times kuti pakadalipano agulitsa kale fodya ochuluka kuposa  yemwe amayembekezera. Pakutha pa sabata yatha msikawu unali utagultsa makilogalamu a fodya oposa 15 million ndipo nthawi zambiri msikawu umakhala oyambilira kutsekedwa.\r\n\r\nPali chiyembekezo pakati pa alimi kuti malonda a Fodyayu apitilira kuchita bwino.\r\nBungwe loona za malonda a fodya mdzikomuno al Tobacco Control Commission TCC lidati alimi mdzikomuno akuyembekezeka kugulitsa fodya osachepera ma kilogalamu 149 million kulekana ndi 171 millio omwe ogula akufuna. Koma malinga ndi momwe zinthu zikuyendera pa msika pali chiyembekezo choti fodya yemwe agulitsidwe akahala wambiri kuposa chiyerekezo chomwe chinalipo.','local_news','2018-07-02','2018-07-02 09:52:39'),(106,'Mutharika wasankhidwanso kutsogolera DPP, Mussa, Nankhumwa,apambananso.','4th July, 2018\r\nMsonkhano waukulu wa chipani cholamula cha Democratic Progressive DPP wasankhanso Professor Peter Mutharika kukhala mtsogoleri wa chipanichi komanso yemwe adzaimire chipani cha DPP pa chisankho cha chaka cha mawa. Msonkhanowu omwe umachitikira ku holo ya COMESA mu mzinda wa Blantyre wasankhanso a Uladi Musa kukhala wachiwiri kwa a Mutharika mchigawo chapakati pomwe a Kondwani Nankhumwa ndiwo asankhidwa kukhala wachiwiri  kwa a Mutharika m\'chigawo cha kumwera. A Goodall Gondwe ndiwo apambana pa udindo wa wachiwiri kwa a Mutharika mchigawo cha kumpoto.\r\nA Mutharika analibe opikisana naye pomwe a Kondwani Nankhumwa agonjetsa a Joseph Mwanamvekha komanso a Hennry Musa.  A Nkankhumwa anapeza mavoti 774 , 401 a Hennry Mussa pomwe a Mwanamvekha anapeza mavoti 407.\r\nMchigawo cha pakati a Uladi Mussa anapeza mavoti 964 kugwetsa a Dean Josaya Banda omwe anapeza mavoti 298, a Zelia Chakale omwe anapeza ma voti 149, Dr Hetherwick Ntaba omwe anapeza ma voti 94 Komanso a Samuel Tembenu omwe anapeza ma voti 91.\r\nAnthu anali odabwa kuti a George Chaponda omwe analembetsa kuti akapikisana nawo pa mpando wa wachiwiri kwa mtsgoleri wa chipanichi mchigawo cha kumwera analengeza ku msonkhanowo kuti sapikisana nawo. Ena mwa anthu omwe asankhidwa popanda opikisana nawo ndi a Jappie Mhango kukhala msungichuma wa chipanichi, a Evason Chimulirenji kukhala mkulu wa zokopa anthu komanso a Charles Mhango ngati mkulu wa zamalamulo ku chipani cha DPP.\r\nZadziwikanso kuti a Grezelder Jeffrey atenganso udindo wa mlembi wamkulu wa chipanichi pomwe amapikisana ndi a Clement Mwale komanso a Wictor Songazaudzu Sajeni.\r\nA Nicholus Dausi tsopano ndi mneneri wa chipani cha DPP ndipo wachiwiri wawo ndi a Chris Thaulo. A Dausi agonjetsa a Francis Kasaira, Ken Msonda komanso mayi Esther Mcheka Chilenje omwe ndi wachiwiri oyamba kwa sipikala ku nyumba ya malamulo.\r\nPakadalipano a Mutharika ayamika anthu omwe anafika ku msonkhanowu kamba kochita msankho mwa bata ndi mtendere ndipo alonjeza kuti anthu omwe sanachite bwino ku mpikisanowu awapatsa zochita zina. A Mutharika apemphanso otsatira chipanichi kuti akhale ogwirizana kuti adzapambane pa chisankho cha chaka cha mawa.\r\nZipani za  MCP komanso AFORD zinapanga kale msonkhano wake wa ukulu ndipo nacho chipani cha UDF chinalengeza kuti chichititsa msonkhano wake mwezi wa mawa.\r\n\r\n\r\n','local_news','2018-07-04','2018-07-04 07:38:17'),(107,'DPP yasintha ena mwa malamulo oyendetsera chipani - Onyoza mtsogoleri azichotsedwa','4th July, 2018\r\nKupatula zisankho zomwe zinali ku msonkhano waukulu wa chipani cha DPP, akuluakulu a chipanichi asinthanso ena mwa malamulo oyendetsera chipanichi. Malinga ndi wapampando wa komiti yomwe imaunikanso malamulowa a Bright Msaka, mwa zina malamulo atsopano akupereka ndondomeko yochotsera mchipani anthu omwe akuchita zinthu zonyoza utsogoleri wa chipanichi kapenanso kunyoza chipanichi ndi atsogoleri ake.\r\nChinanso cha chilendo m\'malamulowa ndichakuti atsogoleri a chipanichi mzigawo zonse zinayi za dziko lino apatsidwa mphamvu yokhazikitsa ma komiti apadera omwe zipereka mwambo kwa omwe alakwira malamulo a chipanichi.\r\nChipanichi chaikanso ndondomeko zoonetsetsa kuti ma udindo onse azikhala ndi nthumwi zochokera mzogawo zonse za dziko lino kuti pasapezeka chigawo china chosalidwa mchipanichi. Ngakhale sanafotokoze bwino chipanichi chati chaikanso ndondomeko zothananirana ndi katangale ati pofuna kuonetsa chitsanzo chabwino. M\'malamulowa aikamonso ndondomeko yomwe izithandiza kuti amayi azisankhidwa m\'maudindo osiyana siyana ngati gawo limodzi lolimbikitsira amayi kutengapo gawo pa ndale.\r\nMalamulo omwe aunikidwa panowa anaunikidwanso mchaka cha 2008.\r\nKupatula a msaka ena omwe anali nawo mu komiti yowunika malamulowa ndi a Samuel Tembenu omwenso ndi nduna ya zamalamulo komanso a Charles Mhango omwe ndi mlangizi wa boma pa nkhani za malamulo. A Francis Mphepo owenso ndi mlangizi wina wa mtsogoleri wa dziko lino anali nawonso mu komitiyi.\r\nKomabe akulu akuluwa ati malamulowa sangakhudze a Chilima omwe analengeza kuti atsatira ndondomeko zoyenera zotulukira mchipanichi.','local_news','2018-07-04','2018-07-04 08:53:17'),(108,'Akatswiri pa ndale ati Chakwera akunena zosatheka','4th July, 2018\r\nAkatswiri pa ndale a Ernest Thindwa komanso a Professor Wiseman Chijere Chirwa ati zomwe wanena mtsogoleri wa chipani cha MCP yemwenso ndi mtsogoleri wa zipani zotsutsa ku nyumba ya malamulo Dr Lazarous Chakwera kuti a Mutharika atule pansi udindo wawo ndikuitanitsa zisankho mwamsanga ndisosatheka. A Chakwera anachititsa msonkhano wa olemba nkhani komwe anati potsatira kuululika kwa chikalata china cha zofufuza-fufuza chomwe ndi cha bungwe lothana ndi katangale ndi ziphuphu la ACB ndipo chikufotokoza kuti pali kuthekera kuti chipani cha DPP  chinapindula nawo ndi ndalama zokwana 145 million zomwe kampani ina yoperekera zakudya za apolisi inapereka mokaikitsa, a Mutharika atule pansi udindo wawo.\r\nPali chikaiko kuti kampaniyi imapereka ndalamazi ku chipani cha DPP ngati  katangale potsatira bizinesi ya ndalama za nkhani nkhani yomwe anaipeza ku boma.\r\nA Thindwa ati zomwe a Chakwera akunena ndizosemphana ndi malamulo a dziko lino ati kamba koti ngati mtsogoleri wasiya kulamulira, wachiwiri wake amatenga udindo ndipo ngakhale izi zili chomwechi iwo anti ndi momwe ndale za mdziko lino zimakhalira, ndizosatheka a Mutharika kutula pansi udindo wawo.\r\nNawo a Chijere Chirwa ati malamulo a dziko lino alibe gawo lofotokoza kuthekera kwa mtsogoleri kuitanitsa chisankho zaka zisanu zisanathe.\r\nNaye mneneri wa mtsogoleri wa dziko lino bambo Mgeme Kalirani wauza nyumba zoulutsa mawu zosiyana siyana kuti zikukambidwazi ndi nkhamba kamwa chabe ndikuti nkhaniyi ikukhotetsedwa mwadala ndicholinga chofuna kuzambaitsa chilungambo kuti ziwakomere. A Kalirani ati pali umboni onse wakuti a Mutharika sanapindule ndi ndalama zokwana 145 million zomwe zinaikidwa ku banki mdzina la chipani cha DPP.\r\nBungwe la ACB kudzera kwa mkulu wake a Ryneck Matemba linati ndilokhumudwa kuti chikalatachi chapita kugulu koma anati iwo apitilira ndi ntchito yofufuza ndipo akukhulupilira kuti sizisokoneza kalikonse.\r\nMabungwe omwe si aboma nawo anapereka sabata ziwiri kwa a Mutharika kuti atule pansi udindo wawo zinthu zomwe a Kalirani anauza olemba nkhani kuti ndizopanda mutu wake.\r\n','local_news','2018-07-04','2018-07-04 08:53:25'),(109,'Ziwawa zakhumudwitsa Airtel','4th July, 2018\r\nKampani ya Airtel yomwe imachititsa mpikisano wa Aitrel Top 8 yati  ndiyokhumudwa ndi ziwawa zomwe otsatira timu ya Nyasa Big Bullets anachita pakutha ma masewero a mu ndime yomaliza ya chikhochi lamulungu lapitali pa bwalo la zamasewero la Bingu mu mzinda wa Lilongwe. Ochemererewa pokwiya ndi penate yomwe Misheck Juwa anapereka ku Blue Eagles mu mphindi yomaliza ya nthawi yoonjezera anathamangira m\'bwaloli kukamenya oimbira mpirayu ndipo zinatengera apolisi kuthanmangira pa malopo pomwe kumenyananso kwina pakati pa apolisi ndi ochemelera timuyi kunayambika. Mkulu wa kampani ya Airtel Malawi a Charles Kamoto anati akupereka chenjezo lamphamvu kwa ochita masewero a mpira wa miyendo mdzikomuno kamba koti anali okhumudwa ndi zomwe zinachitika pa tsikuli.\r\nA Kamoto anati chisangalalo chonse chinasokonekera pa tsikuli ndipio apempha bungwe la FAM kuti lichite chotheka chilichonse kuti lifufuze momwe zinthu zinayendera.\r\nKomabe mkuluyu anati kupatula ziwawa masewerowa anali osangalatsa kamba koti mbali zonse zimafunitsitsa zitapambana.\r\nMkulu wa FAM poyankhulanso ndi olemba nkhani atatha masewerowa anati chiganizo cha oimbira chinali chovuta ku mbali ya Nyasa Bullets  koma ochemelera samayenera kuyambitsa ziwawa kamba koti pali njira zambiri zodandaulira zinthu zikalakwika.\r\nNyamilandu wati bungwe lawo lifufuza za nkhaniyi.\r\nPakadalipano Nyasa Big Bullets yadzudzula ochemelera omwe anayambitsa zipolowe, apolisi omwe amamenya anthu komanso yemwe anaimbira masewerowo ponena kuti sanagwire ntchito yabwino.\r\nPakadalipano mkulu wa apolisi a Rodney Jose apereka 1 million kwacha ku timu ya Blue Eagles pofuna kuwalimbikitsa pa kupambana kwawo komanso kutenga chikho cha Aitrtel Top 8 kwa nthawi yoyamba.','sports_news','2018-07-04','2018-07-04 08:53:36'),(110,'Sitalaka ya aphunzitsi yakanika','09/07/18\r\nBungwe la a phunzitsi mdzikomuno lalengeza kuti aphunzitsi sayamba kunyanyala ntchito monga mwachikonzero chawo boma litamva komanso kuyamba chitapo kanthu pa madandaulo awo. Aphunzitsiwa kudzera ku bungwe lawo la Teachers Union of Malawi TUM adati ayamba kunyanyala ntchito lero kamba koti boma silikuwapatsa ndalama zokwana 1.7 billion zomwe amayenera kulandira pakanthawi kuyambira chaka cha 2010. Mlembi wa mkulu wa bungwe la TUM a Charles Kumchenga ati  sitalaka idzachitika ngati zomwe lalonjeza boma silikwaniritsa\r\nMkulu ku unduna wa zachuma a Ben Botolo  walemba chikalata chomwe chikuti boma latumiza ndalama za phunzitsi ku banki ndipo ayembekeze kulandira posachedwapa.','local_news','2018-07-09','2018-07-09 14:45:09'),(111,'Amayi oyembekezera akuthawa kuchilira ku chipatala','09/07/18\r\nNyuzi pepala ya Nation yasindikiza nkhani yomwe ikuti amayi ambiri oyembekezera akumathawa kuchilira mzipatala ndikusankha kukachilira kwa a zamba kamba ka nkhanza zomwe amakuna nazo kwa  a Namwino mzipatala zosiyana siyana.\r\nMabungwe a White Ribbon Alliance (WRA) komanso Association of Malawian Midwives (Amani) anachititsa msonkhano wawo ku Nathenje m\'bom ala LIlongwe komwe akugwira ntchito yolimbikitsa uchembere wabwino.\r\nMaria Wickford anauza nyuzipepalayi kuti zomwe anakumana nazo ku chipatala china chaching\'ono ku dera kwawo zidachititsa kuti atengere m\'bale wakeyo kwa a zamba.\r\nIye akuti anaonelerapo mawi wina akuchilira panja pomwe pamadutsa anthu ambiri kuphatikizapo a bambo kamba koti ogwira ntchito pa chipatalapo samalabadira za umoyo wake. \r\nKwa azamba komwe anapita anakalipira ndalama zokwana MK 10,000 kuti athandizidwe. Felista Kanthuti yemwe akuyendetsa nawo ntchitoyi wati nkhani zotere amakumana nazo kawiri kawiri. \r\nIwo ati akukambiran andi boma pa momwe angathetsera mchitidwewu.\r\nPakadalipano nchitoyi ikugwirika m\'mabom aa Kasungu ndi Lilongwe','local_news','2018-07-09','2018-07-09 14:55:05'),(112,'Bungwe la MEC lakana kuwonjezera masiku a kalembera','10/07/18\r\n\r\nBungwe loona za kalembera wa chisankho mdzikomuno lakana kuwonjezera nthawi yomwe gawo loyamba la kalembera wa chisankho cha chaka cha mawa limayenera kutha. Bungweli lakana pempholi potsatira zomwe chipani chotsutsa cha Malawi Congress chinalembera bungweli kuti lionjezere masiku a kalemberayu kapena liyambe layimitsa ntchito ya kalembera yomwe bungweli likuchita ponena kuti anthu ambiri sanadziwitsidwe mokwanira za kalemberayu. Kalemberayu anayambika m\'maboma a Kasungu, Dedza komanso Salima lomwe ndi gawo loyamba.\r\nMKulu wa bungwe la MEC mayi Jane Ansah atsimikiza kuti gawo loyamba latha dzulo pa 8 July ndipo anavomereza kuti anthu ochepa ndiwo alembetsa. Iwo akhala akunena kuti anthu ambiri sanapite kukalembetsa kamba koti ndi okhumudwa ndi zomwe adindo omwe anawasankha mchaka cha 2014 akugwilira ntchito zawo.\r\nMayi Ansah atinso kafukufuku wawo wasonyezanso kuti anthu ena sakuonetsa kukhutira ndi momwe bungwe la zachisankho limagwilira ntchito zake ndipo ati ichi nchifukwa chake ataunikira bwino anaona kuti palibe chomwe chingasinthe ngati ataonjezera masiku a kalembera kamba koti vuto si kudziwa kapena kusadziwa za kalemberayu.\r\nKomabe poyankhula ndi nyuzipepala ya Daily Times m\'neneri wa chipani cha MCP a Maurice Munthali anati bungwe la MEC linayenera kumvera madandaulo a chipani cha MCP kamba koti ndi chipani chomwe ndi gawo lofunikira kwambiri pa zisankho zomwe zilinkudza.\r\n','local_news','2018-07-10','2018-07-10 15:18:53'),(113,'M\'nyamata wa chi Albino wasowa ku Phalombe','10/07/18\r\nApolisi ku Phalombe ali pa ntchito yofufuza mnyamata wina wa chi Albino Joseph Kachingwe yemwe akuti sakuoneka.\r\nMneneri wa apolisi m\'bomali Innocent Moses wati mnyamatayu anachoka kwawo pa 6 July ndi anzake awiri koma sanabwerere kufikira pomwe mayi ake amakatula nkhaniyi ku polisi.\r\nMayi a mnyamatayu anauza apolisi kuti bambo ake omupeza ndiwo anali ndi mwanayu pa nathwi yomwe amachoka panyumba koma atawafunsa za komwe kwalowera mwanayo iwo anati sakudziwapo kanthu.\r\nAnzakewo atafunsidwa za komwe kuli nzawo anati mzawoyo anawafotokozera kuti abwelera kunyumbako ndi bambo ake omupeza.Pakadalipano apolisi ati palibe wamangidwa molumikizana ndi nkhaniyi koma bambo wake omupeza m\'nyamatayu anafunsidwa mafunso ku polisi.\r\nMkulu wa bungwe la anthu a chi Albino mdzikomuno a Ovestone Kondowe wati nkhaniyi ikupitilira kutsindika pa nkhawa zawo kuti anthu a chi Albino akupitilira kukhala mosowa mtendere m\'dzikomuno.\r\n ','local_news','2018-07-10','2018-07-10 15:20:04'),(114,'Albino yemwe anasowa ku Phalombe wapezeka ataphedwa','11/07/18\r\nThupi la mnyamata wa zaka 12 Joseph Kachingwe yemwe anali wa chi Albino alipeza ku malo ena potsatira kufufuza kwa apolisi.\r\nApolisi anatsekera mchitokosi anthu angapo mogwirizana ndi kusowa kwa mnyamatayu pa 6 July.\r\nMneneri wa apolisi ku Phalombe komwe kwachitika kwa nkhaniyi sanayankhulepo zambiri za nkhaniyi kupatula kutsimikiza kuti zofufuza zili mkati.\r\nMalinga nndi nyuzi pepala ya Daily Times apolisi akhwimitsa chitetezo ku dera lomwe kwachitika izi pofuna kuteteza anthu omwe amangidwawo.\r\nApolisi sanaulule anthu omwe amangidwa molumikizana ndi nkhaniyi.\r\nBungwe lina lomenyera ufulu wa anthu pa dziko lonse la Amnesty International linatulutsa kafukufuku yemwe akuti anthu a mtunduwu akupitilira kuphedwa pa zifukwa za zikhulupiliro zomwe zilibe umboni weni weni.\r\nMkulu wa bungwe la anthu a chi Albino mdzikomuno a Ovestone Kondowe anatsimikiza kuti apolisi apeza thupi la malemu Joseph Kachingwe.\r\nNngakhale kuti boma linayika malamulo okhwima mchaka cha 2016 othandiza kuthetsa mchitidwe wakupha anthu a chi Albino zikuoneka kuti mchitidwewu ukupitilirabe.\r\nPosachedwapa munthu win awa chi Albino anaphedwa ndipo nkhani ikukhudza wapolisi, wansembe, mchimwene wa malemuyo ndi anthu ena zinthu zomwe zikupitilira kudandaulitsa anthu ambiri poona kuti anthu omwe akanathandiza kuthetsa mchitidwewu ndi omwenso akumakhudzidwa ndi nkhani zoterezi.\r\nPakadalipano anthu 25 a ch Albino ndiwo aphedwa mdzikomuno.','local_news','2018-07-11','2018-07-11 07:42:53'),(115,'Ana 9 000 abadwa opanda kachilombo ka HIV','11/07/18\r\nMalipoti akusonyeza kuti ana 9 000 omwe makolo awo ali ndi matenda a Edzi  anabadwa opanda kachilombo ka ka HIV m\'maboma a Balaka, Machinga, Mangochi, Dedza ndi Blantyre kuchokera mchaka cha 2005.\r\nMalinga ndi bungwe la Sant Egidio lomwe mkulu wake ndi a Marco Impagliazzo anawa anabadwa kuchokera mzipatala zing\'ono zing\'ono khumi ndi zitatu komwe akugwirako ntchito.\r\nIwo ati kulimbikitsa amayi kumwa mankhwala otalikitsa moyo motsatira ndondomeko komanso kuyamwitsa mwakathithi ndi zina mwa ntchito zomwe akulimbikisa mzipatalazi.\r\nIwowa atinso chaka chino palibe mwana wabadwa ndi kachilombo ka HIV zinthu zomwe ati zikugwirizana ndi masomphenya a ntchitoyi.\r\nNtchitoyi akuti yathandizanso kuphunzitsa ogwira ncthito zachipatala osachepera 10, 000 omwe akulimbikitsa ntchito yoti amayi oyembekezera omwe ali ndi kachilomboka asamapatsire mwana obadwayo.\r\nBungweli lati kuyambira mchaka cha 2014 lakhala likulimbikitsa kuti ana obadwa tsopano azikalembetsa ku chipatala ndipo izi zikuchitika pa chipatala cha ku Balako chokha,','local_news','2018-07-11','2018-07-11 09:21:39'),(116,'Siliva ikufuna Sailesi pomwe Bullets ikukambiranabe...','11/07/18\r\nPotsatira kusiya kusewera ku timu ya Dynamos ya mdziko la South Africa komwe akuti samalandila malipiro ake Dalitso Sailesi ali ndi ufulu opita ku timu ina iliyonse ndipo timu ya siliva kapenanso kuti ma Bankers aonetsa chidwi pa mnyamatayu yemwe amasewera pakati.\r\nMlembi wa timu ya Siliva Thabo Nyirenda wati Sailesi ndi osewera wabwino ndipo mwayi utapezeka sangamusiye ngakhale anauza olemba nkhani wa Daily Times kuti pakadalipano sanayankhule ndi osewerayu.\r\nSiliva ingathe kulekana ndi osewera ake awiri Binwell Katinji komanso Brighton Munthali ngati atachita bwino ku mayeso omwe akupanga ndi matimu a Highlands Park komanso Amazulu a mdziko la South Africa omwe awonetsa chidwi pa osewera awiriwa.\r\nMkhalapakati wa osewerayu Chingeni Kadam\'manja watsimikiza kuti ma timu a mdziko lino komanso kunja akufuna atatenga osewerayu koma anati timu ya Nyasa Big Bullets ikhala yoyamba kuipatsa mwayi otenganso osewerayu.\r\nSailesi wakhala akusewera ku Bullets kwa nka nthawi koma ali ndi ufulu opita ku timu yomwe akufuna.\r\nMkulu wa Big Bullets a Fleetwood Haiya wati Sailesi ndi osewera wabwino yemwe ali ndi kuthekera koonjezera mangolemera a timuyi koma anati pakadalipano zokambira zokhudza osewerayu szinathe ndipo alengeza mu nthawi yoyenelera ngati abwelerenso ku timuyi.\r\nSailesi adauza nyuzipepala ya Nation kuti anathetsa mgwirizano ndi timu ya ku Zambia atalephera kumupatsa ndalama zokwana 7.5 million kwacha malinga ndi mgwirizano wawo.\r\n\r\n','sports_news','2018-07-11','2018-07-11 09:20:45'),(117,'Msewu wa Mzuzu -Nkhata Bay autsegulira','11/07/18\r\nMtsogoleri wa dziko lino Aurthur Peter Mutharika lachiwiri anatsekulira msewu wa Mzuzu-Nkhata Bay omwe ndi otalika ma kilomita 46 ndipo wamangidwa ndi ndalama zokwana 16 billion kwacha zochokera ku Banki yayikulu yothandiza pa zitukuko m\'maiko a mu Africa ya  African Development Bank.\r\nPoyankhula kwa anthu omwe anasonkhana pa bwalo la zamaswero la Msamba ku Nkhata Bay konko, a Mutharika anati misewu ndi yofunikira kwambiri pa chitukuko cha dziko. Iwo anati ichi nchifukwa chake boma lawo likugwira ntchito yomanga misewu 17 m\'madera osiyana siyana mdzikomuno. \r\nNduna ya zamtengatenga a Jappie Mhango anauzanso msonkhanowu kuti misewu ina isanu ikhala ikumalizidwa chaka chino chikamatha.\r\nMseuwu uli ndi kuthekera kolimbikitsa ntchito zamalonda pakati pa dziko la Malawi ndi Tanzania komanso wafupikitsa ulendo ochokera mu mzinda wa Mzuzu kupita ku Nkhata Bay.\r\nPali chiyembekezo choti ntchito zokopa alenda zikhoza kukwera ndi kumangidwanso kwa msewuwu kamba koti anthu azitha kupita ku Nkhata Bay komwe kuli nyanja komanso zinthu zopatsa chidwi pa ntchito zokopa alendo.\r\nMalipoti ati ndalama zina zomwe zatsala ku ntchitoyi azigwiritsa ntchito pokulitsa msewu wina mu mzinda wa Mzuzu.','local_news','2018-07-11','2018-07-11 09:35:39'),(118,'Namwino watsekeledwa mchitokosi kamba kogwililira Msungwana','11/07/18\r\nAnthu akamva dzina loti Namwino timayesa kuti ndi wankazi yekha, ayi ndithu alikonso a Namwino a muna mdziko lomwe lino ndipo m\'modzi wa iwo amutsekela mchitokosi ku Mulanje kamba kumuganizira kuti anagwililira msungwana wa zaka khumi ndi zisanu -  15.\r\nMneneri wa apolisi m\'boma la Mulanje a Gresham Ngwira atsimikiza nkhaniyi.\r\nMsungwana wauza apolisi kuti Namwinoyu yemwe ndi Spencer Chigwengwe  anaitanira anamuitanira mnyumba yake pomwe amadutsa mu msewu pafupi ndi pa nyumba yake oa ulendo obwelera kunyumba kwawo kuchokera ku malo ena omwe amakaonelera kanema.\r\nAtalowa mnyumbayo Namwinoyo sanachedwe koma kuthimitsa mwatso kapena kuti magetsi ndikukakamiza msungwanayo kuti agone naye.\r\nMwambo okakamizawu utatha ndipo mpumulo utamupeza Namwinoyu anazindikra kuti wapalamula ndipo anapempha msungwanayo kuti asauze aliyense za nkhaniyo.\r\nKoma malinga ndi apolisi, atafika kunyumba kwawo  msungwanayu anauza makolo ake za zomwe zamuchitikira ndipo mayi ake pokwiya ndi kukhumudwa ndi nkhaniyi anakasuma  ku polisi.\r\nKomwe ko ku Mulanje kwachitikanso nkani yomwe ikuti Maxwell Napuluma wa zaka 21 amutsekera mchitokosi kamba kogwililira bwenzi lake lomwe. Awiriwo anali pa ubwenzi kuchokera mwezi wa June chaka chatha ndipo malinga ndi msungwanayo katatu konse akhala akuchita zadama kunyumba kwa mnyamatayo koma zonse zinaululika pomwe mai a msungwanayi anafunsa zambiri za ubwenzi wa awiriwa. Pakhota mchira wa nyani ndipakuti kugonana ndi msungwana wa zaka khumi ndi zisanu - 15 ndi mulandu ndithu. Chenjeranitu kumeneko.','local_news','2018-07-11','2018-07-11 09:56:47');
